var book = {
	"name": "Loukas",
	"numChapters": 24,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Namar ba don shisha shibun kiba la shimti ban thoh lang ter ter ïa ka jingïathuhkhana shaphang kiei kiei ruh ba la pyndep hapdeng jong ngi,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> kat kumba ki la ai pateng ha ngi, kiba long hi ki nongïohi naduh kaba mynnyngkong bad ki nongïalap jong kata ka ktien:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ka la ibit ha nga ruh haba nga la ïai-ïit biang biang ïa kiei kiei baroh naduh kaba mynnyngkong, ban thoh ryntih ter ter ha me, A Theophilos u babha tam eh,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ba men ïoh tip skhem ïa ka jingshisha shaphang kita kiei kiei ruh, ha kiba me la ïoh hikai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ha ki sngi u Herod, u syiem ka Judia, la don uwei u lyngdoh uba kyrteng “u Sakharaïa”, na ka jingkylliang sngi u Abia: bad ka tnga jong u na ki khun kynthei u Aaron, kaba kyrteng “ka Elisabet”.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Baroh ar ngut ruh ki la long ki bahok ha khmat U Blei, ba ki da ïaid ha ki hukum bad ki niam jong U Trai baroh khlem jingrem.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te kim don khun, naba ka Elisabet ka la long ka balyngki, bad ki sngi ka rta jong ki baroh ar ngut ki la noh arsut.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ka la jia te, haba u dang leh ïa ka kam lyngdoh ha khmat U Blei, ha kaba ter ter ka jingkylliang sngi jong u,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> katba kum ka rukom ka kam lyngdoh, ka la dei ïa u ban thang ka jingainguh thang baiwbih, haba u la leit ha kata ka jaka kyntang ka jong U Trai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad uta u paidbah baroh u dang ïaduwai habar ha kata ka por ka jingainguh thang baiwbih.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te la mihpaw ha u, u angel U Trai, u da ïeng sha kamon ka duwan ka jingainguh thang baiwbih.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Sakharaïa haba u la ïohi, u la sngewkhuslai eh, bad ka jingsheptieng ka la kem ïa u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, uta u angel u la ong ha u, “Wat sheptieng, ko Sakharaïa: naba la shahshkor ïa ka jingduwai jong me; te ka tnga jong me ka Elisabet kan kha khun shynrang ïa me, bad men khot ïa ka kyrteng jong u, ‘u Ïoannis’:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> te men ïoh ka jingsngewbha bad ka jingkmen; shibun ruh kin ïashadkmen namar ka jingkha jong u;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> naba un long uba khraw ha khmat U Trai, bad un ym dih ïa ka Waiñ lane ka kyiad; bad yn pyndap ïa u da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, wat naduh ka kpoh ka kmie jong u:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> shibun te na ki khun Israel un pynphai sha U Trai uba U Blei jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U te un leit ha shuwa ka khmat jong U, ha ka mynsiem bad ka bor u Elias, ban pynphai ïa ki dohnud ki kpa sha ki khun, bad ïa ki bymkohnguh sha ka jingstad ki bahok; ban pynkhreh ïa U Trai, u paidlang ba la pynbit.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Sakharaïa te u la ong ha uta u angel, “Da kumno ngan ïoh tip ïa kane? naba nga long u tymmen, bad ki sngi ka rta ka tnga jong nga ki la noh arsut.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Uta u angel u da ïathuh u la ong te ha u, “Nga long u Gabriel, uba ïeng ha khmat U Blei; te la phah ïa nga ban kren ha me, bad ban wallam ruh ha me ïa kine ki khubor babha.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ha khmih, men sngap jar, bad men ym lah ban kren, tad ynda kata ka sngi ba yn pynlong ïa kine kiei kiei ruh; namar ba mem shym la ngeit ïa ki ktien jong nga, ïa kiba yn pyndep ha ka Ïa jong ki.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Uta u paidlang te u dang ïa-ap ïa u Sakharaïa, bad ki la sngewlyngngoh naba u slem katta katta ha kata ka jaka kyntang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad haba u la mih noh, um lah shuh ban kren ha ki; ki la shemphang te ba u la ïohi ïa ka jingithuhpaw ha kata ka jaka kyntang: u te u shu ïaipynpaw da ki dak ha ki, u la sah ruh u bymnangkren.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ynda la dep kita ki sngi ka jingkam lyngdoh jong u, u la leit noh sha la ïing.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hadien kita ki sngi te, ka Elisabet ka tnga jong u ka la punkhun, bad ka la buhrieh ïa lade san bnai, ka da ong,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Kumne U Trai u la leh ha nga ha ki sngi ha kiba u la khmih ïa nga, ban weng noh ïa ka jinglongbeiñ jong nga hapdeng ki briew.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te ha u bnai u bahynriew la phah ïa uta u angel Gabriel na U Blei sha ka shnong ha Galilaïa, kaba kyrteng “ka Nasaret”,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> sha ka theisotti kaba la ïatehktien bad u briew, uba kyrteng “u Joseph”, na ka ïing u Dabid; ka kyrteng kata ka theisotti te ka long “ka Mari”.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Uta u angel te haba u la leit hapoh sha ka, u la ong, “Khublei, pha kaba la ïoh ka jingaiei bakhraw! U Trai u don lem bad pha; la kyrkhu ïa pha hapdeng ki kynthei.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ka te ka la sngewkhuslai eh na ka jingong jong u, bad ka la puson ha lade hato kaba kumno ka lah ban long kane ka jingkhublei.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Uta u angel u la ong te ha ka, “To wat sheptieng, ko Mari; naba pha la shem ka jingaiei bad U Blei:",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> te ha khmih, phan sa punkhun ha la ka kpoh, bad phan kha ïa u khun, bad phan khot ïa ka kyrteng jong u, ‘U Jisu’:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> une un long U Bakhraw, bad yn khot ïa u, ‘U Khun U Bahakhlieh Tam Eh’: bad U Trai uba U Blei un ai ha u ïa ka khet u Dabid u kpa jong u;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> bad un synshar halor ka ïing u Jakob ha la ka rta; bad ka hima jong u ruh ka ban ym kut shuh.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te ka Mari ka la ong ha uta u angel, “Kumno kane kan long, haba ngam pat ithuh ïa u briew?”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Uta u angel te u da ïathuh u la ong ha ka, “U Mynsiem Bakhuid un wan ha pha, bad ka bor U Bahakhlieh Tam Eh kan kah halor jong pha; namar kata ruh, ïa ita i bakhuid ïa iba yn kha, yn khot ‘U Khun U Blei’;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> ha khmih ruh, ka Elisabet ka kur jong pha, ka ruh ka la punkhun shynrang ha ka jinglong tymmen jong ka; bad une u long u bnai u bahynriew ïa ka, ïa kaba la ju khot ‘ka balyngki’.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Naba kawei ruh ka ktien na U Blei kan ym long khlem ka bor.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ka Mari te ka la ong, “Ha khmih ka shakri jong U Trai, to kan long ha nga katba kum ka ktien jong me.” Te uta u angel u la leit noh na ka.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ka Mari te ka la ïeng ha kita ki sngi, bad ka la leit kyrkieh sha ka ri lum, sha kawei ka shnong kaba ha Juda;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> bad ka la leit rung ha ka ïing u Sakharaïa bad ka la khublei ïa ka Elisabet.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ka la jia ruh, katba ka Elisabet ka la ïohsngew ïa ka jingkhublei jong ka Mari, la khih i khun ha ka kpoh jong ka; bad la pyndap ïa ka Elisabet da U Mynsiem Bakhuid.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ka la pyrta te da ka ktien bajam, bad ka la ong, “La kyrkhu ïa pha hapdeng ki kynthei, bad la kyrkhu ruh ïa u soh ka kpoh jong pha!",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Nangno ruh, la jia kane ïa nga, ba ka kmie U Trai jong nga ka la wan ha nga?",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> naba, ha khmih, katba ka ktien ka jingkhublei jong pha ka sawa ha ki shkor jong nga, la khih i khun na kaba shadkmen ha ka kpoh jong nga:",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> suk ruh kata kaba la ngeit; naba ka jingpyndep kan long ïa kita kiei kiei ruh, ïa kiba la kren ha ka da U Trai.”",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ka Mari ruh ka la ong, “Ka dohnud jong nga ka pynkhraw ïa U Trai,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> bad ka mynsiem jong nga ka shadkmen ha U Blei U Nongpynim jong nga;",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> naba U la khmih ha ka jinglong rangli ka shakri jong U: naba, ha khmih, naduh mynta ki pateng bynriew baroh kin khot ‘kaba suk’ ïa nga.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Namar uta U Badonbor U la leh ki jingphylla ïa nga; bad ka bakhuid ka kyrteng jong U,",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> bad ka jingisynei jong U pateng la pateng bynriew ha kita kiba sheptieng ïa U;",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> U pyni ïa ka borbah da ka ksangkti jong U; U pynsakma ïa kiba sarong ha ka jingmut ka dohnud jong ki:",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> U pynhiar ïa kiba khraw bor na ki khet, bad U kyntiew ïa ki barangli;",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> ïa ki bathngan U pyndap da kiei kiei ki babha; ïa ki bariewspah te U phah noh suda.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> U shan bor ïa u Israel u shakri jong U, ba Un ïoh kynmaw ïa ka jingisynei",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> (kumba U la ïathuh ha ki kpa jong ngi) ïa u Abraham, bad ïa u symbai jong u ha la ka rta.”",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Ka Mari te ka la sah kumba lai bnai bad ka, bad ka la leit phai noh sha la ïing.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Ka por ka Elisabet te ka la dap ïa ka ban kha; te ka la kha khun shynrang.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Te ki paramarjan bad ki kur jong ka ki la ïohsngew ba U Trai u la pynkhraw ïa la ka jingisynei ïa ka, bad ki la ïakmen lem bad ka.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Ka la jia ruh ba ha ka baphra sngi ki la ïawan ban otsher ïa uta u khunlung; bad kin sa kyrteng ïa u ha ka kyrteng u kpa jong u, u Sakharaïa.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Te ka kmie jong u ka la ïathuh bad ka la ong, “Ym kumta, hynrei, yn khot ‘u Ïoannis’ ïa u.”",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Ki te ki la ong ha ka, “Ym don uwei ruh na ki kur jong pha, ïa uba la khot da kane ka kyrteng.”",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Te ki la kylli da ki dak ïa u kpa jong u, kumno u, u mon ban khot ïa u.",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> U la pan te ïa i dieng lyngkniap, bad u la thoh, u da ong, “ ‘U Ïoannis’ long ka kyrteng jong u.” Baroh te ki la sngewkyndit.",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> La plie te ïa ka shyntur jong u kumne kumne ruh, bad ïa u thylliej jong u la pyllait, bad u la kren, u da ïaroh ïa U Blei.",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> Te ka jingsheptieng ka la ngat ha baroh kiba shong sawdong ïa ki: bad ïa kine kiei kiei baroh la pynbna kylleng ka ri lum jong ka Judia baroh.",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> Baroh ruh kiba la ïohsngew ki la buh khop ïa ki ha ki dohnud jong ki, ki da ong, “Une u khunlung shisha u ban long kumno?” Te ka kti U Trai ka la don lem bad u.",
			"67": "<sup>67</sup> La pyndap ruh ïa u Sakharaïa u kpa jong u da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, bad u la ïathuhlypa, u da ong,",
			"68": "<sup>68</sup> “Long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong u Israel; naba U la wan khmih, bad U la pynlong ka jingsiewspah ïa la ki briew;",
			"69": "<sup>69</sup> bad U la pynmih ïa ka reng ka jingpynim ïa ngi, ha ka ïing u Dabid u shakri jong U;",
			"70": "<sup>70</sup> kumba U la kren da ka shyntur ki nongïathuhlypa bakhuid jong U, kiba na mynbarim,",
			"71": "<sup>71</sup> ka jingpynim na kiba shun ïa ngi, bad na ka kti kita baroh kiba isih ïa ngi;",
			"72": "<sup>72</sup> ban pyni ka jingisynei ïa ki kpa jong ngi, bad ban kynmaw ïa ka jutang bakhuid jong U;",
			"73": "<sup>73</sup> ïa ka jingsmai ïa kaba U la smai ha u Abraham u kpa jong ngi,",
			"74": "<sup>74</sup> ïa ka ban ai ha ngi, ïa kiba la knieh kynthet na ka kti kiba shun ïa ngi, ba ngin shakri ïa U khlem da sheptieng,",
			"75": "<sup>75</sup> ha ka jingkhuid bad ha ka hok ha khmat jong U, baroh ki sngi ka rta jong ngi.",
			"76": "<sup>76</sup> Me ruh, ko khun, yn khot ‘u nongïathuhlypa jong U Bahakhlieh Tam Eh’; naba men leit ha shuwa ka khmat U Trai, ban pynkhreh ïa ki lynti bah jong U;",
			"77": "<sup>77</sup> ïa ka ban ai ka jingtip ïa ka jingpynim ha ki briew jong U, ha kaba map ïa ki pop jong ki,",
			"78": "<sup>78</sup> da ka jingisynei bajem eh U Blei jong ngi, da kaba ka jingmih ka sngi na jrong kan wan khmih ïa ngi,",
			"79": "<sup>79</sup> ban pynshai ïa kita kiba shong ha ka ba-dum bad ha ka syrngiew ka jingïap, ïa ka ban ïalam beit ïa ki kjat jong ngi sha ka lynti ka jingsuk.”",
			"80": "<sup>80</sup> Uta u khynnah te u la nang san, u la nang khraw bor ruh ha ka mynsiem, bad u la don ha ki ri khlaw haduh kata ka sngi ba u la pynpaw ïa lade ha u Israel."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia te ha kita ki sngi, ba ka hukum ka la mih noh na u Kaisar Agustos, ban kheiñ ïa kiba shong ha ka pyrthei baroh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> (Kane ka la long ka jingkheiñ ka banyngkong mynba u Kyrinios u long lyngskor ha ri Syria.)",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad baroh ki la leit ba yn kheiñ ïa ki, uwei pa uwei sha la ka jong ka jong ka shnong.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u Joseph ruh u la leit kiew na Galilaïa, na ka shnong Nasaret, sha Judia, sha ka shnong u Dabid, ïa kaba la khot “Bethlehem” (namar ba u long na ka ïing bad na ka jaid u Dabid):",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ba yn kheiñ ïa u lem bad ka Mari kaba la lah ïatehktien bad u, kaba la punkhun.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ka la jia te, katba ki dang don hangta, ba la dap ki sngi ïa ka, ban kha khun.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ka la kha ïa u khun u banyngkong jong ka, bad ka la sop ïa u da ki jaiñsop, bad ka la pynthiah ïa u ha ka shyngoid; naba ym don jaka ïa ki ha ka ïingbasa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> La don te ha kata ka ri, ki nongaplangbrot kiba sah sha lum, bad kiba ïa-ap miet ïa ka kynhun langbrot jong ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ha khmih ruh, u angel U Trai u la wan shisyndon ha ki, bad ka burom U Trai ka la tyngshaiñ baroh sawdong ïa ki: te ki la sheptieng shikatdei eh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, uta u angel u la ong ha ki, “Wat sheptieng; naba ha khmih, nga wallam ha phi ïa ka khubor babha ka jingkmen bakhraw ka ban long ha ki briew baroh:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> naba ha kane ka sngi la kha ïa phi, ha ka shnong u Dabid, ïa U Nongpynim, uba long U Khrist uba U Trai:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> te kane kan long ka dak ïa phi; phin shem ïa u khunlung ba la sop da ki jaiñsop, u da thiah ha ka shyngoid.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad kyndit kyndit la don lem bad uta u angel bun bah u paidbah ka bneng, ki da ïaroh ïa U Blei, ki da ong ruh,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Ka burom ha U Blei ha kiba jrong tam eh, bad ha ka pyrthei ka jingsuk hapdeng ki briew ha kiba U sngewbha eh.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ka la jia ruh, katba kita ki angel ki la leit noh na ki sha bneng, ba kita ki nongaplangbrot ruh ki la ïa-ong paralok hi, “Ïa, ngin ïaleit mynta haduh Bethlehem, bad ngin ïohi ïa kane kaei kaei kaba la jia, ïa kaba U Trai u la pynbna ha ngi.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, ki la ïawan kyrkieh, bad ki la shem ïa ka Mari bad ïa u Joseph, bad ïa uta u khunlung ba u thiah ha kata ka shyngoid.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Haba ki la ïohi te, ki la pynbna kylleng shaphang kata ka jingong, ïa kaba la lah ïathuh ha ki shaphang une u khynnah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Baroh ruh kiba la ïohsngew, ki la kyndit shaphang kita kiei kiei ruh ba la lah ïathuh ha ki da kita ki nongaplangbrot.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, ka Mari ka la ri kyndong ïa kine kiei kiei baroh, ka da ïaikhan ïa ki ha la ka dohnud.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kita ki nongaplangbrot te ki la leit wan noh, da kaba burom bad da kaba ïaroh ïa U Blei namar kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba ki la lah ïohsngew, bad ba ki la lah ïohi, kumba la ïathuh ha ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ynda la dap ka phra sngi ïa ka ban otsher ïa u, la kyrteng ïa u, “U Jisu”, ka kyrteng ïa kaba la lah ai da uta u angel shuwa ban pun ïa U ha ka kpoh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ynda la dap ki sngi ka jingpynkhuid ïa ki, katba kum Ka Hukum u Moses, ki la leit lam ïa U sha Jerusalem, ïa ka ban pynkyntang ïa U sha U Trai:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> (kumba la thoh ha Ka Hukum U Trai, “U shynrang baroh, ïa uba la kha nyngkong, yn ñiew u bakhuid ïa u sha U Trai”);",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad ïa ka ban ai ïa ka jingkñia, kat kum ba la ong ha Ka Hukum U Trai, “Shi jur ki lyngdkhur, lane ar tylli ki khun paro.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ha khmih ruh, la don u briew ha Jerusalem, uba kyrteng “u Simeon”; te une u briew u long u bahok bad u bariewblei, uba da ap kyrmen ïa ka jingpyntngen jong u Israel: bad U Mynsiem Bakhuid u la don ha u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> La pynpaw te ha u da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, ba un ym ïohi ïa ka jingïap, katba um pat ïohi ïa U Khrist u jong U Trai.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u la wan ha U Mynsiem sha ka templ: bad haba kita ki kmie ki kpa ki la wallam shapoh ïa U Jisu uba dang khunlung, ba kin leh na ka bynta jong U kumba shong ka rukom jong Ka Hukum;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ynda kumta, u hi u la shim kynthup ïa U, bad u la kyrkhu ïa U Blei, u la ong de,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Mynta, A Trai, men pyllait noh ïa la u shakri ha ka jingsuk, katba kum ka ktien jong me,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> naba ki khmat jong nga ki la ïohi ïa ka jingpynim jong me,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ïa kaba me la pynkhreh lypa ha khmat ki briew baroh;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ka jingshai ïa ka ban pynshai ïa ki Jentil, bad ka burom u Israel u paidlang jong me.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u Joseph bad ka kmie jong U ki la ïasngewkyndit namar kita kiei kiei ruh ba la kren shaphang jong U.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> U Simeon u la kyrkhu ïa ki ruh, bad u la ong ha ka Mari ka kmie jong U, “Ha khmih, la buh ïa une ïa ka ban long ka jingkyllon bad ka jingïeng ïa ki shibun ha Israel, bad ïa ka dak ruh ïa ka ban kren pyrshah;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> shisha yn pynpei ïa ka mynsiem jong pha hi ruh da ka waitlam; ba yn ïoh pynpaw ïa ki jingmut na ki babun ki dohnud.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> La don ruh kawei ka briew, ka Anna ka nongïathuhlypa, ka khun u Phanuel, na ka jaid Asher: (kaba la slem eh ka rta, kaba la shong bad u tnga tang hynñiew snem naduh ka jinglong sotti jong ka.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad ka la sah riewkynthei jin phraphew saw snem), ka bym ju mih shuh na ka templ, hynrei da ki jingshah jingit bad ki jingduwai, ka da shakri ïa U Blei synñia sngi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kane ruh, haba ka la poi tiap hamar kata ka por, ka la ïaroh ïa U Blei, bad ka la kren shaphang jong U, ha kita baroh kiba ïa-ap kyrmen ïa ka jingsiewspah ka Jerusalem.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ynda ki la pyndep te ïa kiei kiei baroh katba kum ka hukum U Trai, ki la ïawan phai pat sha Galilaïa, sha ka shnong jong ki, ka Nasaret.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te uta u khynnah u la nang san, u la nang khraw bor ruh ha ka mynsiem, ba la pyndap ïa u da ka jingstad: bad ka jingaiei U Blei ka la don ha u.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ki kmie ki kpa jong U te ki ju leit sha Jerusalem ha la ka snem, ha Ka Jingkhawai Niam Ka Jinglait.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ki te, mynba U la dap khat-ar snem ka rta, ki la leit kiew sha Jerusalem, katba kum ka rukom jong kata Ka Jingkhawai Niam.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ynda ki la lah pyndep ïa kita ki sngi, katba ki dang ïawan phai ruh, uta u khynnah, U Jisu, u la nang sah ha Jerusalem; u Joseph te bad ka kmie jong U kim tip.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Hynrei, ba ki da tharai ba U don bad kiba wan lang, ki la leit shi sngi lynti; bad ki la ïawad ïa U hapdeng ki kur, bad hapdeng ki para ba ïa-ithuh.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te haba kim shem ïa U, ki la leit phai pat sha Jerusalem, ki da wad ïa U.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ba hadien lai sngi ki la shem ïa U ha ka templ, ba U da shong hapdeng ki nonghikai, U da sngap ïa ki, bad U da kylli jingkylli ïa ki de.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Baroh te kiba la ïohsngew ïa U ki la sngewlyngngoh ïa ka jingshemphang bad ïa ki jubab jong U.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te haba ki la ïohi ïa U, ki la sngewkyndit eh: bad ka kmie jong U ka la ong ha U, “Ko khun, balei ba me la leh kumne ïa ngi? ha khmih, u kpa jong me bad nga da kaba sngewsih ngi la ïawad ïa me.”",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> U te u la ong ha ki, “Balei ba phi ïawad ïa nga? Phim shym tip ba ka dei ïa nga ban long shaphang kiei kiei ruh ki jong U Kpa jong nga?”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Hynrei, ki kim shym shemphang satia ïa kata ka jingong ïa kaba U la ong ha ki.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Te U la leit hiar noh bad ki, bad U la wan sha Nasaret, bad U la ïaikohnguh ïa ki. Hynrei, ka kmie jong U ka la sumar kyndong ïa kine ki jingong baroh ha ka dohnud jong ka.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> U Jisu ruh u la nang khraw ha ka jingstad bad ha ka rynïeng, bad ha ka jingsngewbha ha khmat U Blei bad ki briew."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha ka bakhatsan snem ka jingsynshar u Tiberios Kaisar, mynba u Pontios Pilat u long lyngskor ka Judia, bad u Herod u long Tetrark ka Galilaïa, bad u Philip u para jong u, u long Tetrark ka Ituraïa bad ka ri Trakhonitis, bad u Lusanias u long Tetrark ka Abilini,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ha kaba u Annas bad u Kaïaphas ki long rangbah lyngdoh, la wan ka ktien U Blei ha u Ïoannis u khun u Sakharaïa ha ka ri khlaw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u la leit sha ka ri baroh sawdong ka Jordan, u da ïalap ïa ka jingbaptis ka jingkylla-ka-bamut, ïa ka ban map ki pop;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> kumba la thoh ha ka kitab ki ktien jong u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa, u da ong: “Ka ktien jong uba pyrta ha ka ri khlaw; ‘Phin pynkhreh ïa ka lynti bah U Trai, phin pynbeit ïa ki lynti jong U.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ïa ka jaka them baroh yn pyndap, ïa u lum bah bad ïa u lum rit baroh yn pynmadan ruh; bad ki lynti ki bakyllaiñ kin long kiba beit, bad kiba shong at shong them ruh kin long ki lynti bamadan;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad ka doh baroh kan ïohi ïa ka jingpynim jong U Blei.’ ”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar kata, u la ong ha ki paidbah kiba la mih noh ba yn pynbaptis ma u ïa ki, “A ki khun ki ksiew ki bseiñ, uei ba la maham lypa ïa phi ban phet ïap noh na ka jingbitar ka ban sa lap?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Naba kumta, to sei noh ïa ki soh kiba dei biang ïa ka jingkylla-ka-bamut, bad wat sdang ban ong ha lade, ‘Ngi don u Abraham uba long u kpa jong ngi’; naba nga ong ha phi, ba U Blei u lah na kine ki maw ban pynmih khun ïa u Abraham!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te wat mynta ruh ïa ka wait la buh ha u thied jong ki dieng: namar kata, ïa u dieng baroh u bymsei soh babha yn khet noh, bad yn bred sha ka ding.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kita ki paidbah ki la kylli ïa u, ki da ong, “Aïu te ngi dei ban leh?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U la ïathuh bad u la ong te ha ki, “Jar uba don ar tylli ki sopti un ïasam bad uta u bymdon; bad jar uba don ki jingbam, to un leh kumjuh.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki nongkhrong ruh de ki la wan ba yn pynbaptis ïa ki, bad ki la ong ha u, “Ko Nonghikai, aïu ngi dei ban leh?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Wat khrong tam ïa kaba la buh ïa phi.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki shipai ruh ki la kylli de ïa u, ki da ong, “Ngi pat ngi dei ban leh aïu?” U la ong ruh ha ki, “Wat leh jubor ïano ïano ruh, lymne wat shim klop ei ei; to sngewhun ruh bad la ka bainong.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te katba uta u paidlang u dang ap lyngngoh, bad ba baroh ki ïasaid hi ha la ki dohnud dohnud shaphang u Ïoannis, ïoh ba dei ma u pynban uta U Khrist;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> u Ïoannis u la ïathuh ha ki baroh, u da ong, “Nga shisha nga pynbaptis ïa phi da ka um; hynrei, un sa wan uba kham khraw ïa nga, uba kam dei ïa nga ban loit noh wat ïa ka jingteh ki juti jong u; uta keiñ un pynbaptis ïa phi da U Mynsiem Bakhuid bad da ka ding:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> uba ka jingpeh jong u ka ha ka kti jong u, ïa ka ban pynkhuid bha ïa ka kyntem jong u, bad ban lum ïa u Kew sha ka thiar jong u; hynrei, ïa u stait un thang da ka ding bymjulip.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kumta, da bun kiwei kiwei pat ki jingsneng u la ïathuhkhana babha ha u paidlang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, u Herod uba u Tetrark, ba u la shah sneng na u, shaphang ka Herodias ka tnga u Philip u para jong u, bad shaphang ki kam bymman baroh ïa kiba u Herod u la lah leh,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> u la kynton lang halor baroh sa ïa kane ruh, ba u la set ïa u Ïoannis ha ka byndi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ka la jia te, ynda la lah pynbaptis ïa uta u paidlang baroh, bad haba la lah pynbaptis ïa U Jisu ruh, bad ba U dang duwai, ba la plie ïa ka bneng,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad U Mynsiem Bakhuid u la hiar ha U ha ka dur met, kum ka paro, bad ka ktien ka la wan na bneng, kaba ong, “Me long U Khun jong nga uba ieit; ha me nga sngewbha eh.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te U Jisu hi haba u la sdang ban hikai, u la long kumba laiphew snem ka rta, uba long (kumba la tharai) u khun u Joseph, u khun u Heli,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> u khun u Matthat, u khun u Lebi, u khun u Melkhi, u khun u Janna, u khun u Joseph,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> u khun u Mattathias, u khun u Amos, u khun u Naum, u khun u Esli, u khun u Naggai,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> u khun u Maath, u khun u Mattathias, u khun u Semei, u khun u Josikh, u khun u Juda,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> u khun u Joanna, u khun u Risa, u khun u Sorobabel, u khun u Salathiel, u khun u Niri,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> u khun u Melkhi, u khun u Addi, u khun u Kosam, u khun u Elmodam, u khun u Er,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> u khun u Jose, u khun u Elieser, u khun u Jorim, u khun u Matthat, u khun u Lebi,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> u khun u Simeon, u khun u Juda, u khun u Joseph, u khun u Ïonan, u khun u Eliakim,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> u khun u Melea, u khun u Menan, u khun u Mattatha, u khun u Nathan, u khun u Dabid,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> u khun u Jesse, u khun u Obed, u khun u Boas, u khun u Salmon, u khun u Naason,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> u khun u Aminadab, u khun u Aram, u khun u Esrom, u khun u Phares, u khun u Juda,",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> u khun u Jakob, u khun u Isaak, u khun u Abraham, u khun u Terah, u khun u Nahor,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> u khun u Serukh, u khun u Raw, u khun u Peleg, u khun u Eber, u khun u Shelah,",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> u khun u Kainan, u khun u Arphaksad, u khun u Shem, u khun u Noah, u khun u Lamekh,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> u khun u Methusela, u khun u Enokh, u khun u Jared, u khun u Malelil, u khun u Kainan,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> u khun u Enos, u khun u Seth, u khun u Adam, uba u khun U Blei."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Jisu te uba la dap da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, u la wan phai pat na ka Jordan, bad la ïalam noh ïa u da U Mynsiem sha ka ri khlaw, sawphew sngi,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ba la pynshoi ïa u da u Soitan. Ei ei ruh em um shym bam ha kita ki sngi; hynrei, ynda ki la kut, u la sngewthngan.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Soitan u la ong te ha U, “Lada me long U Khun U Blei, to ong ha une u maw ba un long kpu.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te U Jisu u la ïathuh ha u, “La thoh: ‘Ym tang da u kpu hi ba un im u briew, hynrei, da ki ktien baroh ki jong U Blei.’ ”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Soitan te, haba u la ïalam noh ïa U sha u lum bajrong eh, u la pyni ha U ha kaba shi khyllipmat ïa ki hima ka pyrthei baroh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Soitan u la ong ha U, “Ïa kane ka bor baroh bad ka burom jong ki, ngan sa ai ha me: naba la ai ïa ka ha nga, bad hano hano ruh ha uba nga mon, nga ai ïa ka;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> lada ma me, namar kata, men mane dem ha khmat jong nga, baroh kan long ka jong me.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Jisu te U la ïathuh bad U la ong ha u, “Khie leit noh shadien jong nga, me u Soitan: naba la thoh: “ ‘Men mane dem ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong me, tang ïa u hi ruh men shakri.’ ”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u la ïalam noh ïa U sha Jerusalem, bad u la pynïeng ïa U halor ka dong ka templ, bad u la ong ha U, “Lada me long U Khun U Blei, to pynnoh ïa lade nangne;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> naba la thoh: “ ‘Un hukum ïa ki angel jong U shaphang jong me, ïa ka ban sumar biang biang ïa me:’",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “bad “ ‘kin ïarah ïa me ha ki kti jong ki, ba ïoh kumno kumno men jynthut la ka kjat ha u maw.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Jisu te U da ïathuh U la ong ha u, “La ong: ‘Men ym tynjuh ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong me.’ ”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda u Soitan u la lah pyndep ïa ka jingpynshoi baroh, u la khlad noh na U shi por.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kumta, U Jisu u la wan phai pat ha ka bor U Mynsiem sha Galilaïa: te ka nam shaphang jong u ka la phriang baroh sawdong kata ka ri.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la hikai ha ki synagog jong ki; baroh ruh ki da burom ïa u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U la wan ruh ha Nasaret, ha kaba la pynsan pynrangbah ïa u; te u la leit rung, kumba u ju leh, ha ka sngi Sabbaton ha ka synagog, bad u la ïeng joit ban pule.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> La ai te ha u ïa Ka Kitab U Isaïah U Nongïathuhlypa: bad haba u la plied ïa kata ka kitab, u la shem ïa ka jaka ha kaba la thoh:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “U Mynsiem U Trai U ha nga: naba U la pynsleh ïa nga ïa ka ban ïalap ïa ka gospel ha ki baduk; U la phah ïa nga ban pynbna ïa ka jingpyllait ha kiba la set byndi, bad ïa ka jingpynpeit pat ha ki bamatlah, ban pyllait noh ïa kiba la ban ka shitom;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ban pynbna ïa ka snem bapdiang hun ka jong U Trai.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u la kli ïa kata ka kitab, bad u la ai noh pat ha uba sumar, bad u la shong. Te ki khmat jong kiba ha kata ka synagog baroh ki la neh ha u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U la sdang te ban ong ha ki, “Ha kane ka sngi, la pyndep ïa kane Ka Jingthoh ha ki shkor jong phi.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Baroh ruh ki la ïaroh ïa u, bad ki la sngewkyndit namar kita ki ktien jali ja-um kiba la mih noh na ka shyntur jong u. Ki la ong ruh, “Une um long u khun u Joseph?”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Khlem pep phin ong ha nga ïa kane ka pharshi, ‘Ko nongpynkhiah, to pynkhiah ïa lade: Ïa kaei kaei ruh ba ngi la ïohsngew ba la leh ha Kapernam, to leh hangne ruh ha la ka jong ka ri.’ ”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U la ong ruh, “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba ym don u nongïathuhlypa ïa uba ki pdiang sngewbha ha la ka jong ka ri.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, ïa kaba shisha nga ong ha phi, shibun ki riewkynthei ki la don ha Israel ha ki sngi u Elias, mynba la khang khop ïa ka bneng, lai snem bad hynriew bnai, katba la long ka 'nemsniew kaba khraw ha kata ka ri baroh kawei;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> te sha kano kano ruh na ki, ym shym la phah ïa u Elias, hynrei, tang sha Sarepta, ha ka ri Sidon, sha ka briew kaba long riewkynthei.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Shibun ruh ki bapang 'ñiangthohlieh ki la don ha Israel ha ka por u Elisha u nongïathuhlypa; te ïa uwei ruh na ki ym shym la pynkhuid, hynrei, tang ïa u Naaman u nong Syria.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Baroh te kiba ha kata ka synagog, haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, ki la dap da ka jingbitar;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> te haba ki la ïeng joit, ki la shop noh ïa u shabar ka shnong, bad ki la ïalam noh ïa u haduh ka shyllangmat u lum, halor uba la tei ïa ka shnong jong ki, ïa ka ban pynnoh khongpong ïa u.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, u, haba u la ïaid lyngba napdeng jong ki, u la leit noh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u la wan arsut sha Kapernam, ka shnong ha Galilaïa; bad u hikai ïa ki ha ka sngi Sabbaton.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ki la sngewkyndit eh ïa ka jinghikai jong u, namar ka ktien jong u ka la long bad ka bor.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ha kata ka synagog te u la don u briew uba don ka mynsiem u ksuid bymkhuid, bad u la pyrta da ka ktien bajam eh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Ieh! ngi ïadonkam aïu bad me, ko Jisu uba na Nasaret? Me la wan khnang ïa ka ban pynjot ïa ngi? Nga ithuh ïa me uei me long, uta U Bakhuid u jong U Blei.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U Jisu te u la sneng ïa u, U da ong, “Wat jam me, to mih noh ruh na u.” Kumta haba uta u ksuid u la pynkyllon ïa u hapdeng, u la mih noh na u, um shym da pynsniew ei ei ruh em ïa u.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> La jia te ka jingsngewlyngngoh ha ki baroh; ki la ïakren lem ruh paralok hi, ki da ong, “Kaba kumno kane ka ktien? naba da ka hukum bad da ka bor, U hukum ïa ki mynsiem bymkhuid, ki ruh ki mih noh!”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ka jingbna te shaphang jong U ka la leit sha man ka jaka jong kata ka ri kylleng sawdong.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ynda U la ïeng noh na kata ka synagog, U la leit rung hapoh ka ïing u Simon. Te ka khieshoh kaba jur eh ka la ngat ha ka syngken kurim u Simon; bad ki la kyrpad ïa U na ka bynta jong ka.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te haba U la ïeng najan jong ka, U la sneng ïa kata ka khieshoh, te ka la iehnoh ïa ka; bad kumne kumne ruh ka la ïeng bad ka la shakri ïa ki.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te haba la sep ka sngi, baroh kat kiba don ki bapang da ki bun jaid ki jingpang, ki la wallam ïa ki ha u; te u la buh ïa la ki kti halor uwei pa uwei na ki, bad u la pynkhiah ïa ki.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ki ksuid ruh de ki la mih noh na kiba bun, ki da pyrta jam, ki da ong ruh, “Me long U Khrist U Khun U Blei.” Hynrei, haba u la sneng ïa ki, um shah ïa ki ban kren, naba ki la tip ba u long U Khrist.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te ynda la mih ka sngi, u la mih noh bad u la leit noh sha ka jaka kynjah ka ri khlaw; bad kita ki paidbah ki la wad ïa u, bad ki la wan poi haduh ha u, bad kin jin da la bat ïa u, ba un ym leit noh na ki.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Hynrei, u la ong ha ki, “Ka dei ïa nga ban ïalap ïa ka gospel ka hima U Blei ha kiwei pat ki shnong ruh, namar ïa kane khnang la phah ïa nga.”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Kumta, u la ïalap ha ki synagog ki jong ka Galilaïa."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia te, katba uta u paidbah u la ïatur sha U ïa ka ban ïohsngew ïa ka ktien jong U Blei, ba U hi U ïeng harud ka pung Gennesaret.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad U la ïohi ar tylli ki lieng kiba ïeng harud kata ka pung; hynrei, ki nongtong dohkha ki la lah mih noh na ki, bad ki dang ïasait ïa la ki jar.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te U la kiew ha kawei na kita ki lieng, kaba long ka jong u Simon, bad U la ong ïa u ban ñiat noh khyndiat na ryngkew. Haba U la shong, te U la hikai ïa kita ki paidbah nalor kata ka lieng.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ynda U la wai noh kaba kren, U la ong ha u Simon, “To ñiat noh sha kaba jylliew, to pynhiar ruh ïa ki jar jong phi ban dup ngat.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Simon u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Ko Kynrad, ngi la ïaleh shitom baroh shi miet, te ei ei ruh em ngim shym la ngat; hynrei, namar ka ktien jong me, ngan pynhiar ïa ki jar.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, ynda ki la lah leh ïa kane, ki la ngat bun bah eh ki dohkha; ki jar jong ki te ki la sdang kad.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki la khawoit te ïa la ki lok kiba ha kata kawei pat ka lieng, ïa ka ban wan ïarap ïa ki. Te ki la wan bad ki la ïa-pyndap ïa ki lieng baroh ar tylli haduh ba ki la sdang ngam.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Simon Petros haba u la ïohi ïa kane, u la dem khrup ha ki khohsiew U Jisu, u da ong, “To khie leit noh na nga; naba nga long u briew u bapop, A Trai.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Naba u la sngewkyndit bad kita baroh kiba don lem bad u, namar ka jingngat ki dohkha ïa kaba ki la ngat;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> kumjuh ruh u Jakob bad u Ïoannis, ki khun u Sebedi, kiba long kiba ïaïoh bynta lem bad u Simon. Ynda kumta, U Jisu u la ong ha u Simon, “Wat sheptieng; naduh mynta men long u nongtong briew.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ynda ki la lah wallam pat ïa la ki lieng sha ryngkew, ki la iehnoh ïa kiei kiei baroh, ki la bud ruh ïa U.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ba haba U don ha kawei na kita ki shnong, ha khmih ruh u briew uba la dap da ka jingpang 'thohlieh: te haba u la ïohi ïa U Jisu u la dem khrup, bad u la kyrpad ïa U, u da ong, “A Trai, lada me mon, me lah ban pynkhuid ïa nga.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Haba U la kner te ïa la ka kti, U la ktah ïa u, U da ong, “Nga mon; to men long khuid.” Te kumne kumne ruh, kata ka pang 'thohlieh ka la jah noh na u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te U la hukum ïa u ban ym ïathuh hano hano ruh; hynrei, “khie leit noh, to pyni ïa lade ha u lyngdoh, to ainguh ruh na ka bynta ka jingpynkhuid jong me, kat kumba u Moses u la hukum, ïa ka ban long ka jingphla ïa ki.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, ka ktien shaphang jong U ka la nang kham phriang pynban; bad ki paidbah babun ki la ïawan lang ban ïohsngew, bad ban ïoh pynkhiah na ki jingpang jong ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U te U la kynriah noh sha ki jaka kynjah ha ri khlaw, U la duwai ruh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ka la jia te ha kawei ka sngi, katba U dang hikai, ba ki la shong hangta ki Pharisi bad ki nonghikai Ka Hukum, kiba la wan na ki shnong baroh jong ka Galilaïa, bad ka Judia, bad na Jerusalem: te ka bor U Trai ka la don bad U ïa ka ban pynkhiah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ha khmih ruh, ki ïabah ha ka palong ïa u briew u bapang ïapshiliang: te ki la ïawad lad ban wallam ïa u hapoh, bad ban buh ïa u ha khmat jong U.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te haba kim shem lad shuh na-ei na-ei ruh ba kin wallam ïa u hapoh, namar uta u paidbah, ki la leit kiew halor kata ka ïing, bad ki la pynhiar noh ïa u lyngba ka jingsop lem bad la ka jingthiah, hapdeng keiñ ha khmat U Jisu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Haba U la ïohi te ïa ka jingngeit jong ki, U la ong ha u, “Ko briew, la map noh ïa me ïa ki pop jong me.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi ki la ïasdang ban ïapyrkhat te, ki da ong, “Uei une uba kren ïa ki jingkrenbeiñ Blei? uei ba lah ban map noh ïa ki pop, hynrei, tang U Blei hi?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu ba U da tip biang ïa ki jingpyrkhat jong ki, U la ïathuh bad U la ong ha ki, “Phi ïapyrkhat aïu ha la ki dohnud?",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kano kaba kham jem, ban ong, ‘La map noh ïa me ïa ki pop jong me’: lane ban ong, ‘To ïeng, to ïaid ruh?’",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, ba phin ïoh tip ba U Khun u briew u don bor ha ka khyndew ban map ïa ki pop” (U la ong ha uta u bapang ïapshiliang), “Nga ong ha me, To ïeng, to bah noh ïa la ka jingthiah, to khie leit noh ruh sha la ïing.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, haba u la ïeng joit ha khmat jong ki, bad ba u la bah noh ïa kata ha kaba u la thiah, u la leit noh sha la ïing, da kaba ïaroh ïa U Blei.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ka jingkyndit te ka la ngat ha ki baroh, bad ki la ïaroh ïa U Blei; la pyndap de ïa ki da kaba sheptieng, ki da ong, “Ngi la ïohi ïa kiei kiei ki baphylla ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, u la leit noh, bad u la ïohi ïa u nongkhrong uba kyrteng “u Lebi”, ba u da shong ha ka ïing khrong, bad U la ong ha u, “To bud ïa nga.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te haba u la iehnoh ïa kiei kiei baroh, u la ïeng joit, bad u la bud ïa U.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Lebi u la thaw ka jingkhawai kaba khraw ïa U ha la ïing; te la don u paidbah babun na ki nongkhrong, bad na kiwei pat kiba la ïashong bam ryngkat bad ki.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ki Pharisi bad ki nongthoh jong ki, ki la ïakren khñium ïa ki synran jong U, ki da ong, “Balei ba phi ïabam ïadih ryngkat bad ki nongkhrong bad ki bapop ruh?”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te U Jisu u da ïathuh, u la ong ha ki, “Ki bakhiah kim donkam ïa u nongpynkhiah, hynrei, ki bapang keiñ:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ngam shym la wan ban khot ïa ki bahok, hynrei, ïa ki bapop sha ka jingkylla-ka-bamut.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ki te ki la ong ha u, “Ki synran u Ïoannis ki shah jingit bunsien, bad ki pynlong jingduwai ruh, kumjuh ruh ki jong ki Pharisi; hynrei, ki jong me ki ïabam ki ïadih ruh.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad U Jisu u la ïathuh ha ki, “Phi lah ban pynbor ïa ki nong-on kurim ban shah jingit, katba u nongleit-kurim u dang don bad ki?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> hynrei, ki sngi kin poi, ynda yn shim noh ïa u nongleit-kurim na ki; ynda kumta keiñ, ha kita ki sngi kin sa shah jingit.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te u la kren ïa ka pharshi ruh ha ki: “Ym don uba tar shi lyngkhot na ka jaiñkup thymmai ïa ka ban syrdep ïa ka jaiñkup barim; ne un pynkad ïa kata ka bathymmai, bad kata ka shi lyngkhot ruh kaba na kata ka bathymmai kam ïadei putet bad kata ka barim.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ym don ruh uba buh ïa ka Waiñ thymmai ha ki lywa snieh barim; ne kata ka Waiñ thymmai kan pynpdang ïa kita ki lywa snieh, ka hi ruh kan jaw noh, bad kita ki lywa snieh kin jot noh;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> hynrei, ïa ka Waiñ thymmai dei ban buh ha ki lywa snieh thymmai.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ym don mano mano ruh, haba u la dih ïa ka barim, uba kwah ïa ka bathymmai; naba u ong, ‘Ka bha ka barim’.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha kawei ka sngi Sabbaton ba u la ïaid lyngba ïa ki lyngkha Kew; ki synran jong u ki la ïakheit soh Kew, te haba ki la kyrjiaw ha la ki kti ki la bam ruh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te kiba na ki Pharisi ki la ong, “Balei phi leh ïa kaba ym dei ban leh ha ka sngi Sabbaton?”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Jisu u da ïathuh te ha ki u la ong, “Phim ju la pule wat ïa kato kaba u Dabid u la leh mynba u la thngan, ma u, bad kita kiba don lem bad u de?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumno ba u la leit rung shapoh ka ïing U Blei, bad ba u la shim bad u la bam ruh ïa ki 'pu pyni, bad u la ai ha kita kiba bad u ruh de; ïa ki bymbit ban bam, hynrei, tang ïa ki lyngdoh hi?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “U Khun u briew u long U Trai jong ka Sabbaton ruh.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha kawei pat ka Sabbaton, ba U la leit rung hapoh ka synagog bad U la hikai; te la don hangta u briew uba ka kti kamon jong u ka la ïap.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi ki la ïa-ap thap ïa U, la un pynkhiah ne em ha ka Sabbaton, ba kin ïoh mudui ïa U.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U te U la lah tip ïa ki jingmut jong ki, bad U la ong ha uta u briew uba don ka kti ka baïap, “To khie joit, to ïeng ruh hapdeng.” Te u la khie bad u la ïeng joit ruh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar kata, U Jisu u la ong ha ki, “Ngan kylli ïa phi: ka dei ïa ka ban leh bha ha ka sngi Sabbaton, lane ïa ka ban leh sniew? ïa ka ban pynim ïa ka jingim, lane ïa ka ban pynduh noh?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te U la khmih sawdong ruh ha ki baroh, bad U la ong ha uta u briew, “To kner noh ïa la ka kti.” U ruh u la leh kumta; te ïa kata ka kti jong u la pynbha.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ki te ki la dap da ka jingbitar lamwir; bad ki la ïasylla paralok hi, aïu ba ki lah ban leh ïa U Jisu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha kita ki sngi, ba u la leit noh sha u lum ban duwai; u la sah ruh baroh shi miet ha ka jingduwai ha U Blei.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda la mih ka sngi te, u la khot ïa ki synran jong u; na ki te u la jied khat-ar ngut, ïa kita ruh u la khot “Apostol”,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ïa u Simon (ïa uba U la kyrteng “Petros” ruh), bad ïa u Andriw u para jong u, ïa u Jakob bad ïa u Ïoannis, ïa u Philip, bad ïa u Bartholomai,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ïa u Mathaïos bad ïa u Thomas, ïa u Jakob u khun u Alphaïos, bad ïa u Simon ïa uba la sin “u Bashitrhem”,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ïa u Juda u para u Jakob bad ïa u Judas Iskariot, uba leit long ruh u nongdie noh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te haba u la hiar arsut lem bad ki, u la ïeng ha ka jaka madan, bad shibun na ki synran jong u, bad u paidbah byllien na Judia baroh, bad na Jerusalem, bad narud duriaw Tyros bad Sidon, kiba la wan ban ïohsngew ïa U, bad ba yn pynkhiah ruh ïa ki na ki jingpang jong ki;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ïa kita kiba la shitom eh na ki mynsiem bymkhuid la pynkhiah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te uta u paidbah baroh u la pyrshang ban ktah ïa U; naba ka bor ka la mih noh na U, bad ka la pynkhiah ïa ki baroh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U te haba u la peit la ki khmat ha ki synran jong u, u la ong, “Suk ma phi ki baduk; naba ka jong phi long ka hima U Blei.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Suk ma phi kiba shah thngan mynta; naba yn pynkdang ïa phi. Suk ma phi kiba ïam mynta; naba phin rkhie.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Suk ma phi ynda ki briew kin shun ïa phi, bad ynda kin tait ïa phi bad kin lehbeiñ ïa phi, bad kin ot beiñ noh ruh ïa ka kyrteng jong phi kum ka bymman, na ka bynta U Khun u briew.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> To kmen phi ha kata ka sngi, to shadkmen ruh! naba ha khmih, ka nong jong phi ha bneng ka long kaba khraw; naba kumjuh hi ki kpa jong ki, ki la leh ïa ki nongïathuhlypa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Hynrei, kordit ïa phi, ki bariewspah! naba phi la ïoh pdiang la ka jingtngen.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Kordit ïa phi, kiba la dap mynta! naba phin thngan. Kordit ïa phi, kiba rkhie mynta! naba phin sngewsih bad phin ïam de.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Kordit ïa phi, haba ki briew baroh kin kren bha ïa phi! naba kumjuh hi ki kpa jong ki, ki la leh ïa ki nongïathuhlypa balamler.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Hynrei, nga ong ha phi kiba sngew: To ieit ïa ki nongshun jong phi; to leh bha ïa kita kiba bishni ïa phi;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> to kyrkhu ïa kita kiba tim ïa phi; duwai ruh na ka bynta kita kiba leh sniew ïa phi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ha uta uba thab ïa me ha kawei ka ngab, to pynshah sa kata kawei ruh; bad ha uta uba shim noh ïa ka jaiñkup jong me, wat khang ïa ka sopti ruh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> To ai ruh ha u briew baroh uba ïapan na me; bad na uta uba shim noh ïa kiei kiei ruh ki jong me, wat pan pat ïa ki.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kumba phi mon ruh ba ki briew kin leh ïa phi, to leh ma phi ruh kumjuh ïa ki.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Naba lada phi ieit tang ïa kita kiba ieit ïa phi, ka jingnguh aïu ka dei ïa phi? naba ki bapop ruh ki ieit ïa kita kiba ieit ïa ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Lada phi leh bha ruh tang ïa kita kiba leh bha ïa phi, ka jingnguh aïu ka dei ïa phi? naba ki bapop ruh ki leh hi kumjuh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Lada phi ai kylliang ruh tang ïa kita na kiba phi kyrmen ban ïoh, ka jingnguh aïu ka dei ïa phi? naba ki bapop ruh ki ai kylliang ha ki bapop, ba kin ïoh mar kajuh hi.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Hynrei, to ieit ïa ki nongshun jong phi, to leh bha ruh, bad to ai kylliang, khlem da duh jingkyrmen satia; te ka nong jong phi kan long kaba khraw, bad phin long ki khun U Bahakhlieh Tam Eh; naba U long uba sbun ïa ki bymnguh bad ïa ki bymman.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> To long phi kiba isynei, kumba U Kpa jong phi ruh U long uba isynei.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> “Wat bishar ruh, te yn ym bishar ïa phi; wat pynrem, te yn ym pynrem ïa phi; to map noh, te yn map ïa phi;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> to ai, te yn sa ai ha phi ruh; ïa ka jingthew ka babha, ba la tynñian bad ba la kyr-ih, bad ba la shlei de, kin thep ha ka pla jong phi; naba da kajuh ka jingthew da kaba phi thew, yn thew pat ha phi.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te u la kren ïa ka pharshi ha ki: “U bamatlah u lah ne em ban ïalam ïa u bamatlah? hato kin ym ïahap baroh ar ngut ha ka thliew?",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> U synran um long halor u nonghikai jong u; hynrei, ynda la hikai bha ïa u, un long kum u nonghikai jong u.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te balei ba me khmih ïa u thngiat uba ha ka khmat u paralok jong me, hynrei, mem pyrkhat ïa ka khung kaba ha ka khmat jong me hi?",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Lane kumno ba me lah ban ong ha u paralok jong me, ‘Ko lok, to shah ba ngan khlaw noh ïa uto u thngiat uba ha ka khmat jong me’ haba me hi mem ïohi ïa ka khung kaba ha ka khmat jong me? Me uba arsap, to khlaw noh shuwa ïa ka khung na ka khmat jong me, ynda kumta te, men ïohi bha ban khlaw noh ïa uto u thngiat uba ha ka khmat u paralok jong me.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> “Namar ym ju don u dieng babha uba sei ki soh bymman; lymne u dieng bymman uba sei ki soh babha.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Namar ïa u dieng baroh yn ithuh na u soh jong u hi; naba kim ju kheit ïa ki soh Dumbur na ki dieng shiah, lymne kim kheit ïa u soh Waiñ na ka 'law lynnong dieng shiah.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> U briew u babha u sei ïa ka babha na ka jingkynshew ka babha ka dohnud jong u: u briew uba bymman ruh u sei ïa ka bymman na ka jingkynshew kaba bymman ka dohnud jong u; naba na ka jingshlei ka dohnud, ka shyntur jong u ka kren.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> “Hynrei, balei ba phi khot ïa nga, ‘A Trai, A Trai’, bad phim leh pynban ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba nga ong?",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Uei uei baroh uba wan ha nga, bad uba ïohsngew ïa ki ktien jong nga, bad uba leh ruh ïa ki, ngan pyni ha phi ïano u syriem.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> U long kum u briew uba tei ïa ka ïing, uba la tih bad uba la ngam jylliew, bad uba la seng nongrim halor u mawsiang; te haba la jia ka jingshlei, ka um ka la shoh kyrthep ïa kata ka ïing, hynrei, kam lah shuh ban pynkhih ïa ka; naba la pynshong nongrim ïa ka halor u mawsiang.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Hynrei, uta uba ïohsngew, bad u bymleh, u long kum u briew uba la tei ïa ka ïing halor ka khyndew, khlem nongrim; ïa kaba ka um ka la shoh kyrthep, bad kumne kumne ruh ka la kyllon; te ka jingjot ka jong kata ka ïing ka la long kaba khraw.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda U la lah pyndep ïa ki jingong jong U baroh ha kaba ïohsngew uta u paidbah, U la rung shapoh Kapernam.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te don u shakri uwei u rangbah shispah, uba u la ieit eh, uba la pang bad ha tmier ka jingïap.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba u la ïohsngew shaphang U Jisu, u la phah ha U ïa ki tymmen basan ki Jiw, u da kyrpad ïa U ban wan pynim ïa uta u shakri jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki te, haba ki la poi ha U Jisu, ki la kyrpad eh ïa U, ki da ong, “U long uba dei ba men leh ïa kane ïa u;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> naba u ieit ïa ka kynja jong ngi, bad la tei ma u ïa ka synagog ïa ngi.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Jisu te U la leit lem bad ki. Te haba um jngai shuh na kata ka ïing, u rangbah shispah u la phah ïa ki lok sha U, ban ong ha U, “Ko Kynrad, wat pynshitom ïa lade; naba ngam long uba dei ba men wan rung hapoh ka ïing jong nga:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> lymne ngam sngew ïa lade uba bit ban wan ha me: hynrei, shu ong da ka ktien, te yn sa pynkhiah ïa u shakri jong nga:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> naba nga ruh nga long u briew ba la buh hapoh ka hukum, uba don ki shipai hapoh jong nga; te nga ong ha une, ‘Khie leit’, te u leit; ha uwei pat ruh, ‘Ale’, u ruh u wan; bad ha u shakri jong nga, ‘Leh ïa kane’, u ruh u leh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei, U la sngewphylla ïa u; bad haba U la phai, U la ong ha uta u paidbah ba bud ïa U, “Nga ong ha phi, ngam shym la shem kat kane ka jingngeit, em, wat ha Israel ruh.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba kita ïa kiba la phah ki la leit phai pat sha kata ka ïing, ki la shem ïa uta u shakri ba u koit bha pat.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka la jia te kum lashai, ba U la leit sha ka shnong ba khot “Nain”: te ki synran jong U ki la ïaleit lem bad U, bad u paidbah byllien.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te katba U la wan hajan ka khyrdop kata ka shnong, ha khmih, ki ïabah shabar ïa uba la ïap, u khun marwei ka kmie jong u, bad ka ruh ka long ka riewkynthei; bad bun u paidbah na kata ka shnong u la don lem bad ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Haba U Trai te U la ïohi ïa ka, U la sngewsynei ïa ka, bad U la ong ha ka, “To wat ïam.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te U la wan hajan bad U la ktah ïa ka krong, kita kiba ïabah te ki la ïeng. Bad U la ong, “Ko samla, nga ong ha me, To ïeng.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te uta uba la ïap u la khie shong, bad u la sdang ban kren: U te U la ai noh ïa u ha ka kmie jong u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ka jingsheptieng te ka la ngat ha ki baroh; bad ki la ïaroh ïa U Blei, ki da ong, “U nongïathuhlypa u bakhraw u la mih hapdeng jong ngi, bad U Blei u la wan-i ïa la ki briew.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kane ka jingbna shaphang jong U ka la phriang noh kylleng ka Judia baroh, bad kylleng kata ka ri kaba baroh sawdong.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki synran u Ïoannis ki la ïathuh ha u shaphang kine kiei kiei baroh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te haba u Ïoannis u la khot ha lade ar ngut na ki synran jong u, u la phah ïa ki ha U Trai, u da ong, “Me long uta u ban sa wan, ne ngin ïa-ap ïa uwei pat?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te haba kita ki briew ki la poi ha U, ki la ong, “U Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis u la phah ïa ngi ha me, u da ong, ‘Me long uta u ban sa wan, ne ngin ïa-ap ïa uwei pat?’ ”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ha kata hi ka por U la pynkhiah shibun ki briew na ki jingpang, bad na ki jingpang kordit, bad na ki mynsiem bymman; ïa shibun ki bamatlah ruh U la pynpeit.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Jisu te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ki, “Khie leit ïathuh ha u Ïoannis ïa kiei kiei kiba phi la ïohi bad ba phi la ïohsngew ruh; ba ki bamatlah ki peit pat, ki ba-dkoh ki ïaid, ïa kiba sa 'ñiangthohlieh la pynkhuid, ki bakyllut ki ïohsngew, ïa ki baïap la pynim pat, bad la ïalap ïa ka gospel ha ki baduk:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> suk ruh uta u ban ym thut ha nga.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba kita ki nonglam-ktien u Ïoannis ki la ïaleit noh, U la sdang ban ong ha kita ki paidbah shaphang u Ïoannis: “Phi la leit sha ka ri khlaw ban jngoh aïu? ïa u khah ba la pynkhih da ka lyer?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, phi la leit ban ïoh khmih aïu? Ïa u briew uba la kup ki jaiñkup bani? Ha khmih, kita kiba kup da ka jaiñkup thaba babun rong, bad kiba shongsuk ruh, ki don ha ki ïingsyiem.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, phi la leit ban ïoh khmih aïu? ïa u nongïathuhlypa? Shisha, nga ong ha phi, bad ïa uba kham khraw ïa u nongïathuhlypa.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Une u dei uta ba la thoh shaphang jong u: “ ‘Ha khmih, nga phah ïa u nonglam-ktien jong nga ha shuwa ka khmat jong me, u ban pynkhreh ïa ka lynti jong me ha shuwa jong me.’",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Naba nga ong ha phi, ‘Na kiba la kha na ki kynthei, ym don u nongïathuhlypa uba kham khraw ban ïa u Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis: pynban, uba kham rit ha ka hima U Blei, u long uba kham khraw ïa u.’ ”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te uta u paidlang baroh haba u la ïohsngew, bad ki nongkhrong ruh, ki la pynksan ïa U Blei, haba la pynbaptis ïa ki da ka jingbaptis u Ïoannis.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, ki Pharisi bad ki riewsaid, ki la kyntait noh ïa ka mon U Blei sha ka ban sniew ïa lade, haba ym shym la pynbaptis ïa ki da u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> U Trai u la ong ruh, “Namar kata, kum kaei ngan tharai ïa ki briew jong kane ka pateng bynriew? kum kaei ruh ki ïasyriem?",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ki long keiñ kum ki khynnah kiba ïashong ha ka jaka ïew, bad kiba ïapyrta paralok; kiba ong, “ ‘Ngi la ïa-put jingput ha phi, te phim shym la shad; ngi la ïarwai sngewsynei ha phi, te phim shym la ïam.’",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> “Naba u Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis u la wan, um da bam kpu lymne um da dih Waiñ; te phi ong, ‘Uba shong ksuid’ ïa u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> U Khun u briew u la wan u da bam u da dih ruh; te phi ong, ‘Ha khmih, u briew uba bam lalot, bad uba dih kyiad, u lok ki nongkhrong bad ki bapop.’",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Hynrei, ka jingstad ka la ksan na ki khun jong ka baroh.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te uwei na ki Pharisi u la khot ïa U ba un ïawan bam ja bad u; kumta te U la rung hapoh ka ïing uta u Pharisi, bad U la shong shaniah ban bam.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ha khmih ruh, ka briew ha kata ka shnong, kaba long ka bapop, haba ka la tip ba U shong shaniah ban bam ha ïing uta u Pharisi, ka la wallam ïa ka dabi alabaster ka jingsleh;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> haba ka la ïeng ruh hajan ki kjat jong U na shadien, ka da ïam, ka la sdang ban sait ïa ki kjat jong U da la ki jingjaw ummat, bad ka la ñiad da u 'ñiuh khlieh jong ka; bad ka la doh ïa ki kjat jong U, bad ka la pynsleh ïa ki da kata ka jingsleh.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te haba uta u Pharisi uba la khot ïa U, u la ïohi, u la kren ha lade, u da ong, “Lada une u long u nongïathuhlypa, un da la ithuh kaei bad kaba kumno kane ka briew kaba ktah ïa u, ba ka long ka bapop.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> U Jisu te U da ïathuh U la ong ha u, “Ko Simon, nga don ei ei ban ong ha me.” U te u la ong, “Ko Nonghikai, to ong.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> “Uwei u nongai ram u la don ar ngut ki nongkit ram; uwei u kit ram, sanspah tyngka, bad uwei pat, sanphew:",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> te haba kim don ei ei ruh ban siew, u la map ei ïa ki baroh ar ngut. Namar kata, to ong, uno na kita u ban kham ieit tam ïa u?”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> U Simon u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Uta, nga mut, uba la ïohmap ei ïa kaba kham bun.” U te U la ong ha u, “Me la bishar kaba dei.”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Bad haba U la phai sha kata ka briew, U la ong ha u Simon, “Me ïohi ne em ïa kane ka briew? nga la rung hapoh ka ïing jong me, te mem shym la ai um ïa ki kjat jong nga, hynrei, kane, ka la sait ïa ki kjat jong nga da ki jingjaw ummat jong ka, bad ka la ñiad da u 'ñiuh khlieh jong ka:",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> mem shym la ai ka jingdoh ïa nga, hynrei, kane, naduh ba nga la wan hapoh, kam shym la keiñ noh ban doh ïa ki kjat jong nga:",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> mem shym la pynsleh ïa ka khlieh jong nga da ka umphniang, hynrei, kane, ka la pynsleh ïa ki kjat jong nga da ka jingsleh:",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> naba kumta nga ong ha me, ‘La map ïa ki pop ki babun jong ka: namar ka la ieit shibun: hynrei, uta uba la ïohmap khyndiat, u ieit khyndiat.’ ”",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> U la ong te ha ka, “La map ïa ki pop jong pha.”",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Kita kiba ïashong bam lem ki la sdang te ban ong ha lade, “Uei une uba map kat ïa ka pop?”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Te U la ong ha kata ka briew, “Ka jingngeit jong pha ka la pynim ïa pha; to khie leit ha kaba suk.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka la jia shen shen hadien kata, ba u la leit jingleit lyngba ki nongbah bad ki nongrit, u da ïalap bad u da ïathuhkhana ïa ka gospel ka hima U Blei: bad lem bad u kita ki khat-ar ngut,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ki kynthei ruh ïa kiba la pynkhiah na ki mynsiem bymman bad na ki jingkhrew, ka Mari, ïa kaba la khot “ka nong Magdala”, na kaba la lah mih noh hynñiew ki ksuid,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ka Ïoanna ka tnga u Khusa, u rangbah u Herod, bad ka Susanna, bad shibun kiwei kiwei ruh, kiba la ju ïasumar sukher ïa u na ki jingdon jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba u paidbah babun u la ïawan lang bad ba ki la wan ruh ha U kiba na ki shnong baroh, U la kren da ka pharshi:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “U nongbet u la mih noh ban bet ïa u symbai jong u; te katba u dang bet, don uba la hap harud lynti, te la ïuh roit ïa u; bad ki sim bneng ki la bam duh ïa u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Uwei pat ruh, u la hap halor u mawsiang; te haba u dang shu mih, u la ïap ryngkhiang, naba um ïoh jingsngem.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Uwei pat te, u la hap hapdeng ki dieng Shiah; te kita ki dieng Shiah ki la ïamih lem, bad ki la ïakjap ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Uwei pat te, u la hap ha ka khyndew ka babha, bad u la mih, bad u la sei soh shispah shah.” Haba U la ong ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, U la pyrta, “Uba don ki shkor ban sngew, to ai ba un sngew.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki synran jong u te ki la kylli ïa u, “Kane ka pharshi ka lah ban mut aïu?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U te u la ong, “Ha phi keiñ la ai ban tip ïa ki maïan ka hima U Blei, hynrei, ha kiwei pat ha ki pharshi; ba haba ki ïohi kin ym ïohi, bad haba ki ïohsngew kin ym sngew-shemphang.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kata ka pharshi ka long kumne: “Uta u symbai, u long ka ktien U Blei.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te kita kiba harud lynti, long kita kiba ïohsngew; hadien kata, u Soitan u wan bad u rong noh ïa kata ka ktien na ka dohnud jong ki, khnang ba kin ym ngeit bad ïohlait im.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kita te kiba halor u mawsiang, ki long kita kiba ynda ki la ïohsngew, ki pdiang ïa kata ka ktien da kaba kmen; bad kine kim don thied, kiba shu ngeit shi por, bad ha ka por ka jingtynjuh, ki phai dien noh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Uta uba la hap hapdeng ki dieng Shiah te, long kita kiba ju ïohsngew, te katba ki nang pynleit la ki sngi ka rta, la kjap ïa ki da ki jingkhuslai bad ka spah, bad ki jingsngewbha kane ka jingim; te kim sei ki soh ki ba-ih bha.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te uta uba ha ka khyndew ka babha, kine ki long kita kiba da ka dohnud ka bahok bad ka babha, haba ki la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien, ki bat skhem ïa ka, bad ki sei soh da ka jingïaineh.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Bad ym don u briew haba u la thang ïa ka sharak, uba tap ïa ka da u khiew, lane uba buh hapoh ka jingthiah; hynrei, u buh ha ka dieng pynïeng sharak, ba kita kiba rung shapoh kin ïohi ïa kata ka jingshai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Naba ym don ei ei ba la buhrieh, ïa kaba yn ym pynpaw; lymne ei ei kaba rieh, ïa ka ban ym tip bad ka ban ym paw.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> To sumar, namar kata, kumno phi sngew; naba jar uba don, ha uta yn ai: uta u bymdon te, wat ïa kata kaba u mut ba u don, yn shim noh na u.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ka kmie bad ki hynmen hynbew jong u ki la wan ha u, hynrei, kim lah ban wan hajan jong u namar uta u paidbah.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> La ïathuh te ha u, “Ka kmie jong me bad ki hynmen hynbew jong me ki ïaïeng habar, ki da kwah ban ïohi ïa me.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, u la ïathuh bad u ong ha ki, “Ka kmie jong nga bad ki hynmen hynbew jong nga ki long kine kiba ïohsngew ïa ka ktien ka jong U Blei, bad kiba leh ïa ka.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ka la jia te ha kawei na kita ki sngi, ba u la leit kiew ha kawei ka lieng lem bad ki synran jong u, bad u la ong ha ki, “Ïa, ngin ïaleit sha shiliang ka pung.” Te ki la ïa-pynmih noh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, katba ki nang pynïaid lieng, u la ïohthiah: te ka 'erïong ka la hiar ha kata ka pung, bad ka lieng ka nang dap nang dap da ka um, bad sa ba kin ïap.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ki la ïawan ha u bad ki la kyrsiew ïa u, ki da ong, “Ko kynrad, kynrad, ngi la ïap!” Te u la kyndit bad u la sneng ïa kata ka lyer bad ïa kata ka jingat phyllung ka um; kumta, ki la ïajah noh, bad ka la long kaba jai jai.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Hangno ka jingngeit jong phi?” Te ba ki la sheptieng ki la sngewphylla, ki da ïa-ong paralok hi, “Une u long uei shisha, ba u hukum kat ïa ki lyer bad ïa ka um, bad ki kohnguh ïa u?”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te ki la poi ha ka ri ki nong Gadara kaba marpyrshah ïa ka Galilaïa.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad haba u la mih noh sha ryngkew, la wan tan ïa U, uwei u briew na kata ka shnong, uba shong ksuid; bad la slem eh um ju kup jaiñ, bad um ju shong ha kano kano ka ïing, hynrei, ha ki maw jingtep.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te haba u la ïohi ïa U Jisu, u la kyang, bad u la dem khrup ha khmat jong U, bad u la ong da ka ktien bajam, “Nga donkam aïu bad me, Jisu, Me U Khun U Blei U Bahakhlieh Tam Eh? Me nga kyrpad ïa me, wat pynshitom ïa nga!”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> (Naba U la hukum ïa uta u mynsiem bymkhuid ban mih noh na uta u briew. Naba la bunsien u la ju kem ïa u; bad la ap phira ïa u, bad la ju khum ïa u da ki kynjri bad da ki narkjat; bad haba u da pyndkut noh ïa kita ki jingkhum, la beh ïa u da uta u ksuid sha ki ri khlaw.)",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad U Jisu u la kylli ïa u, “Kaei ka kyrteng jong me?” u te u la ong, “U Paidbah”, naba bun ki ksuid ki la lah leit rung hapoh jong u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te ki la ïakyrpad ïa U, ba un ym hukum ïa ki ban leit noh sha dujok.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hynrei, la don hangta shi kynhun bah ki sniang kiba ïabam phlang halor lum, te ki la ïakyrpad ïa U ba un shah ïa ki ban leit rung hapoh kita. Te U la shah ïa ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad kita ki ksuid ki la mih noh na uta u briew, bad ki la leit rung hapoh kita ki sniang; te kata ka kynhun ka la phet ïap arsut ïa ka riat sha ka pung, bad ki la ïap jyllop.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te haba kita kiba ïa-ap ki la ïohi ïa kaba la jia, ki la ïaphet ïap noh, bad ki la pynbna ïa kata ha kata ka shnong bad ha kita ki ri bri.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ki la ïamih noh ban leit jngoh ïa kaba la jia; bad ki la wan ha U Jisu, bad ki la shem ïa uta u briew, na uba la lah mih noh kita ki ksuid, ba u la kup jaiñ, bad ba u tipbriew, u da shong de hajan ki kjat U Jisu; te ki la sheptieng.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kita kiba la lah ïohi ruh, ki la ïathuh ha ki kumno ba la lah pynkhiah ïa uta uba shong ksuid.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ynda kumta, u paidbah baroh kylleng sawdong ka ri jong ki nong Gadara, ki la ïakyrpad ïa U ban leit noh na ki; naba la ngat ha ki ka jingsheptieng bakhraw. Te U la kiew sha ka lieng bad U la leit phai pat.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Hynrei, uta u briew na uba la lah mih noh kita ki ksuid, u la kyrpad ïa U ban ïoh long lem bad U; hynrei, U Jisu u la pyllait noh ïa u, U da ong,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> “Khie leit phai pat sha la ïing, to ïathuh ruh ïa kiba katno kiei kiei ruh ba U Blei u la leh ïa me.” Te u la leit noh, u da ïalap ïa kata ka shnong baroh kawei ïa kiba katno kiei kiei ba U Jisu u la leh ïa u.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la wan phai pat, uta u paidbah u la pdiang sngewbha ïa U; naba baroh ki dang ïa-ap khmih lynti ïa U.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ha khmih ruh, u la wan u briew uba kyrteng “u Jairos”, bad uba long u nongsynshar jong ka synagog; te u la dem ha ki kjat U Jisu, bad u la kyrpad ïa U ban wan sha ïing jong u:",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> naba u la don ka khun marwei, kaba la khat-ar snem ka rta, bad kaba la jan ïap. Hynrei, katba U dang leit, kita ki paidbah ki la ïakyntur lang ïa U.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ka briew ruh kaba don ka jingpang mihsnam la khat-ar snem, kaba la lah pynlut ruh ha ki nongpynkhiah ïa la ka jingïoh baroh, hynrei, kam lah ïoh jingkoit nano nano ruh,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> ka la wan hajan na shadien, bad ka la ktah ïa ka rmiang ka jaiñkup jong U; te kumne kumne ruh kata ka jingmih snam jong ka, ka la sangeh noh.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te U Jisu u la ong, “Mano ba la ktah ïa nga?” Te ynda ki la len baroh, u Petros u la ong bad kita kiba don lem bad u, “Ko Kynrad, kine ki paidbah ki ïaphñian bad ki ïakyntur ïa me, te me ong, ‘Mano ba la ktah ïa nga?’ ”",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> U Jisu te U la ong, “Don mano re mano ba la ktah ïa nga; naba nga la sngewthuh ba ka bor ka la mih noh na nga.”",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Kata ka briew te haba ka la ïohi ba kam lah rieh shuh, da kaba khynñiuh ka la wan, bad haba ka la dem khrup ha khmat jong U, ka la ïathuh ha U ha khmat uta u paidlang baroh, na ka balei ba ka la lah ktah ïa U, bad kumno ba la lah pynkhiah ïa ka kumta kumta hi.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te U la ong ha ka, “To kyrmen, ko khun, ka jingngeit jong pha ka la pynkhiah ïa pha; to khie leit ha kaba suk.”",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Katba U dang kren, la wan uwei na ka ïing uta u nongsynshar ka synagog, u da ong ha u, “La ïap noh i khun jong me; wat pynshitom shuh ïa U Nonghikai.”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la ïohsngew, U la ong ha u, “Wat sheptieng: tang shu ngeit, te yn pynkhiah ïa ka.”",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Te haba U la wan sha kata ka ïing, um shah ïano ïano ruh ban rung hapoh, lait na u Petros bad u Ïoannis bad u Jakob, bad u kpa bad ka kmie jong kata ka khynnah.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Baroh te ki la ïaïam, bad ki la ïalynñiar lympat ïa lade namar jong ka. Hynrei, U la ong, “Wat ïam; namar kam shym la ïap, hynrei, ka shu ïohthiah.”",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Ki te ki la ïarkhiebeiñ ïa U, ba ki da tip ba ka la ïap.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Hynrei, U, haba U la pynmih noh ïa ki baroh shabar, bad haba U la bat ïa ka na ka kti, U la pyrta, U da ong, “Ko khynnah, to ïeng.”",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Bad ka mynsiem jong ka, ka la wan phai pat, bad kumne kumne ruh ka la ïeng joit; te U la hukum ban ai ei ei ha ka, ban bam.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Te ki kmie ki kpa jong ka ki la sngewkyndit, hynrei, U la hukum skhem ïa ki ban ym ïathuh hano hano ruh ïa kaba la leh."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u la khot lang ïa ki khat-ar ngut, bad u la ai ha ki ka bor bad ka iktiar halor ki ksuid baroh, bad ïa ka ban pynkhiah ïa ki jingpang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la phah ïa ki ban ïalap ïa ka hima U Blei, bad ban pynkhiah ïa ki bapang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “Wat rah ei ei ruh na ka bynta ka jingleit jong phi, lymne ïa u diengduh, lymne ïa ka ïarong, lymne ïa u kpu, lymne tyngka sbai; lymne wat rah ar tylli ki jingphong:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad ha kano kano ka ïing ba phi leit rung, hangta to ïashong, bad nangta phin mih noh:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> te kino kino ruh ki ban ym pdiang ïa phi, haba phi mih noh na kata ka shnong, to kynther noh ïa ka 'dewmet na ki kjat jong phi, ïa ka ban long ka sakhi pyrshah ïa ki.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki la mih noh, bad ki la leit kylleng ki nongrit, ki da ïalap ïa ka gospel, bad ki da pynkhiah de kylleng la kylleng ruh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Herod uba u Tetrark u la ïohsngew shaphang kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba la leh; bad u la shitom jingmut eh namar ba la ong da kiwei, ba u Ïoannis u la mihpat na ki nongïap;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad da kiwei pat, ba u Elias u la mihpaw; bad da kiwei pat de, ba u nongïathuhlypa, uwei na ki barim, u la mihpat.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Herod te u la ong, “Ïa u Ïoannis nga la khrai khlieh: hato uei une, uba nga ïohsngew kat kine kiei kiei ruh shaphang jong u?” U la kwah ruh ban ïohi ïa u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ki apostol ynda ki la wan phai pat, ki la ïathuh ha u ïa kiei kiei ruh kat kiba ki la lah leh. Te u la ïalam ïa ki, bad u la leit kyrpang sha ka shnong ba khot “Bethsaida”.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, haba kita ki paidbah ki la tip, ki la bud ïa u; te u la pdiang sngewbha ïa ki, bad u la ïathuh ha ki shaphang ka hima U Blei, bad u la pynkhiah ïa kiba donkam ïa ka jingpynkhiah.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ka sngi te ka la sdang noh; te ki khat-ar ngut ki la wan bad ki la ong ha u, “To pyllait noh ïa u paidbah, ba kin ïoh leit sha ki nongrit bad sha ki ri bri kylleng sawdong, ba kin ïoh thiah basa, bad ba kin ïoh jingbam: naba hangne ngi don ha ka jaka kynjah.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, u la ong ha ki, “To ai ma phi ha ki ban bam.” Te ki la ong, “Ngim don tam ïa san tylli ki kpu, bad ar tylli ki dohkha; lymda ngi leit thied jingbam ïa une u paidlang baroh.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Naba ki la long jin san hajar ki rangbah. U la ong te ha ki synran jong u, “To pynshong shaniah ïa ki, sanphew sanphew ha la ka jong ka jong.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ki la leh kumta, bad ki la pynshong shaniah ïa ki baroh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u la shim ïa kita ki san tylli ki kpu, bad ïa kita ki ar tylli ki dohkha, bad haba u la khmied sha bneng, u la kyrkhu ïa ki bad u la kdiah; bad u la ai ha kita ki synran ban buh ha khmat uta u paidbah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ki la ïabam bad ki la ïakdang baroh: la khar khat-ar tukri ruh na kaba lwet kaba la sah tam ïa ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ba haba u dang duwai hi weibriew, kita ki synran ki ïadon lem bad u; u la kylli te ïa ki, u da ong, “Ki paidbah ki ong ba nga long uei?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki da ïathuh te ki la ong, “ ‘U Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis’; hynrei kiwei pat, ‘u Elias’; bad kiwei pat, ba u nongïathuhlypa uba na ki barim u la mihpat.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u la ong ha ki, “Phi te phi ong ba nga long uei?” U Petros u da ïathuh te u la ong, “Uta U Khrist jong U Blei.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, u la maham ïa ki, bad u la hukum ban ym ïathuh ïa kata hano hano ruh;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> u da ong, “Ba ka dei ïa U Khun u briew ban shah shibun kiei kiei ruh, bad ba yn kyntait ïa u da ki tymmen basan bad ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki nongthoh ruh, bad ba yn pynïap ïa u, bad ba yn pynmih pat ïa u ha ka balai sngi.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki baroh, “Lada uno uno ruh u mon ban wan nadien jong nga, ai ba un len ïa lade, bad un rah ïa la ka diengphna ha la ka sngi, bad un bud ïa nga;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> naba uno uno ruh uba mon ban pynim ïa la ka mynsiem, un duh noh ïa ka; hynrei, uno uno ruh u ban duh noh ïa la ka mynsiem na ka bynta jong nga, uta keiñ un pynim ïa ka;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> naba u briew un myntoi aïu, lada u ïoh ïa ka pyrthei baroh, haba u la pynjot noh lane haba u la pynduh noh ïa lade?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> naba uno uno ruh u ban sngewlehrain ïa nga bad ïa ki ktien jong nga, ïa uta keiñ U Khun u briew un lehrain, ynda un wan ha ka burom jong u, bad ka jong U Kpa, bad ka jong ki angel bakhuid:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> hynrei, nga ong ha phi ïa kaba shisha, Don kiba na kine kiba ïeng hangne, ki ban ym mad ïa ka jingïap, tad ynda ki ïohi ïa ka hima U Blei.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ka la jia te kumba phra sngi hadien kine ki ktien, ba u la shim lem ïa u Petros, bad ïa u Ïoannis, bad ïa u Jakob, bad u la leit kiew sha u lum ban duwai.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te katba u dang duwai, ka dur ka khmat jong u ka la kylla, bad ka jaiñ jong u ka la lieh phyrnai eh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ha khmih ruh, ki rangbah ar ngut ki la ïakren bad u kiba la long u Moses bad u Elias,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> kiba la mihpaw ha ka burom bad ki la ïakren shaphang ka jingleit noh jong u, ïa kaba un sa pyndep ha Jerusalem.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> U Petros te bad kita kiba don lem bad U ki la sngewkhia da kaba samthiah, hynrei, haba ki la peitmat bha, ki la ïohi ïa ka burom jong U, bad ïa kita ar ngut ki rangbah kiba la ïeng lem bad U.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ka la jia, haba kita ki dang ïaleit noh na U, ba u Petros u la ong ha U Jisu, “Ko Kynrad, ka bha ïa ngi ban don hangne; ai ngin ïathaw te lai tylli ki ïingtrep; kawei ïa me, bad kawei ïa u Moses, bad kawei de ïa u Elias”: um da tip ïa-ei ba u ong.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te katba u dang kren ïa kine kiei kiei, la wan u lyoh bad u la kah ïa ki: te ki la sheptieng haba kita ki leit rung hapoh uta u lyoh.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ka ktien ruh ka la wan na uta u lyoh, ka da ong, “Une u long U Khun jong nga uba ieit; to phin sngew ïa u.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te haba la wai kata ka ktien, la shem ïa U Jisu weibriew. Ki te ki la sngap jar, bad kim shym la ïathuh hano hano ruh ha kita ki sngi ei ei ruh na kita kiei kiei kiba ki la lah ïohi.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ka la jia ruh kum lashai, ynda ki la lah wan hiar na uta u lum, ba u paidbah babun u la wan tan ïa U.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ha khmih ruh, u briew uba na uta u paidbah u la pyrta, u da ong, “A Nonghikai, nga kyrpad ïa me, to khmih ïa u khun jong nga, naba u long u khun marwei jong nga;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> ha khmih ruh, don u mynsiem ba kem ñiat ïa u, te shisyndon noh u lynñiar; bad u ring kyrthat ïa u katba u da sei tyrtho; bad haba u la pynlwet ïa u, da kaba eh u leit noh na u.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Nga la kyrpad te ïa ki synran jong me ba kin beh noh ïa u, hynrei, kim lah satia.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te U Jisu u la ïathuh bad U la ong, “A phi ka pateng bynriew bymngeit bad bamutlop, sa katno ngan long bad phi, bad ba ngan shah ïa phi? To wallam ïa u khun jong me shane.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te katba u dang wan, uta u ksuid u la pynkyllon sbak ïa u, bad u la ring kyrthat eh ïa u. U Jisu te U la sneng ïa uta u mynsiem bymkhuid, bad U la pynkhiah ïa uta u khynnah, bad U la ai noh ïa u ha u kpa jong u.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Baroh te ki la sngewkyndit namar kata ka borbah jong U Blei. Te katba baroh ki dang sngewphylla namar kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba U Jisu u la leh, u la ong ha ki synran jong u,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> “To ai ba kine ki ktien kin ngam ha ki shkor jong phi: naba yn sa aiti noh ïa U Khun u briew ha ki kti ki briew.”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Hynrei, ki, kim sngewthuh ïa kane ka jingong, bad la buhrieh ïa ka na ki, ba kin ym shemphang ïa ka; te ki la sheptieng ban kylli ïa u shaphang kata ka jingong.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Te la mih ka jingïasaid hapdeng jong ki, uno na ki u ban long uba kham khraw.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Hynrei, haba U Jisu u la ïohi ïa kata ka jingmut ka dohnud jong ki, U la shim ïa u khynnah, bad U la pynïeng ïa u hajan jong U,",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> bad U la ong ha ki, “Uno uno ruh u ban pdiang ïa une u khynnah ha ka kyrteng jong nga, u pdiang ïa nga; bad uno uno ruh u ban pdiang ïa nga, u pdiang ïa uba la phah ïa nga; naba uta uba long uba kham rit hapdeng jong phi baroh, uta keiñ u long uba khraw.”",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> U Ïoannis te u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Ko Kynrad, ngi la ïohi ïa uwei uba beh noh ïa ki ksuid ha ka kyrteng jong me; te ngi la adong ïa u, naba um ïabud lem bad ngi.”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Wat adong shuh; naba uta u bym ïapyrshah ïa ngi u long ha ka liang jong ngi.”",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Ka la jia ruh, mynba la jan poi ki sngi ban pdiang noh ïa u sha jrong, ba u te u la thew skhem la ka khmat ïa ka ban leit sha Jerusalem,",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> bad u la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien ha shuwa ka khmat jong u; te ki la leit bad ki la rung sha kawei ka nongrit ki nong Samaria, ïa ka ban pynkhreh ïa u.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Hynrei, kim shym la pdiang sngewbha ïa u, naba ka khmat jong u ka la thew leit sha Jerusalem.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Te haba ki synran jong u, u Jakob bad u Ïoannis, ki la ïohi ïa kata, ki la ong, “Ko Trai, me mon ba ngin hukum ïa ka ding ban hiar na bneng, bad ban thang duh ïa ki, kumba u Elias ruh u la leh?”",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Hynrei, u la phai, bad u la sneng ïa ki, bad u la ong, “Phim tip na kaba kumno ka mynsiem phi long:",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> naba U Khun u briew um shym wan ban pynjot ïa ki mynsiem ki briew, hynrei, ban pynim.” Ynda kumta, ki la ïaleit sha kawei pat ka nongrit.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Te katba ki dang ïaleit ha kata ka lynti, don uwei uba la ong ha U, “Ko Trai, ngan bud ïa me kat shaba me leit.”",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> U Jisu te U la ong ha u, “Ki myrsiang ki don ki thliew, bad ki sim bneng ki jaka rieh tngen, hynrei, U Khun u briew um don jaka ban buh la ka khlieh.”",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Te U la ong ha uwei pat, “To bud ïa nga.” Hynrei, u la ong, “Ko Trai, shah ba ngan da leit noh shuwa ban tep ïa la u kpa.”",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Ieh ïa ki baïap ban tep ïa ki baïap jong ki; hynrei, khie leit noh ma me, bad ïalap ïa ka hima U Blei.”",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Uwei pat de u la ong ruh, “Ko Trai, ngan bud ïa me; hynrei, shah ïa nga ban khublei shuwa ïa kita ki ba-ha-ïing jong nga.”",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Ym don u briew, haba u la buh ïa la ka kti ha ka jinglur bad u da kyrtiang dien, uba bit ïa ka hima U Blei.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, U Trai u la thung hynñiewphew ngut kiwei pat, bad u la phah noh ïa ki ar ar ha shuwa ka khmat jong u, sha ki shnong bad ki jaka baroh, sha kiba u hi un sa leit.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “Ka jingot ka bun shisha, hynrei, ki nongtrei ki khyndiat; namar kata, to ïakyrpad phi ïa U Trai kata ka jingot, ba un phah noh ïa ki nongtrei sha ka jingot jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> To khie leit noh; ha khmih, nga phah noh ïa phi kum ki khun langbrot hapdeng ki suri.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Wat rah ïa u 'saipan, lymne ïa ka ïarong, lymne ïa ki juti; bad wat khublei ïano ïano ruh ha kata ka lynti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sha kano kano ka ïing ruh ba phin rung, to ong shuwa, ‘Long ka jingsuk ïa kane ka ïing!’",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Lada don te u khun ka jingsuk hangta, ka jingsuk jong phi kan ïaishong halor jong u; te lada ym don, kan wan phai pat ha phi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad phin ïaishong ha kata kajuh ka ïing, da bam da dih ruh ïa kiei kiei ruh katba kin ai; naba ka dei ïa u nongtrei ban ïoh ïa la ka bainong. Wat kynriah noh na ka ïing sha ka ïing.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad sha kano kano ka shnong ruh ba phi rung, bad ki pdiang sngewbha ïa phi, to bam ïa kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba la buh ha khmat jong phi;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> te phin pynkhiah ïa ki bapang kiba don hangta, bad to ong ha ki, ‘Ka hima U Blei ka la wan hajan jong phi.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, sha kano kano ka shnong ruh ba phi rung, bad kim pdiang sngewbha ïa phi, phin mih noh sha ki lynti bah jong ka, bad phin ong,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ‘Wat ïa ka 'dewmet kaba la snoh ha ngi na ka shnong jong phi, ngi shu ñiad noh sha phi pat; la kumta to tip ïa kane, ba ka hima U Blei ka la wan hajan.’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nga ong ha phi, ba kan long kham jem ïa ka Sodom ha kata ka sngi, ban ïa kata ka shnong.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Kordit ïa pha, Khorasin! Kordit ïa pha, Bethsaida! Naba lada la lah leh ïa kita ki kambah ha Tyros bad Sidon, ïa kiba la lah leh ha phi, kin jin da la kylla-ka-bamut la mynslem, kin da shong ha ka jaiñ khain bad ka dpei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, kan long kham jem ïa ka Tyros bad ka Sidon ha ka jingbishar, ban ïa kaba ïa phi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Pha ruh, Kapernam, ïa kaba la kyntiew shaduh bneng, yn pynhiar noh arsut keiñ ïa pha haduh Hades.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Jar uba sngew ïa phi, u sngew ïa nga; bad jar uba kyntait ïa phi, u kyntait ïa nga; bad jar uba kyntait ïa nga, u kyntait ïa uta uba la phah ïa nga.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kita ki hynñiewphew ngut ki la wan phai pat da ka jingkmen, ki da ong, “Ko Trai, wat ïa ki ksuid la pyndem hapoh jong ngi ha ka kyrteng jong me.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U te u la ong ha ki, “Nga la ïohi ïa u Soitan ba u hap kum ka leilieh na bneng.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ha khmih, nga la ai ka bor ha phi ïa ka ban ïuh roit halor ki bseiñ bad ki 'ñianglartham, bad halor ka bor baroh ka jong u nongshun; bad ym don ei ei ruh ka ban pynsniew ïa phi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, wat kmen ha kane, ba ïa ki mynsiem la pyndem hapoh jong phi; hynrei, to kmen namar ba la thoh ïa ki kyrteng jong phi ha bneng.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ha kata hi ka por, U Jisu u la shadkmen ha U Mynsiem Bakhuid, bad u la ong, “Nga nguh ïa me, ko Kpa, U Trai ka bneng bad ka khyndew, ba me la buhrieh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh na ki bastad bad na ki bashemphang, bad ba me la pynpaw ïa ki ha ki khunlung; shisha, ko Kpa, naba kumta ka la ibit ha khmat jong me.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ïa kiei kiei baroh la ai ha nga na U Kpa jong nga; ym don ruh uba ithuh ïa U Khun u long uei, hynrei, tang U Kpa; bad ïa U Kpa u long uei, hynrei, tang U Khun, bad uta ha uba U Khun u mon ban pynpaw.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba u la phai sha la ki synran kyrpang, u la ong, “Suk kita ki khmat kiba ïohi ïa kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba phi ïohi!",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Naba nga ong ha phi, ba bun ki nongïathuhlypa bad ki syiem, ki la kwah ban ïohi ïa kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba phi ïohi, hynrei, kim shym la ïohi, bad ban ïohsngew ïa kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba phi ïohsngew, hynrei, kim shym la ïohsngew.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ha khmih ruh, uwei u riewsaid u la ïeng bad u la tynjuh ïa U, u da ong, “Ko Nonghikai, ngan leh aïu ba ngan ïoh ka jingim bymjukut?”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U te U la ong ha u, “La thoh aïu ha ka hukum? kumno me pule?”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U te u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “ ‘Men ieit ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong me da ka dohnud jong me baroh, bad da ka mynsiem jong me baroh, bad da ka bor jong me baroh, bad da ka jingmut jong me baroh; bad ïa la u paramarjan kumba ïa lade.’ ”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U la ong te ha u, “Me la ïathuh ïa kaba dei: to leh ïa kane, te men ïoh im.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U te, ba u kwah ban pynksan ïa lade, u la ong ha U Jisu, “Uno te uba long u paramarjan jong nga?”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U Jisu u la ïathuh bad U la ong, “Don uwei u briew uba la leit hiar na Jerusalem sha Jerikho; bad u la hap hapdeng ki nongtuh, kiba, haba ki la pynlyngkhuit ïa u, bad ba ki la shoh ïa u, ki la leit noh, ki da iehnoh ïa u, kum u baïap.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te uwei u lyngdoh, da kaba jia ryngkhat u la wan hiar na kata ka lynti; bad haba u la ïohi ïa u, u la ïaid kiar noh sharud lynti.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kumjuh ruh de, uwei u jaid Lebi, haba u la poi sha kata ka jaka, bad haba u la ïohi ïa u, u la ïaid kiar noh sharud lynti.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hynrei, uwei u kynja Samaria, katba u dang leit jingleit, u la poi haduh ha u; te haba u la ïohi ïa u, u la sngewsynei;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> bad u la wan ha u bad u la spaiñ ïa ki jingjngem snam jong u, u da theh ha ki, ïa ka umphniang bad ka Waiñ; te u la buh ïa u halor u mrad jong u hi, bad u la wallam ïa u sha ka ïingbasa, bad u la sumar ïa u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te haba kaba lashai, haba un sa leit noh, u la sei noh ar tyngka bad u la ai ha u trai ïingbasa bad u la ong ha u, ‘To sumar ïa u; bad kaei kaei ruh ba men pynlut tam, nga, ynda nga wan phai pat, ngan siew pat ïa me.’",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na kine ki lai ngut, uno, me mut, uba la long u paramarjan ïa uta uba la hap hapdeng kita ki nongtuh?”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te u la ong, “Uta uba la leh isynei keiñ ïa u.” U Jisu namar kata U la ong ha u, “Khie leit, to leh ma me ruh kumjuh.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te katba ki nang leit jingleit, u la rung ha kawei ka nongrit, bad kawei ka briew kaba kyrteng “ka Martha” ka la pdiang sngewbha ïa u sha ïing jong ka.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ka la don ruh ka para kaba kyrteng “ka Mari”, kaba la shong ruh ha ki kjat U Trai, bad kaba la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong u.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Hynrei, ka Martha ka la khuslai shaphang bun ka jingkam; te ka la wan ha u bad ka la ong, “Ko Trai, mem khmih ba ka para jong nga ka la iehnoh ïa nga ban shu trei jingtrei marwei? to ong ïa ka, namar kata, ba kan ïarap lem ïa nga.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Hynrei U Trai u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ka, “Ko Martha, Martha, pha khuslai, bad pha pynshitom sat ïa lade shaphang bun kiei kiei ruh;",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> hynrei, tang kawei kaba donkam eh; ka Mari te ka la jied ïa kata ka bynta ka babha, ïa kaba yn ym rong noh na ka.”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba U dang duwai ha kawei ka jaka, ba ynda U la wai noh, uwei na ki synran jong U, u la ong ha U, “Ko Trai, to hikai ïa ngi ban duwai, kumba u Ïoannis ruh u la hikai ïa ki synran jong u.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Haba phi duwai, to ong: “Ko Kpa jong ngi uba ha bneng, long bakhuid ka kyrteng jong me: wan ka hima jong me: long ka mon jong me ha ka khyndew ruh, kumba ha bneng.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ai ha ngi ha la ka sngi ka sngi ïa ka jingbam jong ngi kaba biang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> To map ruh ïa ngi ïa ki pop jong ngi; naba ngi hi ruh ngi map ïa baroh kiba leh sniew ïa ngi. To wat ïalam ïa ngi sha ka jingpynshoi ruh, hynrei, sumar ïa ngi na ka basniew.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “Lada uwei na phi u don u lok, bad un leit ha uta shiteng synñia, bad un ong ha u, ‘Ko lok, ïa-ai kylliang ïa nga lai tylli ki kpu;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> naba u lok jong nga u dang poi ha nga na la ka jingleit, bad ngam don ei ei ruh ïa kaba ngan buh ha khmat jong u’;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> uta te napoh ïing un jubab bad un ong, ‘Wat pynshitom ïa nga; la khang ïa ka jingkhang mynta, bad ki khun jong nga ruh ki ha jingthiah bad nga; ngam lah ban khie bad ban ai ha me’;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> nga ong ha phi, la un ym khie bad un ym ai ruh ha u namar ba u long u lok jong u; pynban, namar kata ka jingïaikyrpad jong u, un da khie un ai ruh ha u katba u donkam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nga ruh nga ong ha phi; to pan, te yn sa ai ha phi; to wad, phin sa shem ruh; to tied, te yn sa plie ïa phi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Naba baroh uba pan, u pdiang; bad jar uba wad, u shem; bad ïa uta uba tied, yn sa plie.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te lada u khun un pan kpu na uno uno ruh na phi uba long u kpa, hato un ai noh da u maw ha u? lane un pan ruh  ïa ka dohkha, bad ha kaba dei da ka dohkha un ai noh da u bseiñ ha u?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ne lada un pan ïa ka pylleng, hato un ai noh da ka 'ñianglartham ha u?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Namar kata, lada phi, kiba long bymman, phi tip ïa ka ban ai ïa ki jingai babha ha ki khun jong phi, kaba katno tam ba U Kpa jong phi uba ha bneng un ai ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid ha kita kiba pan na u?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te U dang beh ïa u ksuid u bymnangkren; ka la jia ruh, haba uta u ksuid u la mih noh, ba uta u bymnangkren u la kren; te ki paidbah ki la sngewkyndit.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, don na ki, kiba la ong, “Da u Belsebul, u rangbah ki ksuid, U beh noh ïa ki ksuid.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kiwei pat de, ba ki da tynjuh ïa U, ki la ïapan na U ïa ka dak na bneng.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, U, ba U da tip ïa ki jingmut jong ki, U la ong ha ki, “Ka hima baroh kaba ïaleh makynti kan jot noh; bad ka ïing ruh kaba ïaleh makynti, kan kyllon.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te lada u Soitan ruh u ïaleh hi ïa lade, kumno kan neh ka hima jong u? naba phi ong ba nga beh noh ïa ki ksuid da u Belsebul.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Lada nga te nga beh noh ïa ki ksuid da u Belsebul, hato dano ba ki khun jong phi ki beh noh ïa ki? namar kata, ki hi kin long ki nongbishar jong phi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, lada nga beh noh ïa ki ksuid da ka shynriah'ti U Blei, te kumta ka hima ka jong U Blei ka la wan ha phi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Haba u bakhlaiñ uba la kieng atiar bha u ap phira ïa ka ïingbah jong u, kiei kiei ruh kiba don ki jong u ki don ha ka jingskhem.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, ynda uba kham khlaiñ ïa u un wan ïaleh ïa u, bad un jop ïa u, u shim noh ïa ka jingkieng atiar jong u baroh ha kaba u la shaniah, bad u ïabynta ïa ki jinglute jong u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Jar u bymlong bad nga, u ïaleh ïa nga; bad jar u bymïalum bad nga, u pynsaphred.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Haba u mynsiem bymkhuid u la mih noh na u briew, u ïaid ïa ki jaka ryngkhiang, u da wad jaka shongthait; te haba um shem, u ong, ‘Ngan leit phai pat sha la ïing na kaba nga la mih noh.’",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Haba u la wan te, u shem ïa ka, ba la sar, bad ba la buh beit ïa ki jingbuh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, u leit noh, bad u shim lem bad u, sa hynñiew ki mynsiem kiba kham bymman ban ïa u hi; bad haba ki la rung shapoh, ki shong sah hangta; te ka jinglong bakhatduh jong uta u briew ka kham sniew ïa ka banyngkong.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ka la jia ruh, katba u dang kren ïa kine kiei kiei, ba kawei ka briew kaba na uta u paidbah ka la pyrta, bad ka la ong ha u, “Suk kata ka kpoh kaba la pun ïa me, bad ki jymbuiñ ïa kiba me la buiñ!”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hynrei u te u la ong, “Kham suk shisha kita kiba ïohsngew ïa ka ktien ka jong U Blei, bad kiba sumar ruh ïa ka.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te katba kita ki paidbah ki la nang ïalang ha u, u la sdang ban ong, “Kane ka pateng bynriew ka long ka pateng bynriew kaba bymman; ka ïaiwad ïa ka dak, hynrei, yn ym ai ïa ka dak ha ka, hynrei, tang ka dak u Jonah.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Naba kumba u Jonah u la long ka dak ïa ki nong Ninebeh, kumta ruh U Khun u briew un long ïa kane ka pateng bynriew.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ka syiem kaba na shathie kan ïamih lem ha ka jingbishar bad ki briew jong kane ka pateng bynriew, bad kan pynrem ïa ki; naba ka la wan na sha ki bakut ka pyrthei, ïa ka ban ïohsngew ïa ka jingstad u Solomon, bad ha khmih, uba kham khraw ïa u Solomon u don hangne.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ki nong Ninebeh kin ïaïeng lem ha ka jingbishar bad kane ka pateng bynriew, bad kin pynrem ïa ka; naba ki la kylla-ka-bamut da ka jingïalap u Jonah, bad ha khmih, uba kham khraw ïa u Jonah u don hangne.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> “Ym don u briew, haba u la thang ïa ka sharak, uba buh ïa ka hapoh khrum, lymne hapoh ka shang, hynrei, ha ka dieng pynïeng sharak keiñ, ba kita kiba rung hapoh kin ïohi ïa ka jingshai.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ka sharak jong ka met ka long ka khmat: namar kata, haba ka khmat jong me ka long kaba sngur, ka met jong me baroh ruh ka shai bha; hynrei, haba ka long kaba jngut, ka met jong me ruh ka dum.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Namar kata, to sumar ïoh ba kata ka jingshai kaba ha me ka long ka jingdum!",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Haba kumta, lada ka met jong me baroh ka shai bha, bymdon ruh ka bynta ka ba-dum, baroh kan shai bha, kumba haba ka sharak ka pynshai ïa me da ka jingtyngshaiñ jong ka.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te ynda U la lah kren, uwei u Pharisi u la khot ïa U ba un wan bam ja bad u; te haba U la rung U la shong bam.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Hynrei, haba uta u Pharisi u ïohi ïa kata, u la sngewphylla ba um shym thet shuwa, haba un sa bam ja.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u, “Te phi ki Pharisi, phi pynkhuid ïa kaba shabar ka khuri bad ka pliang, hynrei, kaba shapoh jong phi ka dap da ka jingleh-jubor bad ka jinglehsniew.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> A phi ki babieit! Uta uba la thaw ïa kaba shabar, hato um shym la thaw ïa kaba shapoh ruh?",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te hynrei, to ai kum ka jingai isynei na kiei kiei kiba shapoh; te ha khmih, kiei kiei baroh ki long khuid ïa phi.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> “Hynrei, kordit ïa phi ki Pharisi! Naba phi ai ïa kaba shiphew na u pudina, bad na u rue, bad na u jhur baroh, phi ryngkang te ïa ka hok bad ïa ka jingieit ka jong U Blei; ka la dei ban leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, hynrei, ban ym iehnoh keiñ ïa kita kiwei.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Kordit ïa phi ki Pharisi! Naba phi ieit ïa ki jingshong bakor tam ha ki synagog bad ïa ki jingnguh ha ki ïew.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Kordit ïa phi ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi kiba arsap! naba phi long kum ki jingtep ki bym paw, bad ki briew kiba ïaid shalor kim tip ïa kata.”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ynda kumta, uwei na ki riewsaid u da ïathuh u ong ha U, “Ko Nonghikai, da kaba ong ïa kane me krenbeiñ ïa ngi ruh.”",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> U te U la ong, “Kordit ïa phi ruh ki riewsaid! Naba phi pynbah ha ki briew da ki jingkit kiba eh ban bah, phi hi te phim ktah ïa kita ki jingkit da kawei na ki shynriah'ti jong phi.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Kordit ïa phi! Naba phi ïatei ïa ki maw jingtep ki nongïathuhlypa, bad ki kpa jong phi ki la pynïap ïa ki.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Kumta, phi long ki sakhi bad phi ïakohnguh lem ïa ki kam ki kpa jong phi: naba ki, ki la pynïap ïa ki, phi ruh phi ïatei ïa ki maw jingtep jong ki.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Namar kata ruh, ka jingstad jong U Blei ka la ong, ‘Ngan phah sha ki, ïa ki nongïathuhlypa bad ïa ki apostol; te ïa kiba na ki kin pynïap bad kin behbeiñ noh’;",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> ba yn wad noh na kane ka pateng bynriew ïa ka snam jong kita ki nongïathuhlypa baroh, ïa kaba la pynmih na myndanglong ka pyrthei;",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> naduh ka snam u Abel haduh ka snam u Sakharaïa, ïa uba la pynïap hapdeng ka duwan bad ka ïing U Blei; shisha nga ong ha phi: Yn wad noh ïa ka na kane ka pateng bynriew.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Kordit ïa phi ki riewsaid! Naba phi la rah noh ïa u shabi jong ka jingtip: phi hi phim shym la rung shapoh, bad ïa kita kiba dang ïarung phi la khang.”",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Te haba u la mih noh nangta, kita ki nongthoh bad kita ki Pharisi ki la sdang ban ban shikatdei eh ïa u, bad ban pankwah ïa u ban shu kren naphang shaphang kham bun kiei kiei ruh,",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> ki da ap thap ïa u ban ïoh kem daw ei ei na ka shyntur jong u, ba kin dup ïoh mudui ïa u."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Mynkata haba la ïalum lang bun hajar u paidbah, kat ban ïaïuh paralok hi, U la sdang ban ong ha ki synran jong U nyngkong eh, “To kiar noh phi na u thiat ki Pharisi, uba long ka jingarsap.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hynrei, ym don ei ei ruh ba la tap, ïa kaba yn ym pynpaw, bad ba la buhrieh, ïa kaba yn ym pyntip.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Namar kata, ïa kano kano ba phi la ong ha ka jingdum, yn pynsngew ha ka jingshai; bad ïa kaba phi la ïathuh ha ka shkor ha ki pulit, yn ïalap halor ki ïing.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Nga ong ruh ha phi ki lok jong nga: wat sheptieng ïa kita kiba pynïap noh ïa ka met, bad ki bymdon ei ei nalor kata ba ki lah ban leh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, ngan maham ïa phi ïano phin sheptieng: To sheptieng ïa uta uba hadien kaba u la pynïap, u don bor ban bred sha dujok; shisha nga ong ha phi: To sheptieng keiñ ïa uta.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hato ym ju die shi anna san tylli ki sim ïing? Pleng kawei ruh na ki, kam long kaba la klet ha khmat U Blei.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, wat ïa u 'ñiuh khlieh jong phi baroh la ñiew. Namar kata, wat sheptieng; phi long kham kor ïa shibun ki sim ïing.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nga ong ruh ha phi, “Uno uno baroh u ban phla ïa nga ha khmat ki briew, te ïa uta, U Khun u briew ruh un phla ha khmat ki angel U Blei.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, jar uba len ïa nga ha khmat ki briew, yn len noh ïa u ha khmat ki angel U Blei.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te uno uno baroh u ban kren ka ktien pyrshah ïa U Khun u briew, yn map ïa u, hynrei, ïa uta uba krenbeiñ ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid, yn ym map.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ynda kin ïalam ïa phi ha khmat ki synagog bad ki nongbishar bad ki nongsynshar, wat sngewkhuslai phi, kumno lane kaei ba phin ïasaid-da, lane kaei ba phin ong:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> naba U Mynsiem Bakhuid un hikai ïa phi ha kata ka por, ïa kaei ba phi dei ban ong.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te uwei na uta u paidbah u la ong ha U, “Ko Nonghikai, to ong ha u para jong nga ban ïabynta noh ïa ka bri bad nga.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U te U la ong ha u, “Ko briew, uei ba la pynlong ïa nga u nongbishar, lane u nongpynïabynta halor jong phi?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “To sumar, to kiar ruh na ka jingkwah lalot baroh: namar ka jingim u briew kam shong satia ha ka jingdap kyrhai jong kiei kiei kiba u don.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U la kren ruh ka pharshi ha ki, u da ong, “Ka bri uwei u briew u bariewspah ka la sei bha shibun.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u la puson ha lade, u da ong, ‘Kumno ngan leh? naba ngam don jaka ha kaba ngan lum ïa ki soh jong nga.’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U la ong te, ‘Ïa kane ngan leh: ngan lied ïa ki thiar jong nga, bad ngan tei ïa kiba kham khraw; te hangta ngan lum ïa u Kew jong nga bad ïa ki mar jong nga baroh:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad ngan ong ha la ka mynsiem: Ko mynsiem, pha don shibun kiei kiei ba la buh lypa ïa bun snem; to shongsuk, to bam, to dih, to leh kmen.’",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, U Blei u la ong ha u, ‘A me u babieit, ha kane ka miet yn pan noh ïa ka mynsiem jong me na me; ki jongno te kin long kita kiei kiei ïa kiba me la khreh lypa?’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, u long uta uba kynshew lypa ïa lade, hynrei, u bymlong riewbha sha U Blei.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki synran jong u, “Namar kata, nga ong ha phi: Wat khuslai shaphang ka jingim jong phi, kaei ba phin bam, lymne shaphang ka met ruh, kaei ba phin kup.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar ka jingim ka kham kor ïa ka jingbam, bad ka met ïa ka jaiñkup.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> To khmih thuh ïa ki tyngab! ba kim ïabet, lymne kim ïa-ot, ki bymdon ka ïing kynshew, lymne ka thiar, hynrei, U Blei u bsa ïa ki. Kaba katno tam phi kham kor ma phi ïa ki kynja sim?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Uno na phi ruh, da kaba u khuslai, uba lah ban pyntam shi pruh ïa la ka rynïeng?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Namar kata, lada phim lah wat ïa kaba rit tam eh, phi khuslai lei te shaphang kiwei kiwei ruh?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Khmih thuh ïa ki 'tiew Lili kumno ba ki man; kim trei bri, lymne kim thir; pynban, nga ong ha phi, ba wat u Solomon ha ka burom jong u baroh, um shym la kup kat uwei na kine.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Lada U Blei te u pynkup kumta ïa u phlang, uba mynta u long, lashai te la bred ha ka lawar ding, kaba katno tam un pynkup ïa phi, A phi kiba rit ka jingngeit?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Phi te wat wad ïa kaei ba phin bam, lane ïa kaei ba phin dih, phi wat khuslai artatien ruh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Naba ïa kine kiei kiei baroh ki jaid bynriew jong ka pyrthei ki ïawad; hynrei, U Kpa jong phi u tip ba phi donkam ïa kine kiei kiei ruh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, phi to ïawad ïa ka hima ka jong U Blei; te ïa kine kiei kiei baroh yn sa ai lang tam ha phi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “To wat sheptieng, ko kynhun i barit; naba U Kpa jong phi u sngewbha eh ban ai ha phi ïa kata ka hima.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> To die noh ïa kiei kiei ki jong phi, to ai jingai isynei ruh; to thaw ïa lade ki jingpan ki ban ym man rim, ka jingkynshew keiñ ha ki bneng ka ban ym lut noh, sha kaba u nongtuh um wan hajan, lymne ka khñiang kam pynjot.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Naba ha kaba long ka jingkynshew jong phi, hangta kan long ruh ka dohnud jong phi.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “To long kiba la panpoh ïa la ki syngkai, bad ba la thang ïa ki sharak jong phi;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> phi hi ruh kum ki briew kiba ïa-ap khmih ïa u kynrad jong ki, lano un wan phai na ka jingkhawai shongkurim; ba haba u la wan bad ba u la tied, kin plie ïa u kumne kumne ruh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Suk kita ki shakri, ïa kiba haba u wan u kynrad, un shem ba ki dang ïasharai; shisha nga ong ha phi, ba un panpoh ïa lade, bad un pynshong bam ïa ki, bad un wan bad un shakri ruh ïa ki.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad lada un wan ha ka ba-ar jingap miet, lane ha ka balai, bad un shem ruh ïa ki kumta, suk keiñ kita ki shakri.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Hynrei, ïa kane to tip, ba lada u trai ïing u la lah tip ha kano ka por ba wan u nongtuh, un da la ap, bad un ym da ieh ban prat ïa ka ïing jong u.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Phi ruh to long kiba la kloi; naba ha ka por ba phim mut, ba u wan U Khun u briew.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> U Petros te u la ong, “Ko Trai, me kren ha ngi ïa kane ka pharshi, ne ha ki baroh de?”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong, “Uno te uba long u sordar uba lah ban shaniah bad u bastad, ïa uba u kynrad jong u un buh halor kiba ha ïing jong u, ïa ka ban ai ha ki, ïa la ka bynta ka jingbam ha ka por babiang?",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Suk uta u shakri, ïa uba u kynrad jong u haba u wan, un shem ba u leh kumta.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba un buh ïa u halor kiei kiei baroh kiba u don.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Hynrei, lada uta u shakri un ong ha la ka dohnud, ‘U Kynrad jong nga u tud ban wan’; bad un sdang ban shoh ïa ki shakri shynrang bad kynthei, bad ban bam ban dih, bad ban buaid de;",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> u kynrad jong uta u shakri un wan ha ka sngi ha kaba um khmih lynti, bad ha ka por ha kaba um tip, te un sympat jur eh ïa u, bad un buh ïa ka bynta jong u bad ki bymngeit.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Uta u shakri te uba la tip ïa ka mon u kynrad jong u, bad u bym shym la pynkhreh, lymne leh katba kum ka mon jong u, yn sympat ïa u da ki bun thri.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Hynrei, uta u bym shym tip, bad uba la leh ïa kaba dei ban ïoh sympat da ki thri, yn sympat ïa u khyndiat thri. Naba ha uno uno ha uba la ai shibun, na uta yn pan shibun; bad ha uba ki la aiti shibun, na uta kin pan kaba kham bun keiñ.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> “Nga la wan ïa ka ban shat ding ha ka pyrthei; bad nga mon aïu, lada la pynmeh lypa noh ïa ka?",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Hynrei, nga don ka jingbaptis da kaba yn pynbaptis ïa nga; te katno nga sngewkhuslai tad ynda ba la pyndep ïa kata!",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Phi mut ba nga la wan ïa ka ban ai ka jingsuk ha ka pyrthei? Nga ong ïa phi, Em, hynrei, ka jingïaleh makynti pynban.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Naba naduh mynta kin long san ngut ha kawei ka ïing kiba ïaleh makynti paralok, lai ngut ki ïaleh ïa ki ar ngut, ar ngut ruh ki ïaleh ïa ki lai ngut.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Kin ïaleh makynti u kpa bad la u khun, u khun ruh bad la u kpa; ka kmie bad la ka khun, ka khun ruh bad la ka kmie; ka kiaw kurim bad la ka pyrsa kurim, ka pyrsa kurim ruh bad la ka kiaw kurim.”",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Te u la ong ha kita ki paidbah ruh, “Haba phi ïohi ïa u lyoh ba mih na sepngi, kumne kumne ruh phi ong, ‘U slap kyrthep un wan’; ka jia kumta ruh.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Bad haba ka lyer na shathie ka beh, phi ong, ‘Kan sa shit kyr-ang’; ka long ruh.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> A phi kiba arsap, phi tip ban bishar thuh ïa ka khmat jong ka khyndew bad jong ka bneng; hynrei, kumno ba phim nang ban bishar ïa kane ka aïom?",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> “Balei ruh wat na lade hi ba phim bishar kaei kaba dei?",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Naba katba me dang leit lem bad uba ïaleh bad me sha u nongsynshar, to pyrshang biang ha lynti ban ïohlait suk na u; ïoh ba un ring noh ïa me ha u nongbishar, bad uta u nongbishar un ai noh ïa me ha u nongap byndi, bad uta u nongap byndi un bred ïa me ha ka byndi.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Nga ong ha me: men ym mih noh nangta, haba da lei lei ruh, tad ynda me la siew ïa ka damli ka bakhatduh eh.”"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha kata hi ka por ki la don kiba ïathuh ha u shaphang ki nong Galilaïa, kiba u Pilat u la lah khleh lang ïa ka snam jong ki bad ki jingkñia jong ki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te U Jisu u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ki, “Phi mut ba kine ki nong Galilaïa ki la kham pop ban ïa ki nong Galilaïa baroh, namar ba ki la shah ïa kine kiei kiei?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Nga ong ha phi, Em; hynrei lymda phi kylla-ka-bamut, phi baroh phin jot noh kumjuh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lane kita ki khatphra ngut, ha kiba la hap ka ïing phira kaba ha Siloam, kaba la pynïap noh ruh ïa ki, phi mut ba kita ki la long kiba kham pop ban ïa ki briew baroh kiba shong sah ha Jerusalem?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nga ong ha phi, Em; hynrei, lymda phi kylla-ka-bamut, phi baroh phin jot noh kumjuh.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U la kren ïa kane ka pharshi: “Uwei u briew u la don u dieng Dumbur ïa uba u la thung ha ka brisoh jong u; bad u la wan wad soh ha u, te um shem ei ei.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u la ong ïa u nongsumar brisoh, ‘Ha khmih, kine lai snem nga wan wad soh ha une u dieng Dumbur, te ngam shem satia; to khet noh ïa u, balei ba u pynlehnohei ruh ïa ka khyndew?’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U da ïathuh te u la ong ha u, ‘Ko Trai, to ieh ïa u sa ha kane ka snem ruh, tad ynda ngan tih sawdong ïa u, bad ba ngan ai sboh ruh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Lada un sei soh, te bha; hynrei lym kumta, men sa khet noh ïa u.’ ”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba u dang hikai ha kawei na ki synagog ha ka sngi Sabbaton,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ha khmih, la don ka briew kaba la don u mynsiem ka jingkhrew jin khatphra snem, kaba la dor ryngkdung ruh katba kam lah shuh ban pynbeit ïa lade.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Haba U Jisu te u la ïohi ïa ka, u la khot ïa ka, bad u la ong ha ka, “Ko kynthei, la pyllait noh ïa pha na ka jingkhrew jong pha.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U la buh ruh ïa la ki kti ha ka, bad kumne kumne ruh la pynïeng beit ïa ka, te ka la pyndonburom ïa U Blei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, u nongsynshar ka synagog ba u da sngewbitar eh, namar ba U Jisu u la lah pynkhiah ha ka Sabbaton, u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha u paidbah, “Don hynriew sngi ha kiba ki briew ki dei ban trei jingtrei; ha kita namar kata, to wan ba yn pynkhiah ïa phi, te ym ha ka sngi Sabbaton.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, U Trai u la ïathuh ha u, bad U la ong, “Phi kiba arsap, hato phi baroh ha ka sngi Sabbaton phim ju pyllait na sem ïa la u masi lane ka kadda, bad ïalam dih um ruh?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ïa kane ka briew te, kaba long ka khun u Abraham, ïa kaba u Soitan u la khum, ha khmih, jin khatphra snem, kam dei ban pyllait ïa ka na kane ka jingkhum ha ka sngi Sabbaton?”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te katba U dang kren ïa kine kiei kiei, la pynsngewlehrain ïa ki nongïaleh pyrshah jong U baroh, hynrei, u paidbah baroh u la leh kmen namar kiei kiei baroh kiba phylla kiba U la leh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U la ong ruh, “Ka hima jong U Blei ka long syriem ïa kaei? bad kum kaei ngan pynsyriem ïa ka?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ka long kum u symbai tyrso, ïa uba haba u briew u la shim, u la bred ha ka kper jong u; te u la mih bad u la nang long dieng, bad ki sim bneng ki la ïashong tngen ha ki tnat jong u.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U la ong pat ruh, “Kum kaei ngan pynsyriem ïa ka hima U Blei?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ka long kum u thiat, ïa uba ka la shim ka briew bad ka la btep ha ki lai pyrha u 'purew, tad ynda ka la sieb baroh.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te U la nang leit la ka jingleit sha Jerusalem, U da hikai katba U nang ïaid lyngba ïa ki nongbah bad ïa ki nongrit.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Uwei te u la kylli ïa U, “Ko Trai, hato ki long khyndiat ïa kiba yn pynim?” U te U la ong ïa ki,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “To pyneh ban bsut lyngba ïa ka khyrdop kaba khim; naba shibun, nga ong ïa phi, kin ïawad ban bsut hapoh, te kim ym lah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te haba shi sien ba u trai ïing u la ïeng, bad u la khang ïa ka jingkhang, bad ba phin sdang ban ïeng shabar bad ban tied ïa ka jingkhang, phi da ong, ‘A Trai, A Trai, to plie ïa ngi’; u te un ïathuh un ong ha phi, ‘Ïa phi ngam ithuh, phi nangno.’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, phin sdang ban ong, ‘Ngi la ïabam ngi la ïadih ruh ha khmat jong me, me la hikai ruh ha ki lynti bah jong ngi.’",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, un ong, ‘Nga ong ïa phi, ngam ithuh ïa phi, phi nangno; khie leit noh na nga, phi baroh ki nongkam bymman.’",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hangta kan long kaba lynñiar bad kaba kum dait bniat, ynda phin ïohi ïa u Abraham, bad ïa u Isaak, bad ïa u Jakob, bad ïa ki nongïathuhlypa baroh, ha ka hima U Blei, te ïa phi hi ba la shop noh shabar.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kin ïawan ruh na mihngi bad na sepngi, bad na shatei bad na shathie, kin ïashong shaniah ruh ha ka hima jong U Blei.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ha khmih ruh, don ki bakhatduh ki ban sa long ki bashuwa, don ki bashuwa ruh, ki ban sa long ki bakhatduh.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ha kata kajuh ka por kiba na ki Pharisi ki la ïawan ki da ong ha u, “To mih noh, to leit noh ruh nangne, naba u Herod u kwah ban pynïap noh ïa me.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u la ong ïa ki, “Khie leit ïathuh ha uta u myrsiang, ‘Ha khmih, nga beh noh ïa ki ksuid, nga trei ruh ïa ki kam pynkhiah mynta bad lashai, te ha ka balai ka sngi yn sa pynjanai ïa nga.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> La kumta ruh, nga dei hi ban nang leit la ka jingleit mynta bad lashai bad ha kaba bud; naba kam lah ban long ba u nongïathuhlypa un ïap noh shabar ka Jerusalem.’",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> A Jerusalem, Jerusalem, kaba pynïap noh ïa ki nongïathuhlypa, kaba lynthem maw ruh ïa kiba la phah ha pha! Katno sien nga la mon ban kdup ïa ki khun jong pha, kumba ka syiar ka kdup ïa la ki khun hapoh ki thapniang jong ka! phi te phim mon.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ha khmih, ïa ka ïing jong phi la iehnoh ïingjah ha phi. Bad nga ong ïa phi: Phin ym ïohi ïa nga tad ynda phin ong, ‘Long ba la kyrkhu uta uba wan ha ka kyrteng U Trai.’ ”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba U la leit hapoh ka ïing uwei na ki nongsynshar, uba na ki Pharisi, ban bam jingbam ha ka Sabbaton, ba ki la ïathap ïa U.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ha khmih ruh, don ha khmat jong U, uwei u briew uba la pang at top.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te U Jisu u da ïathuh U la ong ha ki riewsaid bad ha ki Pharisi, U da kylli, “Ka dei ne em ban pynkhiah ha ka Sabbaton?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki te ki la shu sngap jar. Te U la shim ïa u, U la pynkhiah ïa u bad U la pyllait noh ruh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad U la ong ha ki, “Uei na phi uba don kadda lane masi ba la hap ha ka thliew, u ban ym paring habar ïa u kumne kumne ruh ha ka sngi Sabbaton?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te kim nang shuh ban phai ktien kylliang shaphang kine kiei kiei.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u la kren ka pharshi ha kita ïa kiba la khot, haba u la khmih thuh kumno ba ki ïajied ïa ki jaka shong ba kham donburom, u da ong ïa ki,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Haba uno uno u khot ïa me sha ka jingkhawai shongkurim, wat shong ha ka jaka bakor tam, ïoh don lehse uba kham donburom ban ïa me ba la khot da u;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad ba uta uba la khot ïa me bad ïa u un wan, bad un ong ïa me, ‘To ai jaka ïa une’; ynda kumta te, men sdang da kaba lehrain ban shim ïa ka jaka kaba kham poh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, haba la khot ïa me, leit shong ha ka jaka kaba kham poh; ba ynda un wan uta uba la khot ïa me, un ïoh ong ïa me, ‘Ko lok, to kiew sha kaba kham haneng’; haba kumta, men ïoh burom ha khmat kita baroh kiba ïashong bam lem bad me.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Naba ïa uno uno baroh uba pynkhraw ïa lade, yn pynpoh; te ïa uba pynpoh ïa lade, yn pynkhraw.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te U la ong ruh ha uta uba la khot ïa U, “Haba me khreh ïa ka jingkhawai mynsngi ne mynmiet, wat khot ïa ki lok jong me, lymne ïa ki hynmen hynbew jong me lymne ïa ki kur jong me, lymne ïa ki paramarjan bariewspah jong me, ïoh lehse ki ruh kin khot kylliang ïa me, bad kumta kan long noh ka jingsiew kylliang ïa me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, haba me khreh ïa ka jingkhawai, khot ïa ki baduk, ïa ki bakynriang, ïa ki ba-dkoh, ïa ki bamatlah:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> kumta men long uba suk; namar kim don ei ei ruh ban siew kylliang ïa me; naba yn siew kylliang ïa me ha ka jingmihpat jong ki bahok.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te haba uwei na kita kiba ïashong bam lem u la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei, u la ong ha U, “Suk uta u ban bam jingbam ha ka hima U Blei!”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U te U la ong ha u, “Don uwei u briew uba la khreh ïa ka jingkhawai miet kaba khraw, bad u la khot bun briew.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la phah ïa la u shakri ha ka por kata ka jingkhawai miet, ïa ka ban ong ha kita ïa kiba la khot, ‘To wan, naba la lah khreh ïa kiei kiei baroh.’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te baroh ki la sdang na kawei ka jingmut ban ïakren dong. Uba nyngkong u la ong ïa u, ‘Nga la thied ïa ka lyngkha, nga donkam ruh ban leit jngoh ïa ka; nga kyrpad ïa me, to pyllait ïa nga.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Uwei pat ruh u la ong, ‘Nga la thied san jur ki masi, ngan sa leit ruh ïa ka ban tynjuh ïa ki; nga kyrpad ïa me, to pyllait ïa nga.’",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Uwei pat de u la ong, ‘Nga la shongkurim ïa ka briew, te namar kata, ngam lah ban wan.’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te uta u shakri u la wan bad u la ïathuh ha u kynrad jong u ïa kine kiei kiei ruh. Ynda kumta, uta u trai ïing ba u da sngewbitar, u la ong ha la u shakri, ‘Khie leit kumne kumne ruh sha ki lynti bah bad ki lynti rit ka shnong, bad wallam shapoh shane ïa ki baduk, ki bakynriang, ki bamatlah, bad ïa ki ba-dkoh.’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Uta u shakri te u la ong, ‘Ko Kynrad, la leh kumba me la hukum: hynrei, dang don jaka.’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Uta u kynrad u la ong te ha uta u shakri, ‘Khie leit sha ki lynti bah bad ki lynti lyngkha, to pynbor ïa ki ban wan hapoh, ba yn pyndap ïa ka ïing jong nga.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Naba nga ong ïa phi ba ym don uwei na kita ki briew ïa kiba la khot, u ban ïoh mad ïa ka jingkhawai miet jong nga.’ ”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te bun ki paidbah ki la ïaleit lem bad u; bad haba u la kyrtiang dien, u la ong ha ki,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Lada uno uno ruh u wan ha nga, bad u bym isih ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie, bad ïa la ka tnga bad ïa la ki khun, bad ïa la ki hynmen hynbew ruh shynrang bad kynthei, ho-oid bad ïa la ka jong ka jingim ruh, um lah ban long u synran jong nga.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Uno uno ruh de u bym bah ruh ïa la ka jong ka diengphna, bad ba wan bud nadien jong nga, um lah ban long u synran jong nga.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Naba uno na phi uba mut ban tei ïa ka kut, u bym da shong khop shuwa ban kheiñ ïa kaba lut, la u don biang ne em ïa ka ban pyndep?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ïoh, haba u la seng ïa ka nongrim bad ba um lah ban pyndep, baroh kiba ïohi kin sdang ban ïarkhiebeiñ ïa u,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ki da ong, ‘Une u briew u la sdang ban tei, te um lah du ban pyndep.’",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Lane uno u syiem haba u leit ban ïaleh thma bad uwei pat u syiem, u bym da shong khop shuwa ban pyrkhat bha, la u lah ne em da ki shiphew hajar, ban ïeng ïaleh bad uta uba wan ïaleh ïa u da ki arphew hajar?",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Lymda kumta, mynba uta uwei u dang jngai, u da phah noh ïa ki nongleit pan ïasuk, u pan ruh da kaba kumno ban ïasuk noh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kumta ruh, uno uno uba na phi, u bymñiew duh noh ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba u don, um lah ban long u synran jong nga.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Ka mluh ka bha: hynrei, lada ka mluh ka la kylla blad, da ei yn pynthiang ïa ka?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kam bit, lymne ïa ka khyndew, lymne ïa ka thliew sboh; hynrei, ki bred noh shabar ïa ka. Uba don ki shkor ban sngew, to un sngew.”"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki nongkhrong bad ki bapop baroh ki la wan hajan jong u ban ïohsngew ïa u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hynrei, ki Pharisi bad ki nongthoh ki la ïakhñium eh, ki da ong, “Pleng une u briew u pdiang sngewbha ïa ki bapop, bad u bam lem bad ki.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u la kren ïa kane ka pharshi ha ki, u da ong,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Uno u briew na phi uba don shispah ki langbrot, bad lada jah noh kawei na ki, u bym iehnoh ïa ki khyndaiphew khyndai ha lum bad leit wad ïa kata kaba la jah noh, ha ban da shem ïa ka?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba u la shem ïa ka, u buh ïa ka halor ki tyrpeng jong u da kaba sngewkmen.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ynda u poi sha la ïing, u khot lang ïa la ki lok bad ïa la ki paramarjan, u da ong ha ki, ‘To ïakmen lem bad nga, naba nga la shem ïa ka langbrot jong nga kaba la jah noh.’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nga ong ïa phi, ba kumta ka jingkmen kan long ha bneng na ka bynta uwei u bapop uba kylla-ka-bamut, ban ïa na ka bynta ki khyndaiphew khyndai ki bahok, ki bymdonkam ïa ka jingkylla-ka-bamut.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Lane kano ka briew kaba don shiphew suka, lada ka la jah noh shi suka, kan ym thang ïa ka sharak, bad sar ïa ka ïing, bad wad biang biang ruh ha ban da shem ïa ka?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba ka la shem, ka khot lang ïa la ki lok bad la ki paramarjan, ka da ong, ‘To ïakmen lem bad nga, naba nga la shem ïa kata ka suka kaba nga la lah jah noh.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, nga ong ïa phi, ba ka jingkmen ka long ha khmat ki angel U Blei na ka bynta uwei u bapop uba kylla-ka-bamut.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U la ong ruh, “Don uwei u briew uba don ar ngut ki khun shynrang:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> uba kham poh te na ki, u la ong ha u kpa jong u, ‘Ko Pa, to ai ha nga ïa ka bynta kaba hap ïa nga na kaei kaei kaba don.’ Te u la pynïabynta ha ki, ïa la ka jingim.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ym bun sngi hadien kata, uta u khun uba kham poh u la lum lang ïa kiei kiei baroh, bad u la leit jingleit sha ka ri kaba jngai, bad hangta u la pynsyrwa noh ïa ka bynta jong u, ba u da leh sarong awria.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ynda u la pynlut ïa kiei kiei baroh, la jia 'nemsniew kaba khraw ha kata ka ri, u ruh u la sdang ban sngewkyrduh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, u la leit ïalok bad uwei na ki trai-shnong kata ka ri: te uta u la phah ïa u sha ki lyngkha jong u, ban ap sniang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u da kwah eh ban pynkdang ïa la ka kpoh da kita ki kop soh dieng ïa kiba ju bam ki sniang; te ym don ba ai ïa u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, ynda u la kynmaw bynriew, u la ong, ‘Katno ngut ki shakri u kpa jong nga, kiba don ka jingbam kyrhai, nga seh hangne ngan sa ïap thngan!",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ngan ïeng joit, bad ngan leit sha la u kpa, bad ngan ong ha u: “Ko Pa, nga la leh pop ïa ka bneng, bad ha khmat jong me;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> te ngam long shuh uba dei ba yn khot u khun jong me; to pynlong ïa nga kum uwei na ki shakri jong me.” ’",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u la ïeng joit, bad u la leit sha la u kpa. Hynrei, haba u dang jngai ruh, u kpa jong u, u la ïohi ïa u, bad u la sngewsynei, bad u la mareh, u la dem ruh ha ka ryndang jong u, bad u la ïaidoh ïa u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te uta u khun u la ong ïa u, ‘Ko Pa, nga la leh pop ïa ka bneng, bad ha khmat jong me, te ngam long shuh uba dei ba yn khot u khun jong me.’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, u kpa u la ong ïa ki shakri jong u, ‘Wallam kloi ïa ka jaiñkup kaba kor tam, bad to pynkup ïa u, to buh ruh ïa ka sa'ti ha ka kti jong u, bad ïa ki juti ha ki kjat jong u,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad to wallam ïa uta u khun masi ba la pynsngaid, to pynïap ruh, to ngin ïabam ngin ïalehkmen ruh;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> naba une u khun jong nga u la long uba la ïap, te u la im pat; bad u la long uba la jah noh, te la shem pat ïa u.’ Kumta ki la sdang ban ïalehkmen.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Te uta u khun nyngkong jong u, u la don ha lyngkha: te katba u nang wan bad u nang hajan kata ka ïing, u la ïohsngew ïa ki jingput jingtem bad ïa ka jingshad.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u la khot ïa uwei na kita ki shakri, bad u la kylli, ‘Ki mut aïu kine kiei kiei?’",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U te u la ïathuh ha u, ‘La wan u para jong me, te u kpa jong me u la pynïap ïa uta u khun masi ba la pynsngaid, naba u la ïoh pdiang pat ïa u, u bakoit bakhiah.’",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hynrei, u, u la bitar, bad um mon ban rung hapoh; namar kata, u kpa jong u, u la mih habar bad u la khroh ïa u.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha la u kpa, ‘Ha khmih, la katta snem nga shakri ïa me, bad mynno mynno ruh ngam ju palat ïa ka hukum jong me; pynban, mynno mynno ruh mem ju ai ha nga wat ïa i khun blang, ba ngan ïoh ïalehkmen bad ki lok jong nga!",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, haba la wan une u khun jong me, uba la bam duh ïa ka jingim jong me bad ki nuti, me la pynïap na ka bynta jong u ïa uta u khun masi ba la pynsngaid!’",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> U te u la ong ïa u, ‘Ko khun, ha la ka sngi me don lem bad nga, bad kiei kiei baroh ki jong nga ki long ki jong me.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ka la dei ban ïalehkmen bad ban ïalehsngewbha; naba une u para jong me u la long uba la ïap, te u la im pat, bad u la long uba la jah noh, te la shem pat ïa u.’ ”"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U la ong ruh de ha ki synran jong u: “La don uwei u briew u bariewspah, uba la don u sordar; bad ïa une la mudui ha u ba u da pynsyrwa noh ïa kiei kiei kiba don ki jong u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u la khot ïa u, bad u la ong ha u, ‘Kaei kane ba nga ïohsngew shaphang jong me? To ai jingkheiñ ïa ka kam sordar jong me; naba mem lah shuh ban long sordar.’",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ynda kumta, uta u sordar u la ong ha lade, ‘Kumno ngan leh, naba u kynrad jong nga un sa shim noh ïa ka kam sordar na nga? ban puh khyndew ngam lah, ban leit makia nga sngewlehrain.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nga la kut jingmut kumno ngan leh, ba, haba yn bidai noh ïa nga na ka kam sordar, kin khot ei ïa nga sha ki ïing jong ki.’",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba u la phah khot ha u ïa uwei pa uwei na kiba kit ram na u kynrad jong u, u la kylli ïa u banyngkong, ‘Katno me kit ram na u kynrad jong nga?’",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U te u la ong, ‘Shispah mon ka umphniang.’ Te u la ong ïa u, ‘To shim ïa la ka kot kular, shong ruh kumne kumne bad thoh sanphew.’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, u la kylli ïa uwei pat, ‘Me ruh katno me kit ram?’ U te u la ong, ‘Shispah mon u Kew.’ U ong ïa u ruh, ‘To shim ïa la ka kot kular, thoh ruh phraphew.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u kynrad jong u, u la ïaroh ïa uta u sordar bymhok, namar ba u la leh sian; naba ki khun jong kane ka pyrthei ki kham sian ha la ka pateng bynriew hi, ban ïa ki khun ka jingshai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nga ong ruh ha phi: To pynlong ïa lade ki lok da ka spah bymhok, ba ynda la poi ka bakut, kin pdiang ïa phi sha kita ki ïing bymjukut.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Jar uba long uba lah ban shaniah ha iba khyndiat eh, u long uba lah ban shaniah ha kaba shibun ruh: bad jar uba long u bymhok ha iba khyndiat eh, u long u bymhok ha kaba shibun ruh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Namar kata, lada phim shym la long kiba lah ban shaniah shaphang ka spah bymhok, uei u ban shaniah ha phi ïa ka spah kaba shisha?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad lada phim shym la long kiba lah ban shaniah bad ka jong uwei pat, uei u ban aiti ha phi ïa kata kaba long ka jong phi?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ym don u shakri uba lah ban shakri ar ngut ki kynrad: naba lane un isih ïa uwei, bad un ieit ïa uta uwei pat; lane un bat ïa uwei, bad un lyndet ïa uta uwei pat. Phim lah keiñ ban shakri ïa U Blei bad ïa ka spah.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kita ki Pharisi ruh, kiba ieit sbai eh, ki la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei baroh, te ki la pynran beiñ ïa la ki khmut ïa u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u la ong ïa ki, “Phi long kita kiba pynksan ïa lade ha khmat ki briew, hynrei, U Blei u ithuh ïa ki dohnud jong phi, naba kata ïa kaba la ñiewkor ha ki briew, ka long kaba ijli ha khmat U Blei.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Ka Hukum bad Ki Nongïathuhlypa ki la long haduh u Ïoannis: naduh kata ka por la ïalap ïa ka gospel ka hima U Blei, bad u briew baroh u rung jubor hapoh jong ka.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, kan kham jem ïa ka bneng bad ïa ka khyndew ban dam noh, ban ïa ka ban duh noh iwei iba khun khyndiat  na kata Ka Hukum.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Uno uno ruh uba pyllait noh ïa ka tnga jong u, bad u shongkurim ïa kawei pat, u klim: bad uta uba shongkurim ïa kata kaba la pyniehnoh na u tnga, u ruh u klim.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Te la don uwei u briew u bariewspah, bad u la ju kup da ka jaiñ saw bthuh bad ka jaiñ linen bani, u da leh pahuh eh ruh ha la ka sngi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> La don ruh uwei u nongkhrong uba kyrteng ‘u Lasaros’, uba la tap da ki tohjaw, ïa uba la ju buh ha ka khyrdop jong uta,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad uba la ju sngewkwah ban pynkdang ïa lade na ki lyngkhot lyngkhai kiba ju hap na ka miej jong uta u bariewspah; shisha wat ki ksew ki la ju wan jliah noh ïa ki tohjaw jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ka la jia te, ba uta u nongkhrong u la ïap noh, bad ba la bah noh ïa u da ki angel sha ka shadem u Abraham. Uta u bariewspah ruh u la ïap noh de, bad la tep ïa u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ha dujok u la khmied ïa la ki khmat, haba u long ha ki jingkordit, bad u la ïohi ïa u Abraham na jngai, bad ïa u Lasaros ha ka shadem jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u la pyrta bad u la ong, ‘Ko Kpa Abraham, to isynei ïa nga, to phah ruh ïa u Lasaros ba un wieh ïa ka khmut shynriah'ti jong u ha ka um, ba un ïoh pynkhriat ïa u thylliej jong nga; naba la pynkordit ïa nga ha kane ka thylliej ding.’",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Abraham u la ïathuh, ‘A khun, to kynmaw ba ma me katba me dang im, me la ïoh pdiang ïa kiei kiei ki babha ki jong me, kumjuh ruh u Lasaros ïa kiei kiei ki basniew; hynrei, mynta hangne ïa u la pyntngen, ïa me te la pynkordit.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Nalor kine baroh ruh putet, la buh skhem ïa ka kharai kaba khraw hapdeng jong ngi bad jong phi, ba kumta, kita kiba kwah ban leit sha shiliang nangne sha phi, kim lah, lymne kita kiba nangto, kim lah wan sha shiliang sha ngi.’",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U te u la ong, ‘Haba kumta, nga kyrpad ïa me, ko kpa, ba men phah ïa u sha ka ïing u kpa jong nga,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> naba nga don san ngut ki para; ba un ïoh maham ïa ki, ba ïoh ki ruh kin wan sha kane ka jaka ka jingkordit.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Hynrei, u Abraham u ong, ‘Ki don u Moses bad Ki Nongïathuhlypa; ai kin sngew ïa ki keiñ.’",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U te u la ong, ‘Ym kumta, ko kpa Abraham, hynrei, lada uwei na ki nongïap un leit sha ki, kin sa kylla-ka-bamut.’",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> U la ïathuh te ha u, ‘Lada kim sngap ïa u Moses bad Ki Nongïathuhlypa, kin ym ngeit ruh wat lada mihpat uwei na ki nongïap.’ ”"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki synran, “Ka long ka bym lah ïa ki jingjynthut ïa ka ban ym wan, hynrei, kordit ïa uta da uba ki wan!",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka la kham bha ïa u lada yn teh da u mawtylliat uba khraw ha ka ryndang jong u, bad yn bred ïa u ha duriaw, ban ïa kaba un pynthut ïa uwei na kine ki barit!",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> To ïasumar ïa lade; lada u paralok jong me u leh pop ïa me, to sneng ïa u; bad lada u kylla-ka-bamut, to men map ïa u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lada u leh pop ïa me hynñiew sien shi sngi ruh, bad hynñiew sien shi sngi ruh u phai sha me, da kaba ong, ‘Nga kylla-ka-bamut’, men map ïa u.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te kita ki apostol ki la ong ha U Trai, “To pynroi ïa ka jingngeit jong ngi!”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Trai te u la ong, “Lada phi don ka jingngeit kaba kat iwei i symbai tyrso, phi lah ban ong ïa une u dieng Dumbur, ‘Long me ïa uba la rat noh, bad ïa uba la thung ha duriaw’, te un da la kohnguh ïa phi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Hynrei, uno na phi uba don u shakri uba lur, lane uba ap jingri, u ban ong ha uta haba u la wan na lyngkha, ‘Ale kumne kumne da shong bam?’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, un ym kham ong pynban ïa u, ‘To da khreh ïa kaei kaei ruh ïa kaba ngan bam ja miet; to da panpoh ïa lade, shakri ruh ïa nga, tad ynda nga la bam bad nga la dih; hadien kata, me ruh men sa bam bad men sa dih?’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U sngewnguh ne em ïa uta u shakri, naba u la leh ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba la hukum ïa u? Nga mut, em.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumjuh ruh ma phi, ynda phi la leh ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba la hukum ïa phi, phin ong, ‘Ngi long ki shakri ba khlem dawa, naba ngi la leh tang ïa kaba dei ïa ngi ban leh.’ ”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba u dang leit sha Jerusalem, ba u la leit lyngba ruh napdeng ka ri Samaria bad ka ri Galilaïa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba u dang leit hapoh kawei ka shnong, shiphew ngut ki rangbah ki bapang 'thohlieh ki la ïawan tan ïa u, ki da ïeng na jngai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ki la ïapyrta jam, ki da ong, “Ko Jisu kynrad, to isynei ïa ngi.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba u la ïohi ïa ki, u la ong ïa ki, “Khie leit pyni ïa lade ha ki lyngdoh.” Ka la jia te, ba katba ki dang ïaleit, la pynkhuid ïa ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Uwei te na ki, haba u la ïohi ba la pynkhiah ïa u, u la wan phai, u da ïaroh pyndonburom ïa U Blei da ka ktien bajam;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad u la dem khrup ha ki kjat jong U, u da nguh ïa U; une te u la long u nong Samaria.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Jisu te U da ïathuh U la ong, “Ym shym la pynkhuid ïa ki shiphew? Hynrei, hangno kita ki khyndai?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ym shym la shem kiba la wan phai ban ai burom ïa U Blei, hynrei, tang une u nongwei?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te U la ong ha u, “To ïeng joit, khie leit noh ruh: ka jingngeit jong me ka la pynkhiah ïa me.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te haba la kylli ïa U da kita ki Pharisi, “Ynda lano ka hima jong U Blei kan wan”, U la ïathuh ha ki bad U la ong, “Ka hima jong U Blei kam wan da kaba khmih thuh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Lymne kin ym ong, ‘Ha khmih hangne! lane, Ha khmih hangtai!’ naba ha khmih, ka hima jong U Blei ka long hapoh jong phi.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad U la ong ha ki synran, “Ki sngi kin wan ynda phin kwah ban ïohi ïa kawei na ki sngi U Khun u briew, te phin ym ïohi keiñ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad kin ong ha phi, ‘Ha khmih hangne! lane, Ha khmih hangtai!’ hynrei, wat mih noh, lymne wat bud ïa ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Naba kumba ka leilieh, haba ka ba na kawei ka bynta hapoh ka bneng, ka shai sha kawei pat ka bynta hapoh ka bneng, kumta ruh U Khun u briew un long ha ka sngi jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, ka dei shuwa ïa u ban shah bun kiei kiei ruh, bad ban kyntait ruh ïa u da kane ka pateng bynriew.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te kumba ka la long ha ki sngi u Noah, kumta ruh kan long ha ki sngi U Khun u briew.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ki la ïabam, ki la ïadih, ki la ïashongkurim, la ïa-pynshongkurim ïa ki, tad ynda kata ka sngi ba u Noah u la rung hapoh kata ka ïinglieng, mynba kata ka jingshlei ka la wan, bad ka la pynjot noh ïa ki baroh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumjuh ruh kumba ka la long ha ki sngi u Lot; ki la ïabam, ki la ïadih, ki la ïathied, ki la ïadie, ki la ïathung, ki la ïatei:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> hynrei, ha kata ka sngi ba u Lot u la mih noh na Sodom, U Blei u la pynhap slap da ka ding bad da u kyndok na bneng, bad u la pynjot noh ïa ki baroh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kumta ruh kan long ha kata ka sngi ha kaba yn pynpaw ïa U Khun u briew.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ha kata ka sngi, jar uba don halor ka ïing, bad kiei kiei ruh ki jong u kiba hapoh kata ka ïing, wat ai ba un hiar ban rah noh ïa ki; jar uba ha lyngkha ruh, wat ai ba un leit phai pat.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> To kynmaw phi ïa ka tnga u Lot.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Uno uno ruh u ban wad ban pynim ïa la ka mynsiem, un duh noh ïa ka; hynrei, uno uno ruh u ban duh noh ïa ka, un ri pynim ïa ka.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Nga ong ïa phi, ba ha kata ka miet kin don ar ngut ha kawei ka jingthiah, ïa uwei yn shim noh, te ïa uwei pat yn iehnoh.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ar ngut ki kynthei kin ïatylliat lem, ïa kawei yn shim noh, te ïa kawei pat yn iehnoh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ar ngut kin don ha ka lyngkha, ïa uwei yn shim noh, te ïa uwei pat yn iehnoh.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ki te ki da ïathuh ki la ong ha U, “Hangno, ko Trai?” U te U la ong ïa ki, “Kat shaba don ka met, hangta keiñ kin ïalang ki pukni.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u la kren ka pharshi ha ki shaphang ba ka dei ïa ki ban ïaiduwai, bad ban ym man thait shuh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U la ong, “La don uwei u nongbishar ha kawei ka shnong, u bymsheptieng ïa U Blei lymne burom ïa u briew.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> La don ruh ha kata ka shnong, ka riewkynthei, te ka la wan bunsien ha u, ka da ong, ‘To leh hok ïa nga halor uta uba ïaleh ïa nga.’",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te kham slem um mon, hynrei, hadien kata, u la ong ha lade, ‘La ngam sheptieng ruh ïa U Blei, bad la ngam burom ïa u briew,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> hynrei pynban, naba kane ka riewkynthei ka pynsngew satia ïa nga, ngan bishar hok ïa ka, ïoh haba ka wan khlem da pud, kan pynsngew kyllut ïa nga.’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te U Trai u la ong, “Ha sngew, kaei ba uta u nongbishar bymhok u ong!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Blei te un ym bishar hok ïa kita kiba la jied jong u, kiba lynñiar kyrpad ïa u mynsngi bad mynmiet, bad u shah slem na ka bynta jong ki?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nga ong ïa phi, ba un bishar hok ïa ki kumne kumne ruh. Hynrei, ynda wan U Khun u briew, un shem ne em ïa ka jingngeit ha ka pyrthei?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te U la kren ïa kane ka pharshi ruh ha kita kiba la shaniah skhem ha lade ba ki long ki bahok, bad kiba ibeiñ ïa kiwei.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Ar ngut ki briew ki la leit kiew sha ka templ ban duwai; uwei u Pharisi, bad uwei pat u nongkhrong.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Uta u Pharisi, haba u la ïeng, u la duwai ha lade kumne: ‘A U Blei, nga nguh ïa me ba ngam long kum kiwei ki briew, kiba shim da ka bor, ki bymhok, ki baklim, lane kum une u nongkhrong ruh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nga shah jingit ar sien shi taïew; nga ai kaba shiphew na kiei kiei baroh katba nga don.’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, uta u nongkhrong, u da ïeng na jngai, um nud wat ban khmied da la ki khmat sha bneng, hynrei, u la ïaithab ïa la ka shadem, u da ong, ‘A U Blei, to isynei ïa nga u bapop!’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nga ong ha phi, ba une u la leit hiar pat sha la ïing uba la ksan, ban ïa uta uwei pat; naba ïa uei uei baroh uba pynkhraw ïa lade, yn pynpoh; te ïa uta uba pynpoh ïa lade, yn pynkhraw.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ki la wallam ïa la ki khunlung ruh ha u, ba un ïoh ktah ïa ki; hynrei, ki synran haba ki la ïohi ki la sneng ïa ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu, haba u la khot ha lade ïa ki, u la ong, “To shah ïa ki khunlung ban wan ha nga, to wat khang ruh ïa ki; naba ïa kiba kum kita long ka hima ka jong U Blei.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, Uno uno ruh u ban ym pdiang ïa ka hima U Blei kum u khun khynnah, da lei lei ruh un ym ïoh leit bsut hapoh kata.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te uwei u nongsynshar u la kylli ïa U, u da ong, “Ko Nonghikai babha, ngan leh kumno ba ngan ïoh ka jingim bymjukut?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U Jisu te U la ong ha u, “Balei ba me khot babha ïa nga? ym don u babha, hynrei, tang uwei, uba U Blei keiñ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Me tip ïa ki hukum; ‘Wat klim; Wat pynïap; Wat tuh; Wat sakhi lamler; Burom ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie.’ ”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U te u la ïathuh, “Ïa kine baroh nga la sumar na myndang khynnah.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Jisu te haba U la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, U la ong ha u, “Sa kawei me dang duna. To die noh ïa kiei kiei baroh katba me don, to sam ruh ha ki baduk, te men ïoh ka jingkynshew keiñ ha bneng; bad to wan bud ïa nga.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, haba u la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, u la sngewsih shikatdei eh, naba u la long u bariewspah eh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Haba U Jisu u la ïohi ba u la leh sngewsih eh, U la ong, “A kaba da eh noh ïa kiba don spah ban leit bsut hapoh ka hima U Blei!",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Naba ka long kham jem ïa ka ut ban bsut lyngba ïa ka thliew thyrnia, ban ïa u bariewspah ban bsut hapoh ka hima U Blei.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kiba la ïohsngew te ki la ong, “Uei ba lah te ban lait im?”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U te u la ïathuh, “Kiei kiei ruh ki bym lah bad ki briew, ki long kiba lah bad U Blei.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ynda kumta, u Petros u la ong, “Ha khmih, ngi la iehnoh ïa kiei kiei baroh, bad ngi la ïabud ïa me!”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U te u la ong ha ki, “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba ym don uba la iehnoh ïa ka ïing, lane ïa ki kmie ki kpa, lane ïa ki hynmen hynbew, lane ïa ka tnga lane ïa ki khun, na ka bynta ka hima U Blei,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> u ban ym ïoh diang bun shah ïa katta ha kane ka pyrthei sngi, bad ha ka pyrthei ka ban sa wan, ka jingim bymjukut de.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, haba u la shim kyrpang ïa kita ki khat-ar ngut, u la ong ha ki, “Ha khmih, ngi ïaleit kiew sha Jerusalem, bad yn pyndep ha U Khun u briew ïa kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba la thoh da ki nongïathuhlypa;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> naba yn ai noh ïa u ha ki Jentil, bad yn krenbeiñ ïa u, bad yn lehbeiñ ïa u, bad yn bynthiew ruh ha u;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> te kin sympat, bad kin pynïap noh ïa u, hynrei, ha ka balai sngi un sa mihpat.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, ki kim sngewthuh ei ei ruh na kine kiei kiei ruh; bad la buhrieh ïa kane ka ktien na ki, te kim shemphang ïa kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba la kren.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ka la jia ruh haba u la wan hajan Jerikho, ba uwei u bamatlah u la shong harud lynti, u da makia ruh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Haba u la ïohsngew te ba u paidbah u ïaid lait, u la kylli, “Aïu kane ka lah ban long.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te ki la ïathuh ha u, “U Jisu uba na Nasaret u dang ïaid nangne.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te u la kyang, u da ong, “Ko Jisu, U Khun u Dabid, to isynei ïa nga!”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te kita kiba ïaïaid sha shuwa ki la sneng ïa u ba un sngap jar, hynrei, u la kyrpad jam kham tam pynban, “Ko Khun u Dabid, to isynei ïa nga!”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> U Jisu te haba U la ïeng, U la hukum ba yn wallam ïa u ha U: te haba u la wan hajan, U la kylli ïa u,",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> U da ong, “Me kwah ba ngan leh aïu ïa me?” Te u la ïathuh, “Ko Trai, ba ngan ïoh imat.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> U Jisu u la ong te ha u, “To men ïoh imat, ka jingngeit jong me ka la pynkhiah ïa me.”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh u la ïoh imat, bad u la bud ïa U da kaba ïaroh pyndonburom ïa U Blei. Uta u paidlang baroh ruh haba u la ïohi, u la ai ka jingïaroh ha U Blei."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda U la rung shapoh bad ba U dang ïaid lyngba ïa ka Jerikho,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ha khmih, u briew uba kyrteng “u Sakkhaïos,” uba la long u rangbah ki nongkhrong, bad u la long u bariewspah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u la pyrshang khnang ban ïohi ïa U Jisu, U dei uno; hynrei, um lah na uta u paidbah, naba u long uba lyngkot ka rynïeng.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Namar kata, haba u la mareh sha shuwa u la kiew halor u dieng Dumbur, ba un ïohi ïa U, naba un sa ïaid na kata ka lynti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la poi ha kata ka jaka, U la khmied bad U la ïohi ïa u, U la ong te ha u, “Ko Sakkhaïos, to da hiar noh kloi kloi ruh, naba ha kane ka sngi ka dei ïa nga ban sah ha ïing jong me.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u la hiar noh kloi kloi ruh, bad u la pdiang sngewbha ïa U da kaba leh kmen.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Haba ki la ïohi ïa kata, te, ki la ïakren khñium baroh, ki da ong, “U la leit hapoh ïing ban thiah basa bad u briew u bapop.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, haba u la ïeng joit u Sakkhaïos, u la ong ha U Trai, “Ha khmih, ïa kaba shiteng na kiei kiei ruh ki jong nga, A Trai, ngan sa ai ha ki baduk; bad lada nga la shim klop ïa kaei kaei ruh na uno uno ruh da kaba mudui lamler, ngan sa siew pat saw shah.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Jisu te U la ong ha u, “Ha kane ka sngi ka jingpynim ka la wan ha kane ka ïing, namar ba u ruh u long u khun u Abraham.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Naba U Khun u briew u la wan ïa ka ban wad bad ban pynim ïa kaba la jah noh.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba ki dang shahshkor ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, u la nang kren nang kren ïa ka pharshi, naba u la hajan Jerusalem, bad ba ki ïamut ba ka hima U Blei kan sa paw kumne kumne ruh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Namar kata, u la ong, “La don uwei u briew uba kynja syiem, uba la leit sha ka ri kaba jngai ban ïoh ha lade ka jingsynshar, bad ban wan phai pat.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te haba u la khot shiphew ngut ki shakri jong u, u la ai ha ki shiphew ki rupa, bad u la ong ha ki, ‘To phin khaïi tad ynda nga wan.’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, ki raïot    jong u ki la shun ïa u, bad ki la ïaphah ïa ki nonglam-ktien nadien jong u ki da ong, ‘Ngim mon ïa une ban synshar halor jong ngi.’",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ka la jia haba u la wan phai pat, ynda u la ïoh diang ïa kata ka hima, ba u la hukum ba yn khot ha u ïa kita ki shakri, ha kiba u la ai ïa kita ki sbai rupa, ba un ïoh tip katno ba uwei pa uwei u la myntoi da kaba khaïi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U banyngkong te u la wan u da ong, ‘Ko Trai, ka rupa jong me ka la pynman shiphew pat ki rupa.’",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U la ïathuh te ha u, ‘Bha me u shakri babha! naba me la long uba ngeit ha iba khyndiat eh, to men ïoh bor halor shiphew ki shnong.’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U ba-ar u la wan ruh u da ong, ‘Ko Trai, ka rupa jong me ka la pynman san ki rupa.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U la ïathuh te ha uta ruh, ‘Me ruh to long halor san ki shnong.’",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Uwei pat u la wan ruh u da ong, ‘Ko Trai, ha khmih ka rupa jong me, kaba nga la sumar song khop ha ka jaiñ rumar;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> namar nga la sheptieng ïa me, naba me long u briew uba eh; me shim ïa kaba mem shym la buh, me ot ruh ïa kaba mem shym la bet.’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U te u ong ha u, ‘Na ka shyntur jong me ngan bishar ïa me, me u shakri bymman; me la lah tip ba nga long u briew uba eh, uba shim ïa kaba ngam shym la buh, bad uba ot ïa kaba ngam shym la bet:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> hato balei ba mem shym la buh te ïa uta u sbai rupa jong nga ha ka ïing ba ai sut, ba haba nga la wan pat nga lah ban ïoh ïa uta lem bad ka sut de?’",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U la ong te ha kita kiba ïeng hajan, ‘Shim noh na u ïa kata ka rupa, bad to ai ha uta uba don kita ki shiphew ki rupa.’",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ki la ïa-ong te ha u, ‘Ko Trai, u don shiphew ki rupa!’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Nga ong ha phi, ‘ba ha u briew baroh uba don, yn ai shuh; hynrei, na uta u bymdon, wat ïa kata kaba u don yn shim noh na u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, ïa kita ki nongshun jong nga, ki bym shym la mon ïa nga ban synshar halor jong ki, to wallam hangne, bad to pynïap ïa ki ha khmat jong nga.’ ”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ynda u la kren te ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, u la leit sha shuwa, ba u da leit kiew sha Jerusalem.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ka la jia ruh ynda u la poi hajan Bethphage bad Bethania, haduh uta u lum ïa uba ju khot “U Lum ki Olib”, ba u la phah ar ngut na ki synran jong u,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> u da ong, “Khie leit sha kata ka shnong kaba ha marpyrshah jong phi, te haba phi poi hangta phin shem ïa u khun kadda ba la teh, halor jong u ym pat ju don u briew ba la shong mynno mynno ruh; to pyllait ïa u bad wallam ïa u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te lada uno uno ruh u kylli ïa phi, ‘Hato balei phi pyllait ïa u?’ kumne phin ong ïa u, ‘Naba U Trai u donkam ïa u.’ ”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kita ïa kiba la phah te haba ki la leit, ki la shem kumba u la lah ong ha ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Haba ki dang ïapyllait te ïa uta u khun kadda, ki trai jong u ki la ïakylli ïa ki, “Hato balei phi pyllait ïa u khun kadda?”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ki te ki la ong, “U Trai u donkam ïa u.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ki la wallam te ïa u ha U Jisu, bad haba ki la siang ïa la ki jaiñkup halor uta u khun kadda, ki la pynshong ïa U Jisu halor.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te katba U nang leit, ki la ïasiang ïa la ki jaiñkup ha kata ka lynti.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te haba U la poi hajan kat haduh kaba hiar na uta U Lum ki Olib, uta u paidbah synran baroh ki la ïasdang ban ïalehkmen bad ban ïaroh ïa U Blei da ka ktien bajam, namar ki kambah baroh ïa kiba ki la lah ïohi,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> ki da ong, “Long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Syiem uba wan ha ka kyrteng U Trai! ka jingsuk ha bneng, bad ka burom ha kiba jrong tam eh.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te kiba na ki Pharisi napdeng uta u paidbah ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Ko Nonghikai, to sneng ïa ki synran jong me.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> U te U la ïathuh bad U la ong ha ki, “Nga ong ha phi, ba lada kine kin shu sngap jar, ki maw hi kin sa ïakyang buk.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te katba U la poi hajan, haba U la khmih ïa ka shnong, U la ïam na ka bynta jong ka,",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> U da ong, “A lada pha la lah tip, ma pha ruh shisha, ha kane ka sngi, ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba dei ïa ka jingsuk jong pha! hynrei, mynta la buhrieh ïa ki na ki khmat jong pha!",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Naba ki sngi kin jia ha pha, ba ki nongshun jong pha kin ïatih kharai sawdong ïa pha, bad kin ïaker tawiar ïa pha, bad kin ïaset kut ïa pha baroh sawdong,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad kin ïa-pynkyllon ïa pha bad ïa ki khun jong pha hapoh jong pha, bad kin ym ïa-iehnoh ha pha ïa u maw halor u maw; naba pham shym la ithuh ïa ka aïom ka jingwan jngoh ïa pha.”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te U la rung hapoh ka templ, bad U la sdang ban beh noh ïa kita kiba ïadie ïathied,",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> U da ong ha ki, “La thoh: ‘Ka ïing jong nga ka long ka ïing jingduwai’, hynrei, phi, ‘ka krem nongtuh’, phi la ïa-pynlong ïa ka.”",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> U la ju hikai ha la ka sngi ruh ha kata ka templ. Hynrei, ki rangbah lyngdoh, bad ki nongthoh, bad kiba kham rangbah na u paidbah, ki la ïawad dong ban pynïap noh ïa U:",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> te kim lah shem da kaba kumno ba kin leh, naba u paidlang baroh u ïashahshkor bha eh ban ïohsngew ïa U."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia te ha kawei na kita ki sngi, haba U dang hikai ïa u paidlang ha ka templ, bad ba U dang ïalap ïa ka gospel, ba ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki nongthoh, lem bad ki tymmen basan, ki la wan lap ïa U.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki la ïakren ha u, ki da ong, “To ïathuh ha ngi, da ka bor aïu ba me leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, lane uei uta uba la ai ha me ïa kane ka bor?”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U te U la ïathuh bad U la ong ha ki, “Nga ruh ngan kylli ïa phi kawei ka jingkylli, to ïathuh keiñ ha nga.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kata ka jingbaptis u Ïoannis, ka la long kaba na bneng lane na ki briew?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, ki la ïasaid hi ha lade, ki da ong, “Lada ngi ngin ong, ‘Na bneng’, un ong, ‘Hato balei ba phim shym la ngeit ha u?’",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te lada ngin ong, ‘Na ki briew’, u paidlang baroh un lynthem maw ïa ngi, naba u long uba ngeit skhem ba u Ïoannis u la long u nongïathuhlypa.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar kata, ki la ïathuh ba kim tip nangno.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Jisu u la ong te ha ki, “Nga ruh ngam ïathuh ha phi da ka bor aïu ba nga leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, U la sdang ban kren ha uta u paidlang ïa kane ka pharshi. “Uwei u briew u la thung ka brisoh, bad u la ai wai ïa ka ha ki nongsumar bri, bad u la leit noh sha kawei pat ka ri kham slem.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ha ka aïom babiang, u la phah ïa u shakri ha kita ki nongsumar bri, ba kin ïoh ai ha u na ki soh jong kata ka brisoh, hynrei, kita ki nongsumar bri, ki la sympat ïa u, bad ki la phah noh suda.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, u la phah pat sa ïa uwei u shakri, hynrei, ïa uta ruh, haba ki la sympat bad la pynjahburom, ki la phah noh suda.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hadien kata, u la phah sa ïa uba lai pat, hynrei, ïa une ruh de haba ki la ïa-pynmong, ki la ïashop noh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te uta u trai kata ka brisoh u la ong, ‘Ngan leh kumno? ngan phah ïa la u khun uba ieit; lehse haba ki ïohi ïa une kin burom.’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, haba kita ki nongsumar bri ki la ïohi ïa u, ki la ïakren paralok hi, ki da ong, ‘Une u long u nongïoh pateng, ïa, ngin ïa-pynïap noh ïa u, ba ka bynta jong u kan ïoh long ka jong ngi.’",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, haba ki la ïashop noh ïa u shabar kata ka brisoh, ki la ïa-pynïap noh. Namar kata, uta u trai ka brisoh un sa leh kumno ïa kita?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Un wan bad un pynïap duh noh keiñ ïa kine ki nongsumar bri, bad un ai ïa kata ka brisoh ha kiwei.” Te haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la ong, “Wat ai ba kan long kumta!”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te haba U la khmih shaiñ ïa ki, U la ong, “Ka long aïu te kane kaba la thoh? “ ‘Ïa u maw ïa uba ki nongtei ki la kyntait, ïa une la pynlong u khlieh ka dong.’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “U briew baroh uba hap halor uta u maw, yn pynkheiñ lyngkhot lyngkhai ïa u, hynrei, jar ha uba un ïoh hap, un pynlwet jin ïa u.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kita ki rangbah lyngdoh bad kita ki nongthoh te ki la ïawad dong ban kem ïa U ha kata ka por, hynrei, ki la ïasheptieng ïa u paidlang; naba ki la sngewthuh ba dei ïa ki ba U la kren ïa kane ka pharshi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ki la ïa-ap thap ïa u, bad ki la ïaphah ïa ki nongsyntiat kiba leh mynleh riewhok ïa lade, ba kin ïoh ïariam ïa ki ktien jong u, ïa ka ban aiti noh ïa u ha ka hukum bad ha ka bor u lyngskor.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki te ki la ïakylli ïa u ki da ong, “Ko Nonghikai, ngi tip ba me kren bad me hikai ïa kaba dei, bad mem ñiew shiliang khmat, hynrei, me hikai ïa ka lynti U Blei ha kaba shisha:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> te ka bit ne em ïa ngi ban ai khajna ha u Kaisar?”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, u la ithuh ïa ka buit sian bymman jong ki, bad u la ong ha ki, “Balei phi pynshoi ïa nga?”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “To pyni ïa ka shi suka ha nga. Ka dur bad ka jingthoh jongno ka don ha ka?” Ki te ki da ïathuh ki la ong, “Ka jong u Kaisar.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Haba kumta, to ai ïa kiei kiei ruh ki jong u Kaisar ha u Kaisar, bad ïa kiei kiei ruh ki jong U Blei ha U Blei keiñ.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kumta, kim lah shuh ban kem daw na ka ktien jong u ha khmat uta u paidlang: te ki la ïasngewphylla ïa kata ka jingïathuh jong u, bad ki la ïasngap jar.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda kumta, kiba na ki Saddusi ki la wan ha u, kiba ong bymdon ka jingmihpat, ki la ïakylli ïa u,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ki da ong, “Ko Nonghikai, u Moses u la thoh ha ngi, ‘Lada u hynmen jongno jongno ruh uba don ka tnga, un ïap noh, bad lada um don khun, ba u para jong u un shim ïa ka tnga jong u, bad un pynmih symbai ïa la u hynmen.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te la don hynñiew ngut shipara: u banyngkong te u la shongkurim, bad u la ïap noh khlem khun.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Uba shi sien bud ruh u la shim ïa ka bad u la ïap noh khlem khun.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Uba ar sien bud ruh u la shim ruh ïa ka; kumjuh de kita ki hynñiew ngut ruh ki la ïap noh khlem khun.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Khatduh eh kata ka kynthei ruh ka la ïap noh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Namar kata, ha ka jingmihpat, kan long ka tnga jongno na kine? Naba kita ki hynñiew ngut ki la ïoh kurim ïa ka.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te U Jisu u la ong ha ki, “Ki khun jong kane ka pyrthei ki ïashongkurim, bad ju pynshongkurim ïa ki,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> hynrei, kita ïa kiba yn ñiew kiba bit ban ïoh ïa kata ka pyrthei, bad ïa kata ka jingmihpat kaba na ki baïap, kim ïashongkurim keiñ, lymne pynshongkurim ïa ki,",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> naba kim lah ban ïap noh shuh; namar ki ïalong marryngkat bad ki angel, ki long ruh ki khun U Blei, ba ki da long ki khun kata ka jingmihpat.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Hynrei, ba yn pynmih pat ïa ki baïap, wat u Moses ruh u la pyni paw ha kata ka 'law lynnong, mynba u khot ïa U Trai, uba U Blei u Abraham, bad U Blei u Isaak, bad U Blei u Jakob.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te um long U Blei ki baïap, hynrei, ki ba-im, naba baroh ki im ha U.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te kiba na kita ki nongthoh ki da ïathuh ki la ong, “Ko Nonghikai, me la kren ïa kaba dei.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Naduh kata, kim ïanud ban kylli ei ei shuh ïa u.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Hynrei, u la kylli ïa ki, “Hato kumno ki ïa-ong ba uba U Khrist u long u khun u Dabid?",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Naba u Dabid hi u ong ha ka kitab ki Salm, “ ‘U Trai    u la ong ha U Trai jong nga: Ma me to shong sha kamon jong nga,",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> tad ynda ngan pynlong ïa kiba shun ïa me, ka jingïuh hapoh ki kjat jong me.’",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> “Te kumta u Dabid u khot ‘U Trai’ ïa U: kumno te U long U khun jong u?”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te ha kaba ïohsngew uta u paidbah baroh, U la ong ha ki synran jong U,",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> “To kiar noh na ki nongthoh, kiba kwah ban ïaid kai ha ki jaiñkup bajynsur, bad kiba ieit ïa ki jingnguh ha ki ïew, bad ïa ki jingshong bakor tam ha ki synagog, bad ïa ki jaka ba kham kor ha ki jingkhawai;",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> kiba bam duh ïa ki ïing ki riewkynthei, bad kiba duwai jlan ruh khnang ban tyllep; kine kin ïoh diang ïa ka jingshitom kaba kham khraw.”"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u la khmied, u la ïohi ïa ki bariewspah kiba noh ïa ki jingainguh jong ki ha ka jingkynshew.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U la ïohi ruh ïa kawei ka riewkynthei ka baduk, kaba noh hangta ar damli.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U la ong te, “Kaba shisha nga ong ha phi, ba kane ka riewkynthei ka baduk ka la noh kham bun ïa kita baroh;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> naba kita baroh na ka jong kata kaba sah tam ïa ki, ki la noh ha ki jingainguh U Blei, hynrei, kane na ka jingkyrduh jong ka, ka la noh ïa ka jingim baroh phar katba ka don.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te mynba la don kiba ïakren shaphang kata ka templ, kumno ba la pynitynnad ïa ka da ki maw ki babha bad da ki jingainguh ïa U Blei, u la ong,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Ïa kine kiei kiei ruh kiba phi khmih, ki sngi kin jia ha kiba yn ym iehnoh hangne ïa u maw halor u maw, ïa u ban ym pynhap noh.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ki la kylli ïa u, ki da ong, “Ko Nonghikai, hato lano kine kiei kiei ruh kin long? bad ka dak kaba kumno kan long ha ban sa long kine kiei kiei ruh?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U la ïathuh te, “To sumar ba yn ym shukor ïa phi; naba bun kin wan ha ka kyrteng jong nga ki da ong, ‘Ma nga U Khrist’, bad ‘kata ka aïom ka la jan’: wat leit bud nadien jong ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba phin ïohsngew shaphang ki thma bad ki jingkhihwin, phi wat sheptieng; naba ka dei ïa kine kiei kiei ruh ban jia shuwa, hynrei, kata ka bakut kam long kumne kumne ruh.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong ha ki, “Ka jaid bynriew kan ïeng ïaleh bad ka jaid bynriew, ka hima ruh bad ka hima,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ki jingkhynñiuh jumai kiba jur kin long ruh, bad ha shibun ki jaka ki 'nemsniew bad ki jingïapthem ruh, bad kin long ruh kiei kiei bashyrkhei bad ki dak bakhraw ruh na bneng.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, shuwa ïa kine kiei kiei baroh, kin kem ïa phi bad kin pynshitom ruh ïa phi, ki da ai noh ïa phi ha ki synagog bad ha ki ïing byndi, ki da leit lam ruh ïa phi ha khmat ki syiem bad ki nongsynshar, na ka bynta ka kyrteng jong nga.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, kan pynjia lad ïa phi ïa ka ban long ka jingïaphla.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namar kata, to kut jingmut ha la ki dohnud ban ym puson lypa kumno ban ïasaid-da,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> naba ngan ai ha phi ka shyntur bad ka jingstad, ïa kaba ki nongïaleh jong phi baroh keiñ kin ym lah ban ïasei nia kylliang, lane ban ïasaid kylliang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Yn ai noh ruh ïa phi wat da ki kmie ki kpa, bad da ki para, bad da ki kur, bad da ki lok; bad ïa kiba na phi kin pynïap.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Phin long ruh kiba la isih da ki briew baroh namar ka kyrteng jong nga.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, iwei i shñiuh na ka khlieh jong phi in ym jah noh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Da ka jingïaineh minot jong phi phin ri pynim ïa la ki mynsiem.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Hynrei, haba phin ïohi ïa ka Jerusalem ba la ker tawiar ïa ka da ki paidïapom, ynda kumta, te phin tip ba kata ka jingpynduh ïa ka, ka la jan.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, kita kiba ha Judia, to kin ïaphet ïap noh sha ki lum; bad kita kiba hapdeng jong ka, to kin ïakynriah noh; bad kita kiba ha ki ri bri, to kin ym leit bsut hapoh jong ka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Naba kine ki long ki sngi ka jingpynshitom hok, ïa ka ban pyndep ïa kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba la thoh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, kordit ïa kita kiba la punkhun, bad ïa kita kiba ai buiñ ha kita ki sngi! namar ka shipa kaba khraw kan long ha kata ka ri, bad ka jingbitar ha une u paidlang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kin kyllon ruh da ka syrti waitlam, bad yn ïalam mraw ïa ki sha ki kynja bynriew baroh; bad kan long ba la ïuh top ïa ka Jerusalem da ki Jentil, tad ynda yn pyndep ïa ka Ïa ki Jentil.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Ki dak ruh kin long ha ka sngi bad ha u bnai bad ha ki khlur, bad ha ka khyndew ka jingjynjar jong ki jaid bynriew, ki da sngewlyngngoh namar ka jingkyrhuh ka duriaw bad ki jingat phyllung,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> ki briew ki da ïapler da kaba sheptieng bad da kaba ap lyngngoh ïa kita kiei kiei ruh ki ban sa jia thred ha ka pyrthei: naba yn pynkhih ïa ki bor jong ki bneng.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda kumta, te kin ïohi ïa U Khun u briew ba u da wan ha u lyoh, da ka bor bad ka burom bakhraw.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te haba kine kiei kiei ruh ki sdang ban jia long, to khmied bad to mied ïa la ki khlieh, naba ka jinglait im jong phi ka la jan.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u la kren ka pharshi ha ki, “To khmih thuh ïa u dieng Dumbur, bad ïa ki kynja dieng baroh;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> haba ki khie lung, phi ïohi bad phi tip na lade ba ka lyiur mynta ka hajan.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kumjuh ruh ma phi, ynda phin ïohi ba la jia kine kiei kiei ruh, to phin tip ba ka hima U Blei ka la jan.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, kane ka pateng bynriew kan ym leit noh tad ynda yn pyndep ïa kiei kiei baroh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ka bneng bad ka khyndew kin duh noh, hynrei, ki ktien jong nga kin ym duh noh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Namar kata, to sumar ïa lade, ïoh kumno kumno ba ki dohnud jong phi kin sngewkhia da kaba bam lalot, bad da kaba buaid, bad da ki jingkhuslai pyrthei, bad ba kata ka sngi kan lap kyndit ïa phi kum ka jingriam:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> naba kumta kan ngat ha kita baroh kiba shong sah ha sla ka khyndew baroh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Namar kata, to sharai phi ha la ka sngi da kaba duwai, ba yn ïoh ñiew ïa phi kaba bit ban lait noh na kine kiei kiei baroh ki ban sa jia, bad ban ïeng ha khmat U Khun u briew.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad mynsngi mynsngi u ju hikai ha ka templ, hynrei, mynmiet mynmiet u ju mih noh, bad u sah miet ha u lum ïa uba khot “Olib”.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te ki paidbah baroh ki ju leit la dang shai byrngut ha u ha ka templ ïa ka ban ïohsngew ïa u."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te Ka Jingkhawai Niam U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat ka la jan, ïa kaba khot “Ka Niam Ka Jinglait”.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki nongthoh, ki la ïawad dong kumno ba kin ïoh ban pynïap noh ïa u; naba ki la ïasheptieng ïa u paidlang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ynda kumta, u Soitan u la leit bsut hapoh u Judas ïa uba la sin “Iskariot”, uba long uwei na ki khat-ar ngut.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba u la leit noh, u la ïasylla bad kita ki rangbah lyngdoh bad kita ki kapten, da kaba kumno un ïoh ai noh ïa U ha ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ki la ïakmen, bad ki la ïakut ban ai sbai ha u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U ruh u la kohnguh, bad u la wad dong kaba bit ïa ka ban ai noh ïa U ha ki ha ka bymdon u paidbah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, la jia kata ka sngi U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat, ha kaba la dei ban kñia ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te U la phah ïa u Petros bad ïa u Ïoannis, U da ong, “To khie leit ïakhreh ïa ngi ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, ba ngin ïoh ïabam.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki la kylli ïa U, “Hangno me mon ba ngin ïakhreh?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U la ïathuh te ha ki, “Ha khmih, ynda phi la rung ha kato ka shnong, u briew un ïakynduh bad phi, uba bah shi kum  ka um: phin bud ïa u sha kata ka ïing sha kaba u rung,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad phin ong ha u trai kata ka ïing, ‘U Nonghikai u kylli ïa me, Hangno kata ka kamra ha kaba ngan ïoh bam ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait lem bad ki synran jong nga?’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U te un pyni ha phi ïa ka kamra haneng kaba khraw kaba la don ka jingbuh jingsat: hangta phin ïakhreh.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, ki la ïaleit, bad ki la shem kumba U la lah ong ha ki: bad ki la ïakhreh ïa kata Ka Niam Ka Jinglait.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kata ka por te ka la jia, U la shong shaniah, bad kita ki apostol lem bad U.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Nga la kwah shikatdei eh ban bam ïa kane Ka Niam Ka Jinglait lem bad phi, katba ngam pat shah,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> naba nga ong ha phi, ba ngan ym bam shuh na kane, tad ynda yn pyndep ïa ka ha ka hima U Blei.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u la shim ïa ka khuri, bad haba u la lah nguh de, u la ong, “To shim ïa kane bad to ïasam hi paralok;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> naba nga ong ha phi, ba ngan ym dih shuh na u soh u dieng Waiñ, tad ynda kata ka hima jong U Blei kan da wan.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U la shim ruh ïa u kpu, bad haba u la lah nguh de, u la kdiah ïa u, bad u la ai ha ki, u da ong, “Une u long ka met jong nga ïa kaba la ai noh na ka bynta jong phi; to phin leh ïa kane ïa ka ban kynmaw ïa nga.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumjuh ruh ïa kata ka khuri, hadien kaba bam ja miet, U da ong, “Kane ka khuri ka long kata Ka Jutang Ka Bathymmai da ka snam jong nga, ïa kaba yn sa theh noh na ka bynta jong phi:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> pleng ha khmih, ka kti ka jong uta uba die noh ïa nga, ka don lem bad nga halor kane ka miej:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> te shisha U Khun u briew u leit noh, kumba la thmu lypa; hynrei, kordit ïa uta u briew da uba yn die noh ïa u!”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la sdang ban ïakylli paralok hi, hato dei uwei na ki u ban sa leh ïa kane.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ka la mih ruh ka jingïasaid hapdeng jong ki, ïano na ki yn ñiew uba kham khraw.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Ki syiem jong ki Jentil ki leh trai khlieh ïa ki, bad ïa kita kiba don bor halor jong ki la khot ‘Nongkambha’.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, phi, phin ym long kumta; hynrei, uta uba kham khraw hapdeng jong phi, ai ba un long kum uba kham poh; bad uta uba synshar, kum uta uba shakri.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Naba uno uba kham khraw, uta uba shong bam lane uta uba shakri? ym dei uta uba shong bam? hynrei, nga, nga long hapdeng jong phi kum uta uba shakri.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Phi long kita te kiba la ïaisah lem bad nga ha ki jingtynjuh jong nga.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Nga te nga kular skhem ha phi ïa ka hima, kumba U Kpa jong nga u la ai ha nga,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ba phin ïoh bam bad ïoh dih ha ka miej jong nga ha kata ka hima jong nga, bad halor ki khet phin ïoh shong bishar ïa ki khat-ar ki jaid Israel.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> U Trai u la ong ruh, “Ko Simon, Simon, ha khmih u Soitan u la pan ban ïoh ïa phi, ïa ka ban ïoh tai ïa phi kum ïa u Kew:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> hynrei, nga la duwai ma nga na ka bynta jong me, ba ka jingngeit jong me kan ym duh noh; ma me te ynda me la kylla bha pat to men pynskhem ïa ki para jong me.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> U te u la ïathuh ha U, “Ko Trai, nga la kloi ban leit ryngkat bad me sha ka byndi, bad sha ka jingïap ruh.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> U te U la ïathuh, “Nga ong ha me, ko Petros, u syiar un ym riew ha kane ka sngi tad ynda men len lai sien ba me ithuh ïa nga.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong ha ki, “Mynba nga la phah noh ïa phi khlem ka jingpan, bad ka ïarong, bad ki juti, phi la sngewkyrduh ei ei ruh ne em?” Ki te ki la ïathuh, “Ei ei ruh em.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te u la ong ha ki, “Hynrei mynta, jar uba don ka jingpan, to ai ba un rah, kumjuh ruh ïa la ka ïarong: bad jar u bymdon ka waitlam, to ai ba un die noh ïa la ka jaiñkup, bad ba un thied kawei;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> naba nga ong ha phi, ba ka dei ban pyndep ha nga ïa kane kaba la thoh: ‘Bad la ñiew ïa u lem bad ki nongpalat’: naba don ka jingpyndep shisha ïa kita kiei kiei ruh shaphang jong nga.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ki te ki la ong, “Ko Trai, ha khmih, ar tylli ki waitlam hangne.” U te u la ong ha ki, “Keiñ noh!”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te u la mih noh, bad u la leit, kumba u ju leit, sha u lum Olib; te ki synran jong u ruh ki la bud ïa u.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Haba u la lah poi te ha kata ka jaka, u la ong ha ki, “To ïaduwai ba phin ym hap ha ka jingpynshoi.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ynda kumta te u la kynriah noh na ki, kat shi sien pda maw; te haba u la dem la ki khohsiew, u la duwai,",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> u da ong, “Ko Kpa, lada me mon to pynphai noh ïa kane ka khuri na nga: hynrei, ym ïa ka mon jong nga, hynrei, ïa ka jong me, yn leh.”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Hangta la mihpaw ha U, u angel na bneng, u da pynshait ïa U.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te ba U don ha ka jingpisa mynsiem bajur, U la duwai kham shitrhem shibun eh: te ka syep jong U ka la long kum ki jingjaw ka snam kaba lang, ki da hap ha ka khyndew.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te haba U la ïeng na kata kaba duwai, U la wan ha ki synran jong U, bad U la shem ïa ki ba ki da ïohthiah na kaba sngewsih;",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Balei ba phi ïohthiah? To ïeng joit ïaduwai ruh, ïoh ba phin hap ha ka jingpynshoi.”",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Haba U dang kren te, ha khmih u paidbah, bad uta ïa uba la khot “Judas” (uwei na kita ki khat-ar ngut) u la ïaid ha shuwa jong ki, bad u la wan hajan U Jisu ban doh ïa U.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Hynrei U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Ko Judas, da ka jingïadoh me die noh ïa U Khun u briew?”",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Te haba kita kiba sawdong ïa U ki la ïohi ïa kata ka ban sa jia, ki la kylli ïa U, “Ko Trai, ngin pom ne em da ka waitlam?”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Uwei te uba na ki u la pom ïa u shakri jong u rangbah lyngdoh, bad u la mait noh ïa ka shkor kamon jong u.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> U Jisu te U la ïathuh bad U la ong, “To shah haduh kane,” bad haba U la ktah ïa kata ka shkor jong u, U la pynkhiah ïa u.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> U Jisu u la ong te ha ki rangbah lyngdoh, bad ha ki rangbah ka templ, bad ha ki tymmen basan, kiba la wan kem ïa U, “Kum ban kem ïa u nongtuh, phi la mih noh bad ki waitlam bad ki diengduh ruh?",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Mynba nga la don lem bad phi ha la ka sngi ha ka templ, phim shym la kner satia ïa la ki kti ban kem ïa nga: hynrei, kane ka long ka por jong phi, bad ka bor jong ka jingdum.”",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Ynda ki la kem ïa u, ki la ïalam noh, bad ki la wallam ïa u hapoh ka ïing u rangbah lyngdoh. U Petros te u la bud na jngai.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Te ynda ki la sliew ding hapdeng ka phyllaw, bad ba ki la ïashong lem, u Petros u la shong hapdeng jong ki.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Hynrei, kawei ka shakri haba ka la ïohi ïa u, ba u shong hajan kata ka ding, bad haba ka la khmih shaiñ ïa u, ka la ong, “Une ruh u la long lem bad U.”",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Hynrei, u la len, u da ong, “Ko kynthei, ngam ithuh ïa U.”",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Ynda la shibit te, uwei pat u la ïohi ïa u, bad u la ong, “Me ruh me long uwei na ki.” Hynrei, u Petros u la ïathuh, “Briew, ngam long.”",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Sa kumba shi por pat, sa uwei u la kren skhem, u da ong, “Da kaba shisha une ruh u la long lem bad U: naba u long u nong Galilaïa.”",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Hynrei, u Petros u la ïathuh, “Briew, ngam tip kaei ba me ong.” Te kumne kumne ruh katba u dang kren, la riew u syiar.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Te U Trai u la phai, bad U la khmih lieb ha u Petros. Bad u Petros u la kynmaw ïa kata ka ktien ka jong U Trai, kumno ba U la ong ha u, “Haba um pat riew u syiar ha kane ka sngi, men len ïa nga lai sien.”",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Te u Petros u la mih noh shabar bad u la lynñiar kthang eh.",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Kita ki briew te kiba ïabat lem ïa U Jisu, ki la lehbeiñ ïa u, bad ki la sympat ïa u.",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> Haba ki la lah ïatap matlah ruh ïa u, ki la shoh ïa u na ka khmat, bad ki la kylli ïa u, ki da ong, “To ïathuh, uei uba la shoh ïa me?”",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> Bad shibun kiwei pat kiei kiei ki la kren pyrshah ïa u, ki da krenbeiñ ïa u.",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> Te tang shu mih ka sngi, la ïalum lang ïa ka jingïaseng ki tymmen basan jong u paidlang, bad rangbah lyngdoh, bad nongthoh de, bad ki la ïalam ïa u sha ka dorbar jong ki,",
			"67": "<sup>67</sup> ki da ong, “Lada me long uta U Khrist, to ïathuh ha ngi.” Te u la ïathuh ha ki, “Lada ngan ïathuh ha phi, phin ym ngeit satia:",
			"68": "<sup>68</sup> bad lada ngan kylli ruh, phin ym ïathuh satia ha nga, lane pyllait noh:",
			"69": "<sup>69</sup> hynrei, naduh mynta U Khun u briew un long uba shong sha kamon ka bor U Blei.”",
			"70": "<sup>70</sup> Te ki la ïa-ong baroh, “Haba kumta me long U Khun U Blei?” U te u la ïathuh ha ki, “Phi ong ba nga long.”",
			"71": "<sup>71</sup> Ki la ïa-ong te, “Ngi dang donkam sabut aïu pat? naba ngi hi ngi la ïohsngew na ka shyntur jong u hi.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba ka jingïaseng jong ki baroh ka la ïeng joit, ki la ïalam noh ïa U ha khmat u Pilat.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ki la sdang ruh ban mudui ïa U, ki da ong, “Ngi la shem ïa une ba U da pynkiat ïa u paidlang, bad ba U da khang ban ai khajna ha u Kaisar, U da ong ba U hi U long U Khrist U Syiem.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Pilat u la kylli ïa U, u da ong, “Me long ma me uta u Syiem ki Jiw?” Te U la ïathuh bad U la ong ha u, “Me ong.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u Pilat u la ong ha kita ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ha kita ki paidbah, “Ngam shem satia ka jingpalat ha une u briew.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, ki te ki la kham ïa-pyneh, ki da ïa-ong, “U pynkhih ïa u paidlang, U da hikai kylleng ka Judia baroh, da kaba sdang naduh Galilaïa haduh hangne.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba u Pilat u la ïohsngew ïa kata, u la kylli la uta u briew u long ne em u nong Galilaïa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Haba u la tip ruh ba U long na ka jingsynshar u Herod, u la phah pateng ïa U sha u Herod, uba don hi ruh ha Jerusalem ha kita ki sngi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Herod te haba u la ïohi ïa U Jisu, u la kmen shikatdei eh; naba u la kwah la slem ban ïohi ïa U, namar ba u la ïohsngew shibun kiei kiei ruh shaphang jong U, bad u la kyrmen ban ïohi ïa kano kano ka dak ba un leh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U la kylli te ïa U da ki shibun ki ktien; hynrei, um shym la ïathuh ei ei ruh em ha u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kumta kita ki rangbah lyngdoh bad kita ki nongthoh ki la ïeng, ki da mudui jam eh ïa U.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, u Herod bad ki shipai jong u ki la lehbeiñ ïa U, bad ki la pyrthuhbeiñ, bad haba ki la ïa-pynkup ka jaiñ batyngshain ha U, ki la phah noh pat ïa U sha u Pilat.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Herod bad u Pilat ki la ïalok noh ha kata hi ka sngi; naba mynshuwa ki la ju ïashun paralok hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Pilat u la khot lem ïa ki rangbah lyngdoh, bad ïa ki nongbishar, bad ïa u paidlang,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad u la ong ha ki, “Phi la wallam ïa une u briew ha nga, kum uba pynkiat ïa u paidlang: ha khmih ruh, haba nga la tohkit ïa u ha khmat jong phi, ngam shem satia ka jingpalat ha une u briew shaphang kita kiei kiei ruh ba phi mudui ïa u:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> lymne u Herod hi ruh, naba u la phah pat ïa u sha ngi; ha khmih, um shym la leh ei ei ruh em kaba u dei ban ïap:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> namar kata, ynda nga la sympat ïa u, ngan pyllait noh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> (Naba u la donkam ban pyllait noh ïa uwei ha ki ha Ka Jingkhawai Niam.)”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, ki la ïapyrta lang baroh, ki da ïa-ong, “To da shim duh noh ïa une! bad da pyllait noh ha ngi ïa u Barabbas!”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> (Ïa uba la buh ha ka byndi, namar kawei ka jingkhihwin ba la pynlong ha kata ka shnong, bad ka jingpynïap briew.)",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Namar kata, u Pilat u la kren pat ha ki, ba u da mon ban pyllait noh ïa U Jisu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, ki la ïapyrta jam, ki da ïa-ong, “Sahnarphna, sahnarphna ïa U!”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u la ong ha ki ha ka balai sien, “Balei, une u briew u la leh bymman aïu? ngam shym shem satia ha u ka daw ba u dei ban ïap; namar kata, ynda nga la sympat ïa u, ngan pyllait noh.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, ki la ïaipyneh da ki jingpyrta bajam, ba ki da pan ba yn sahnarphna ïa U. Kumta, ki jingpyrta jong ki, bad ki jong kita ki rangbah lyngdoh, ki la ïalah.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u Pilat u la rai ba dei ban leh ïa kaba ki pan.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kumta, u la pyllait noh ha ki, ïa uta ba la set ha ka byndi, namar ka jingkhihwin bad ka jingpynïap briew, ïa uba ki la pan; hynrei, ïa U Jisu u la aiti noh ha ka mon jong ki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te katba ki dang ïalam noh ïa U, ki la ïakem ïa uwei u Simon u nong Kyrini, uba wan na ka ri bri, bad ki la ïapynbah ha u ïa ka diengphna, ban bah nadien U Jisu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te la bud ïa U, u paidbah babun ki briew, bad ki kynthei kiba la lynñiar lympat ruh ïa lade, bad ba la ïam sngewsynei ïa U.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hynrei, haba U Jisu u la phai sha ki, U la ong, “Ko kynthei Jerusalem, wat ïaïam phi namar jong nga, hynrei, to ïaïam namar ïa lade, bad namar ki khun jong phi!",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Naba, ha khmih, ki sngi kin wan ha kiba kin ong, ‘Suk ki balyngki, bad ki kpoh ki bym ju kha, bad ki jymbuiñ ki bym ju ai buiñ!’",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ynda kumta, kin sdang ban ïapyrta ha ki lum bah, ‘To hap ha ngi!’ bad ha ki lum rit, ‘To tap ïa ngi!’",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Naba lada ki leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh ha u dieng bajyrngam, ïa kaei yn leh ha u batyrkhong?”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te la ïalam lem bad U, ar ngut kiwei pat ruh, ki nongkam sniew, ba yn pynïap ïa ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ynda ki la poi te ha kata ka jaka ïa kaba ju khot “Maloi khlieh”, hangta ki la sahnarphna ïa U, bad ïa kita ki nongkam sniew, ïa uwei sha kamon, bad ïa uwei sha kadiang de.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te U Jisu u la ong, “Ko Kpa, to map ïa ki; naba kim tip kaei ba ki leh.” Haba ki la ïabynta ïa ki jaiñkup jong U, te ki la ïakhalai.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Uta u paidlang te u la ïeng jngoh. Ki nongsynshar ruh de ki la ïa-pynran beiñ ïa la ki khmut, ki da ïa-ong, “Ïa kiwei U la pynim; to un pynim ïa lade, lada une U long U Khrist u jong U Blei, uba la jied jong u!”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad ki shipai ruh ki la ïalehbeiñ ïa U, ki da ïawan ha U, bad ki da ïatyrwa ai ka bajew ha U,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad ki da ong, “Lada me long U Syiem jong ki Jiw, to pynim ïa lade.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> La don te ka jingthoh shalor ba la thoh haneng jong U, ha ki dak Grik, bad Roman, bad Hebru de, “Une U Long U Syiem Jong Ki Jiw.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Uwei te na kita ki nongkam sniew, ba la sdien, u la krenbeiñ ïa U, u da ong, “Mem long uta U Khrist? To pynim ïa lade bad ïa ngi de.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Hynrei, uta uwei pat u la ïathuh, bad u la sneng ïa u, u da ong, “Mem sheptieng satia ïa U Blei, naba me long hapoh kajuh ka jingpynrem?",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ma ngi shisha da ka bahok ruh; namar ngi ïoh diang ïa kaba dei na kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba ngi la leh: hynrei, une um shym la leh ei ei ruh em ka bymdei.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> U la ong te, “Ko Jisu, to kynmaw ïa nga ynda me poi ha ka hima jong me.”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> U Jisu te U la ong ha u, “Shisha nga ong ha me, ha kane ka sngi men long lem bad nga ha ka paradais.”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Bad ka la long hamar kaba hynriew baje, te ka jingdum ka la wan tap ïa ka khyndew baroh haduh kaba khyndai baje.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te la pyndum ïa ka sngi, bad la pynkad ïa ka jingkah jong ka templ napdeng.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> U Jisu te haba u la pyrta da ka ktien bajam, u la ong, “Ko Kpa, ha ki kti jong me nga aiti ïa la ka mynsiem”: te haba u la ong ïa kane, u la ai noh ïa ka mynsiem.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Te haba u rangbah shispah u la ïohi ïa kaei ba la leh, u la ïaroh ïa U Blei, u da ong, “Da shisha une u briew u la long u bahok.”",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Bad kita ki paidbah baroh kiba la ïawan lang ban khmih ïa kane, haba ki la ïohi ïa kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba la leh, da kaba thab ïa la ki shadem, ki la leit phai pat.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Baroh ruh ki para ba ïa-ithuh jong u, bad ki kynthei kiba la lah ïabud lem ïa u na Galilaïa, ki la ïaïeng na jngai, ki da khmih ïa kine kiei kiei ruh.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Ha khmih ruh, u briew uba kyrteng “u Joseph”, uba long u myntri, u briew u babha bad bahok;",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> une um shym la ïakohnguh ïa ka jingsylla bad ïa ka jingleh jong ki; uba na Arimathaïa, ka shnong jong ki Jiw, uba u hi ruh u ju ap kyrmen ïa ka hima ka jong U Blei;",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> une u la leit ha u Pilat bad u la pan ïa ka met U Jisu.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Te haba u la pynhiar ïa ka, u la sop spaiñ ïa ka da ka jaiñ linen bani, bad u la buh ïa ka ha ka jingtep ba la tih jlih ha u maw, ha ka bym pat ju tep briew.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Te ka la long ka sngi ka jingpynkhreh, bad kan sa mih ka Sabbaton.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Te kita ki kynthei ruh, kiba la ïawan lem bad U na Galilaïa, ki la ïabud nadien, bad ki la ïakhmih ïa kata ka jingtep, bad kumno ba la buh ïa ka met jong U.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Ynda ki la ïaleit phai pat te, ki la ïa-pynkhreh ïa ki jingiwbih bad ïa ki jingsleh; hynrei, ha ka Sabbaton ki la shong sngi, katba kum ka hukum."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha ka sngi nyngkong ka taïew, haba kan sa shai byrngut, ki la leit sha kata ka jingtep, ki da rah ïa ki jingiwbih ïa kiba ki la ïa-pynkhreh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ki la shem ba la pyntyllun noh ïa u maw na kata ka jingtep.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Haba ki la ïabsut hapoh te, kim shym shem ïa ka met jong U Jisu uba U Trai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ka la jia te, haba ki dang ïakhuslai shaphang kane, ha khmih ruh, ar ngut ki rangbah ki la ïeng hajan jong ki ha ki jaiñkup baphyrnai lieh eh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te katba ki la ïasheptieng, bad ba ki la ïa-pyndem la ki khmat sha khyndew, ki la ong ha ki, “Balei phi wad ïa u ba-im hapdeng ki baïap?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> um don hangne, hynrei, u la mihpat; to ïakynmaw kumno u la ong ha phi, mynba u dang don ha Galilaïa,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> u da ong ba ka dei ban ai noh ïa U Khun u briew ha ki kti ki briew ki bapop, ban sahnarphna, bad ban mihpat ha ka balai sngi.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, ki la ïakynmaw ïa ki ktien jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba ki la ïaleit phai pat na kata ka jingtep, ki la ïathuh ïa kine kiei kiei baroh ha ki khatwei ngut, bad ha kita kiwei pat baroh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ki la long te ka Mari ka nong Magdala, bad ka Ïoanna, bad ka Mari ka kmie u Jakob; bad kiwei pat ki kynthei kiba don lem bad ki, ki la ïathuh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh ha kita ki apostol.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, kine ki ktien ki long ha ki kum ka jingkren kai; bad kim ngeit ïa ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, u Petros u la ïeng joit, bad u la phet sha kata ka jingtep; bad haba u la dem ban jngoh, u ïohi ïa kita ki jaiñ linen bani ba la buh kyrpang; bad u la leit noh sha la ïing da kaba sngewlyngngoh shaphang kata kaba la jia.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ha khmih ruh ar ngut na ki, ki dang ïaleit ha kata ka sngi sha ka nongrit, kaba kyrteng “Ka Emmaus”, kaba jngai na Jerusalem kumba phra mail.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki la ïakren paralok hi shaphang kine kiei kiei baroh kiba la lah jia long.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ka la jia te, katba ki dang ïakren bad ba ki ïakylli jingmut paralok hi, ba U Jisu hi u la wan hajan, bad u leit lem bad ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, la pynthame ïa ki khmat jong ki, kat ban ym ithuh ïa u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u la ong ha ki, “Kiba kumno kine ki jingong ïa kiba phi ïasyllok kylliang paralok hi, katba phi ïa-ïaid?” Te ki la ïeng, ki da 'matsngewsih.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te uwei na ki, uba kyrteng “U Kleopas”, u da ïathuh u la ong ha U, “Long tang ma me u nongwei ha Jerusalem, bad mem tip ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba la jia ha ka ha kine ki sngi?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Ïa kiba kumno?” Ki la ïathuh te ha U, “Ïa kiei kiei shaphang U Jisu uba na Nasaret, uba la long U Nongïathuhlypa, u bakhrawbor ha ka jingleh bad ha ka ktien ha khmat U Blei bad u paidlang baroh;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> kumno ruh ba ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki nongsynshar jong ngi, ki la aiti noh ïa U sha ka ban rem ban ïap, bad ba ki la ïasahnarphna ïa U.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngi, hynrei, ngi la ïakyrmen ba long ma U, U ban sa siewspah ïa u Israel; nalor kine baroh ruh putet, kane ka sngi ka long ka sngi balai naduh ba la jia kine kiei kiei ruh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nalor kata, ki kynthei ruh na ngi ki la ïa-pynkyndit thred ïa ngi, haba ki la don mynstep eh ha kata ka jingtep:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> namar haba kim shem ïa ka met jong U, ki la ïawan ong te, ba ki la ïohi ïa ka jingithuhpaw ki angel, kiba la ong ba U im.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te kiba na kita kiba la don lem bad ngi, ki la leit sha kata ka jingtep, bad ki la shem kumta, kumba kita ki kynthei ki la ïathuh ruh; hynrei, ïa U kim shym la ïohi keiñ.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ynda kumta, U la ong ha ki, “A phi kiba mut bakla, bad ba shan'ti ka dohnud ïa ka ban ngeit ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba ki nongïathuhlypa ki la ïathuh!",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ym long kaba la dei ïa uba U Khrist ban shah ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, bad ban leit bsut hapoh ka burom jong u?”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te haba u la sdang na u Moses, bad na Ki Nongïathuhlypa baroh, u la pynpaw ha ki ha Ki Jingthoh baroh ïa kiei kiei ruh shaphang ïa lade.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ki la poi te hajan kata ka nongrit sha kaba ki leit; U te U la leh ïa lade kum U ban sa leit kham jngai.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te ki la kyrpad ïa U, ki da ong, “To sah bad ngi; naba ka long janmiet, bad ka sngi ka la noh.” Te U la leit hapoh ïa ka ban sah lem bad ki.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ka la jia te haba U dang shong bam bad ki, haba U la shim ïa u kpu, U la kyrkhu, bad U la kdiah, bad U la sam ha ki.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, la pynpeit ïa ki khmat jong ki, bad ki la ithuh ïa U; U te U la jah noh jar na ki.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ki la ïa-ong paralok hi, “Ka dohnud jong ngi kam shym la pluh ha ngi, katba U la kren ha ngi ha kata ka lynti, bad katba U la plie wang ha ngi ïa Ki Jingthoh?”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ki la ïeng joit ha kata kajuh ka por, bad ki la leit phai pat sha Jerusalem, bad ki la shem ïa kita ki khatwei ngut, bad kita kiba don lem bad ki, ba ki la ïaseng lang,",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> ki da ïa-ong, “U Trai u la mihpat shisha, bad U la paw ha u Simon.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ki ruh ki la ïathuhkhana ïa kiei kiei ruh ba la jia ha kata ka lynti, bad kumno la ithuh ïa U da ki ha kaba kdiah ïa u kpu.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te katba ki dang ïakren ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, U Jisu hi u la ïeng hapdeng jong ki, bad u la ong ha ki, “Long ka jingsuk ïa phi!”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Hynrei, ki la sngewshyrkhei bad ki la sheptieng, bad ki la tharai ba ki la ïohi rngai.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> U la kylli te ïa ki, “Balei phi ïasngewtieng? bad namar balei ba ki jingmut artatien ki ïamih ha ki dohnud jong phi?",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> To khmih ïa ki kti jong nga bad ïa ki kjat jong nga, ba dei ma nga hi; to tba ïa nga, to khmih ruh; naba ka mynsiem kam don ka doh bad ka shyieng, kumba phi ïohi ïa nga ba nga don.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad haba u la ong ïa kane, u la pyni ha ki, ïa la ki kti bad ïa la ki kjat.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te haba ki dang ïalong ki bymngeit namar ka jingkmen, bad ba ki ïasngewphylla, u la ong ha ki, “Phi don ei ei hangne ban bam?”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ki la ai te ha u shi dkhot ka dohkha ba la thang bad na ka rewngap.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te haba u la shim u la bam ha khmat jong ki.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “Kine ki long kita ki ktien ïa kiba nga la kren ha phi, mynba nga dang don lem bad phi, ba ka dei ba yn pyndep ïa kiei kiei baroh, ïa kiba la thoh ha Ka Hukum u Moses bad ha Ki Nongïathuhlypa, bad ha Ki Salm de, shaphang jong nga.”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ynda kumta, u la plie wang ïa ka jingmut jong ki, ïa ka ban shemphang ïa kita Ki Jingthoh.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “Kumne la thoh ba ka la dei ïa U Khrist ban shah, bad ban mihpat de na ki nongïap ha ka balai ka sngi;",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> bad ba ha ka kyrteng jong u yn ïalap ïa ka jingkylla-ka-bamut bad ïa kaba map ki pop hapdeng ki jaid bynriew baroh, da kaba sdang na Jerusalem:",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> phi ruh phi long ki sakhi ïa kine kiei kiei.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Ha khmih ruh, nga phah ha phi ïa kata ba la kular U Kpa jong nga: hynrei, phi to ïaishong ha ka nongbah Jerusalem, tad ynda yn pynkup ïa phi da ka bor na jrong.”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ïalam noh habar ïa ki haduh Bethania; haba u la rah ïa la ki kti ruh, u la kyrkhu ïa ki.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Ka la jia ruh haba u dang kyrkhu ïa ki, ba u la khlad noh na ki, ba la rah ruh ïa u sha bneng.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Te haba ki la lah ïamane ïa u, ki la leit phai pat sha Jerusalem bad ka jingkmen kaba khraw.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Ki la don ruh khlem da pud ha ka templ, ki da ïaroh bad ki da ïakyrkhu ïa U Blei. Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;